Umubare w'abarwaye coronavirus (COVID-19) wiyongereye cyane mu Burayi/mu Karere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'abarwaye coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza ko ibintu bimeze nk'uko bimeze mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, ibyo bikaba byemeza ko nubwo icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri mu bihe bitandukanye bitewe n'igihugu, kiri kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Dushingiye ku byaranze Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane bigomba kongera imyiteguro yabo yo guhangana n'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazakenera kwitabwaho, cyane cyane ku barwayi bababaye cyane.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari itsinda ry'abantu barwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero batazwi impamvu yabiteye, bavuzwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko icyateye iki cyorezo ari coronavirus nshya ubu yitwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yitwa indwara ya koronavirusi (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko abagera kuri 80% by'abantu barwaye COVID-19 barwaye indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga indwara y'ubuhumekero irimo cyangwa idafite indwara y'ibihaha, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu bantu bagera kuri 14%, COVID-19 ihinduka indwara ikomeye cyane igasaba kujya mu bitaro mu gihe abasigaye 6% barwara indwara ikomeye igasaba kwitabwaho cyane.
Imfu z'abarwayi barwariye mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, tugenzura uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwagiye bufata ingufu mu bihugu byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'u Bwongereza (UK) maze tukabigereranya n'ubw'intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya kandi umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri iki gihe mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza n'ababa mu Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
