Mu Burayi/EEA, abantu batatu ba mbere bemejweho ubwandu batangajwe n'u Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarutse bavuye i Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, hari hamaze kugaragara abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu byose 30 bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza (UK), aho hagati ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 n'uwo munsi harimo, hari hamaze kugaragara abanduye 39,768 n'abamaze gupfa 1,727, mu gihe abanduye 17,750 n'abamaze gupfa 1,441 ari abo mu Butaliyani gusa.
Kubona umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 n'umubare w'abawanduye
Mu Kigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurinda no Gutegeka Indwara (ECDC), imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi hose, iboneka gusa mu makuru y'ibanze nk'abakozi ba Minisiteri y'Ubuzima, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'akarere ndetse na OMS, iherutse gusubirwamo buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma uko COVID-19 yagiye igenda mu Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza, no kuyigereranya n'iyo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'ikimenyetso cy'umubare w'abanduye COVID-19, twabaze umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14, dufata mu mutwe uko COVID-19 yagendaga mu bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'itariki ya 1 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Twerekanye kandi imibare yose y'abamaze kwandura muri buri gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo ugereranyije n'iy'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Imiterere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Imiterere y'ibyumweru 14 by'ubwandu bw'abantu banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange yakurikije iy'intara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku bihugu byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'u Burayi/EEA n'u Bwongereza muri rusange, ubwandu bw'indwara ya COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma buzamuka cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ibikoresho by'inyongera).
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'ukwiyongera kwihuse kw'umubare w'abanduye bavuye mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byerekanye imiterere nk'iyo yo kwiyongera kw'ubwandu bw'indwara ya COVID-19 (Ibikoresho by'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare yose y'abanduye COVID-19, mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'abari mu Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Rushimangira ko, ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibindi bihugu 15 bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byari byamaze gutangaza umubare w'abanduye ugereranywa n'uw'Ubutaliyani mu byumweru bitatu gusa mbere cyangwa munsi yayo.
Ibisubizo byacu bigaragaza ko umubare w'abamaze kwandura COVID-19 wiyongera mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Imiterere igaragara mu mubare w'abandura COVID-19 igaragaza ko iki cyorezo kigenda gitera imbere ku muvuduko ugereranywa mu bihugu byose.
Ibi ni mu gihe ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, hari itandukaniro mu buryo bw'igihugu bwo kwita ku buzima rusange, kandi hashobora kuba hari ibisobanuro bitandukanye by'uburwayi mu bihugu no ku buryo butandukanye bwo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo bamenye niba barwaye COVID-19, harimo no gupima abanduye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere two mu Butaliyani twazahajwe na COVID-19 basobanuye ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwayi barwaye COVID-19 bari bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane kandi itangazamakuru ryatangaje ko ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane muri utwo turere byamaze kugera ku bushobozi bwabyo.
Amakuru ajyanye no kwakira abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane ubu aboneka ku rwego rwa EU/EEA ku bantu 6% gusa na 1% (amakuru ntaragaragazwa).
Icyakora, bigomba gukusanywa mu buryo buhoraho kugira ngo byunganire amakuru y'ubugenzuzi aherutse, yibanda ku mubare w'abamaze kwandura no ku bapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 201011 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini mu bibanza byo kurwaramo by'indembe n'iby'indembe mu Burayi, kuva ku byumba 29,2 mu Budage kugeza ku byumba 4,2 ku baturage 100,000 muri Portugal.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kugira amikoro menshi cyangwa make kurusha u Butaliyani (ibitanda 12,5 byo kwita ku barwayi barwaye indwara zikomeye n'ibyo mu rwego rwo hagati ku baturage 100,000 mu 201011).
Imyiteguro yo gukora imiterere ijyanye no guhaza ubushobozi bwo kwita ku buzima, hamwe n'ibyerekezo kuri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza by'ubwiyongere bw'abanduye COVID-19 bari mu bitaro bifitanye isano n'ibyago 90% byo kurenza ubushobozi bw'ibitanda byo mu bitaro bya ICU, bitangwa mu isesengura rya gatandatu ry'icyerekezo cy'ibyago byihuse bya ECDC kuri COVID-19.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu abanduye baguye mu bice bimwe na bimwe byo mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibigo by'indembe bikunze gukorera abaturage bo mu karere runaka, amakuru ajyanye n'abanduye n'ibitanda by'indembe by'indembe by'indembe by'indembe by'indembe by'indembe by'indembe by'indembe, byaba byiza aboneka ku rwego rwa Nomenclature y'ibigo by'indembe by'ibarurishamibare 2 (NUTS-2).
Ubumenyi bw'u Butaliyani n'imiterere iriho mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri gutera imbere mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane bigomba rero kwitegura uko bizagenda mu gihe SARS-CoV-2 izakomeza kwanduzwa mu baturage no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu bitaro bya muganga, nk'uko bimeze mu turere two mu Butaliyani twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago rya vuba aha rya ECDC, uburyo bwihuse, bwihuse kandi bunonosoye ni ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, aho guhindukira ukava ku buryo bwo kugabanya ubwandu ukajya ku buryo bwo kugabanya ubwandu, kuko ukwiyongera kwihuse kw'umubare w'abarwayi kwitezwe bishobora kutaha abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro igihe gihagije cyo gusobanukirwa, kwemera no guhuza ibisubizo byabo niba bitashyizwe mu bikorwa hakiri kare.
Igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago kandi rirerekana ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari umwanya muto ibihugu bifite amahirwe yo kongera imbaraga mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya igitutu ku buvuzi.
Bitabaye ibyo, birashoboka ko mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibindi bihugu bya EU/EEA zizagerwaho n'umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000 kandi cyanduza abarenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, bigatuma abantu bagerwaho n'amakuba.
Kimwe na virusi yayo ihuriyeho, SARS-CoV, yateje SARS mu bantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no kwanduzwa n'imbeba kandi igateza ibimenyetso bisa n'ibyo binyuze mu buryo nk'ubwo.
Icyakora, COVID-19 ifite ubukana n'urupfu biri hasi ugereranyije na SARS ariko ikwirakwira cyane kandi ikagira ingaruka ku bantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato n'abagabo kurusha abagore.
Kubera ko umubare w'ibitabo by'ubushakashatsi ku birebana n'iyo ndwara iri kuvumburwa ugenda wiyongera, iyi ngingo igerageza gutanga isuzuma ryuzuye kandi ryuzuye ry'icyo kibazo cy'ubushakashatsi kigenda kivuka mu buryo bwihuse.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ibanze ku birebana n'icyorezo, impamvu kivuka, virusi, uko kivumburwa, uko kivurwa, uko kigira icyo gitanga n'uko gikumira indwara.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko iyi nkuru izadufasha gusobanukirwa no kurandura iyi ndwara iteje akaga.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi wabaye ku ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye ikintu kitazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu ngo zabo mu gihe cyose cy'iminsi mikuru ndetse no mu byumweru byinshi nyuma yaho kubera icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubwandu bushya.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na koronavirusi (CoV) yateje icyorezo cy'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS) mu 2003; bityo, yatangajwe SARS-CoV-2 n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, n'indwara ifitanye isano na yo itangira kwitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze gikwirakwira mu gihugu hose kandi kigera ku bandi bantu 50 ku isi hose.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yatumye haboneka abantu barenga 80.000 banduye COVID-19, abarenga 40.000 barasezererwa, abarenga 3.000 barapfa.
OMS iraburira ko COVID-19 ari umwanzi wa rubanda numero 1 kandi ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, inyandiko zirenga 200 zanditswe kuri COVID-19 zirimo Virology, Epidemiology, Etiology, Diagnostics, n'ubuvuzi kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yagaragaje uko virusi yagiye itandukana n'abarwayi benshi.
Iyi raporo igerageza gusubiramo iterambere ry'ubushakashatsi mu gice gishya kandi cyihuta.
Igihe cyose bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na CoV, indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, icyorezo cyabaye mu 2012).
Nanone tuzasuzuma ibyo tumaze kumenya ku birebana no kwirinda iyo ndwara no kuyisuzuma, ndetse n'ibindi bibazo bikiriho ariko byihutirwa.
CoVs zisanzwe zisanzwe zisanzwe zisanzwe zitewe n'indwara zidakora ku bantu, ahanini zitera hafi 15% by'ibicurane 4.
Icyakora, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye inshuro ebyiri na CoV z'abantu ziteye indwara cyane, ni ukuvuga SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye habaho icyorezo cyatangiriye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi bidatinze zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi zifite ubwandu n'urupfu biteye ubwoba.
Ku bw'ibyo, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho ubu ni icya gatatu cy'ubwandu bwa CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku ishusho ya 1,1, ibicurane by'indwara y'amahaha bifite inkomoko zitazwi byatangajwe bwa mbere mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kuri Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, urukurikirane rw'iyo CoV rwasohotse.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, havuzwe umuntu wa mbere w'umurwayi w'icyaha cy'urupfu mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyo cyorezo cyahise kigera mu migi, intara n'ibihugu byo hafi aho.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, hatanzwe raporo y'uko abashinzwe ubuzima banduye, ibyo bikaba byumvikanisha ko bishobora guterwa n'umuntu ku wundi.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan warafunzwe n'uburyo bwose bwo gutwara abantu n'ibintu buhagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe kuri iyi ndwara bwagaragaje ko mu barwayi 41 bagaragaweho iyi ndwara, 21 gusa ari bo bahuye mu buryo butaziguye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja ryo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, ryafashwe nk'aho iyi ndwara yaturutse ku nyamaswa zitazwi.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingutu ku isi hose.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yatangazwaga, iyi ndwara yari imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo ku isi hose (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo.2).2).
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda bihinduka mu buryo bwihuse, icyiciro cya nyuma n'uburemere bw'iki cyorezo biracyari kugenzurwa.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakorewe mu bigo bitandukanye ku barwayi 8,866 barimo 4,021 banduye COVID-19 bwashyizwe ahagaragara mu buryo bushya bw'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe kuri iki cyorezo (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yanduje abantu b'imyaka yose, ariko cyane cyane mu myaka 30-65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47.7%) cy'abanduye bari bafite imyaka irenga 50, bake cyane bari munsi ya 20, kandi abantu 14 gusa banduye bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yanduje abagabo benshi (0,31/100,000) kurusha abagore (0,27/100,000).
COVID-19 yaguye mu matsinda ahanini mu karere ka Hubei no mu nkengero zaho.
COVID-19 yatwaye iminsi 5 (2-9) kuva itangiye kugeza igaragaye.
Igihe cy'uburumbuke cyabayeho ni iminsi 4,8 (3,0-7,2).
Igihe cy'ibanze kuva umuntu atangira kwandura kugeza apfuye ni iminsi 9,5 (4,8-13).
Umubare w'ibanze w'abandura (R0) wari 3.77 (IC 95%: 3.51- 4.05) naho R0 yahindutse yari 2.23-4.82.
Umubare w'abanduye wiyongereye cyane mbere ya 23 Mutarama 2020, bihuye n'igihe cy'ingendo zikomeye mbere y'umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi mu Bushinwa.
Imfu z'abarwayi bagaragaweho ubwandu bwari ku kigero cya 1, 44% (IC 95%: 1, 10 - 1, 86%), naho iz'abarwayi bose bari barenganye zari 3, 06% (IC 95%: 2, 02- 4, 59%).
Ibintu bitatu by'ingenzi bishobora gutera COVID-19 ni igitsina (abagabo), imyaka (≥60), n'indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha.
CoV ni umuryango muto wa virusi nini kandi z'uruhu rurerure zirimo urusobe rumwe rw'ubwonko bwa RNA.
Zishobora kugabanywamo amoko ane, ari yo alpha, beta, gamma na delta, aho alpha na beta-CoV bizwi ko zandura abantu.
Glycoprotein ya enveloppe spike (S) ifatanye n'indwara ya SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV mu buryo buteganyijwe n'indwara ya angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) na dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) mu byiciro byayo, hanyuma ikora fusion y'urusobe.
Genome ya RNA ya virusi irasohoka mu cytoplasma; nyuma yo gusubiramo genome ya virusi, RNA ya genome iherekejwe na glycoproteins ya envelope na nucleocapsid protein ihanga uduhimba turimo virion, hanyuma tukabundanya n'urwungano rwa plasma kugirango dusohore virusi.
Urukurikirane rwa mbere rwa genomic rwa SARS-CoV-2 rwatangajwe ku ya 10 Mutarama 2020.
SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye ko ari ubwoko bushya bwa beta-CoV ifite ibimenyetso birenga 99,98% by'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima mu bipimo 10 byatoranyijwe hakurikijwe urutonde rw'ibinyabuzima byavanywe aho iki cyorezo cyatangiriye, ku isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Huanan mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite ibinyabuzima byinshi bisa na SARS-CoV kurusha MERS-CoV.
Binyuze mu gukoresha mikorosikopi ya elegitoronike, uduhimba twa SARS-CoV-2 twabonetse mu bice by'ubunini bw'ubwonko bw'umuntu.
Basanze ACE2 y'umuntu ari receptor ya SARS-CoV-2 ndetse na SARS-CoV.
Icyakora, poroteyine ya S ya SARS-CoV-2 ifatanye na ACE2 y'umuntu mu buryo budafite imbaraga kurusha iya SARS-CoV, ibyo bikaba bihuriyeho n'uko SARS-CoV-2 ituma abarwayi banduza cyane kurusha SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no gukora poroteyine ngufi nshya ivanze na orf3b na poroteyine ihuma ivanze na orf8.
Orf3b ya SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira uruhare mu gutuma virusi igira ubwandu kandi igabanya uburyo IFNβ igaragara; ariko, orf8 nta gice cyangwa impamvu igaragara igaragara.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Zhou, et al., batangaje imiterere ya cryo-EM y'umuntu wuzuye ACE2 ku 2.9 Å mu buryo buhuje na B0AT1 yohereje amino acide.
Basanze uru ruvange, rufite imiterere ifunguye n'ifunze, rwateranyirijwe hamwe nk'ikinyabutabire kandi uruvange rwa ACE2-B0AT1 rushobora guhuza poroteyine ebyiri za S, ibyo bikaba bitanga ibimenyetso byo kumenya no kwandura CoV.
B0AT1 ishobora kuba icyerekezo cyo kuvura mu gupima imiti mu guhashya ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Inkomoko n'umufasha
Birazwi ko SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV byakomotse ku ducurama kandi ko byandujwe ku bantu binyuze mu ducurama n'ingamiya.
Binyuze mu igereranya ry'imiterere ya SARS-CoV-2 n'izindi CoV, udusimba twafashwe nk'abanduye SARS-CoV-2 kuko virusi nshya ihwanye na 96% na CoV ebyiri zisa na SARS zaturutse ku ducurama twitwa bat-SL-CoVZX45 na bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Icyakora, ntiharamenyekana uwo virusi yavuye mu bwoko bwayo ikaza ku bantu, kandi inzira yo kuyandura ntiramenyekana.
Ji, et al, batanze inama y'inzoka nk'abanyamubiri ba virusi kuva ku mbuni kugera ku bantu, byaranzwe no kongera guhuza mu buryo bumwe muri poroteyine ya S.
Nk'uko ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abashakashatsi bo mu mujyi wa Guangzhou mu Bushinwa, bwagaragaje ko ingona - inyamaswa zifite amazuru maremare zirya ibimonyo zikunze gukoreshwa mu buvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa - ari zo zishobora kuba nyirazo wa SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n'uko ihuriyeho n'ibinyabuzima mu buryo bwa 99% mu bwoko bwa CoV yavumbuwe mu ngona na SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko, itandukaniro rya 1% ryakwirakwijwe mu bwoko bubiri bw'ibinyabuzima biracyari itandukaniro rinini; bityo, ibisubizo bifatika by'ibimenyetso bifatika birategerejwe (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo.33).
Imiterere ya SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo bw'ibinyabuzima n'ubw'imikorere yayo ntiharamenyekana.
SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zishobora kubaho mu byumba by'imashini mu gihe cy'amasaha 48 mu bidukikije byumye no mu gihe cy'iminsi 5 mu gihe cy'ubushyuhe bwa 40-50% n'ubushyuhe bwa 20 °C.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira imiterere nk'iyo.
Byatangajwe ko SARS-CoV-2 igira ibyago byo kwandura mu mwuka wa ultraviolet no ku bushyuhe ku gipimo cya 56 °C mu gihe cy'iminota 30; ether, 75% ya éthanol, umuti wica udukoko urimo chlorine, acide peracetic, chloroform n'ibindi byuma by'ibinure, ariko si chlorhexidine, bishobora gutuma virusi idakora.
Ubusanzwe abantu bose ntibaba bafite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 bityo bakaba bashobora kwandura iyi virusi nshya.
Kugeza ubu nta bushakashatsi burambuye bwakozwe ku bijyanye n'igisubizo cy'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri kuri SARS-CoV-2.
Bityo, dushobora gusa kureba ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere ku zindi CoV, cyane cyane SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV (Igishushanyo. (Igishushanyo.4).4).
Ubusanzwe, nyuma y'uko virusi igeze ku mugenzuzi, itangira kumenyekana n'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bw'uwo mugenzuzi binyuze mu byuma byakira ibiranga umubiri (PRRs) birimo ibifata ibisa na C-type lectin, ibifata ibisa na Toll (TLR), ibifata ibisa na NOD (NLR), n'ibifata ibisa na RIG-I (RLR).
Binyuze mu nzira zitandukanye, virusi ituma habaho kugaragaza ibintu by'ubuhumekero, gukura kw'ingirabuzimafatizo za dendritic, no guhimba interférons z'ubwoko bwa I (IFN) zigabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi kandi zikihutisha imikorere ya fagocytose ya macrophage y'indwara z'ubwandu.
Icyakora, poroteyine ya N ya SARS-CoV ishobora gufasha virusi guhunga ibisubizo by'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara.
Bidatinze, ubwirinzi bw'umubiri buzafatanya n'ubundi kurwanya iyo virusi.
Imyunyungugu ya T irimo CD4+ na CD8+ T zigira uruhare rukomeye mu kurinda.
Ingirabuzimafatizo za CD4+ T zitera ingirabuzimafatizo za B gukora za antibody zihariye virusi, naho ingirabuzimafatizo za CD8+ T zikangiza mu buryo butaziguye ingirabuzimafatizo zanduye virusi.
Ingirabuzimafatizo za T zifasha mu kurinda umubiri zitanga uturemangingo tw'ingirabuzimafatizo tw'ubwoko bw'imiti (cytoquines) dutuma umubiri urwara.
Icyakora, CoV ishobora kubuza imikorere y'ingirabuzimafatizo za T binyuze mu gutuma ingirabuzimafatizo za T zipfa.
Ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri burimo n'ibindi bikoresho nk'ibinyabutabire nka C3a na C5a ndetse n'udupira ni ingenzi mu kurwanya ubwandu bw'agakoko gatera SIDA.
Urugero, udukoko tw'ubwirinzi twatoraguwe mu murwayi wakize twateye inkeke MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, iyo umubiri w'umuntu ugize ubwirinzi bukabije, bituma habaho ingirabuzimafatizo nyinshi z'umudendezo zishobora kwangiza cyane ibihaha n'izindi ngingo, kandi mu mimerere mibi cyane, zikangiza ingingo nyinshi ndetse zigatuma umuntu apfa.
Indwara ya SARS-CoV-2, igaragara mu miterere y'ibinyamubiri, ishobora kurwara cyane abantu bageze mu za bukuru bafite indwara ziterwa na yo hamwe n'abagore batwite.
Ni ibisanzwe ko abantu bagaragarizwa virusi nyinshi cyangwa bafite ubwirinzi bw'umubiri budafite imbaraga, bagira ibyago byinshi byo kwandura kurusha abandi.
Igihe cyo kubamo cya SARS-CoV-2 kigereranywa ni iminsi 1-14, cyane cyane iminsi 3-7 ishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 425 ba mbere banduye muri Wuhan.
Icyakora, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 1.099 bugaragaza ko igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro cyari iminsi 3 ku kigereranyo kandi kikava ku minsi 0 kugeza ku minsi 24.
Ubushakashatsi buheruka, nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, bugaragaza ko igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro cyari iminsi 4,8 (3,0-7,2) hashingiwe ku mibare y'abantu 8,866.
Ni ngombwa cyane ko inzego z'ubuzima zihindura igihe cy'igenzurwa cy'ubwirinzi gishingiye ku gihe cy'igwingira cy'ukuri, bityo bikirinda abantu banduye ariko badafite ibimenyetso kwanduza abandi.
Ubusanzwe, abantu banduye cyangwa banduye iyi virusi basabwa kumara iminsi 14 mu kato.
Ese igihe cyo gushyirwa mu kato kigomba kongerwa kikagera ku minsi 24?
Ubushyuhe ni cyo kimenyetso cy'ingenzi kandi cya mbere cya COVID-19, gishobora kutagira ibimenyetso cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso nk'umusonga utose, guhumeka nabi, ububabare bw'imitsi, iseseme, umutwe, kubabara mu muhogo, impumuro, ububabare bw'igituza, umubyibuho, kugira iseseme, kugira isesemi no gusubirana.
Bamwe mu barwayi bagaragaweho impumuro nke na/ cyangwa hypoxemia nyuma y'icyumweru kimwe indwara itangiye.
Mu gihe indwara iba ikomeye, abarwayi bahitaga barwara indwara y'ubuhumekero, ikamuga gashya, acidose y'umubiri n'indwara y'ubuhumekero.
Abarwayi bafite umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero n'umuriro ukabije, ndetse n'abadafite uburwayi bwo mu bihaha, bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo bamenye niba nta virusi iri muri bo kugira ngo bashobore kugenzura hakiri kare.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019 bwagaragaje ko ibice by'ibimenyetso byari 98% ku bishyuha, 76% ku musarani, 55% ku ndwara yo guhumeka nabi, na 3% ku ndwara y'ibisebe; 8% by'abarwayi bari bakeneye inkunga yo guhumeka.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi nk'ubwo byavuzwe mu bushakashatsi bubiri buherutse gukorwa ku muryango n'ubundi bwatewe no kwanduzanya kw'umuntu udafite ibimenyetso.
Mu buryo bufatika, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2012 bwagaragaje ko abarwayi ba MERS-CoV na bo bari bafite umuriro (98%), inkorora yumye (47%), na dyspnea (55%) nk'ibimenyetso byabo by'ibanze.
Icyakora, 80% muri bo bari bakeneye inkunga yo guhumeka, barenze cyane abarwayi ba COVID-19 kandi bihuje n'ubukana bw'indwara ya MERS buruta ubwa COVID-19.
Kuribwa n'igifu (26%) no kubabara mu muhogo (21%) na byo byagaragaraga ku barwayi ba MERS.
Mu barwayi ba SARS, byagaragaye ko umuriro (99%-100%), inkorora yumye (29%-75%), guhumeka nabi (40%-42%), impiswi (20-25%), no kubabara mu muhogo (13-25%) ari byo bimenyetso by'ingenzi kandi inkunga yo guhumeka yari ikenewe ku barwayi bagera kuri 14%-20%.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, umubare w'abapfa bishwe na COVID-19 wari 2% ubwo abamaze kwandura ku isi hose bari 66,576.
Mu buryo bufatika, umubare w'abapfa bishwe na SARS mu Ugushyingo 2002 wari 10% ku bantu 8.096 bamaze kwandura.
Ku bijyanye na MERS, hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu kwezi kwa Kamena 2012, umubare w'abapfa wari 37% ku bantu 2,494 bamaze kwandura.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwagaragaje ko R0 ya SARS-CoV-2 yari hejuru ya 6.47 ifite intera yo kwizerwa (CI) ya 95% ya 5.71-7.23, mu gihe R0 ya SARS-CoV yari hagati ya 2 na 4.
Kugereranya SARS-CoV-2 na MERS-CoV na SARA-CoV ku bijyanye n'ibimenyetso, impfu n'ubwandu bw'indwara ya R0 byatanzwe mu mbonerahamwe Table1.1.
Imibare iri hejuru igaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwira kurusha MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV, ariko ko idashobora kwica cyane kurusha izo ebyiri za nyuma.
Bityo, kurwanya icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 biragoye cyane kurusha icyorezo cya MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV.
Kenshi iyo indwara igaragara mu matsinda, iboneka mu muryango umwe cyangwa mu bantu benshi cyangwa mu modoka imwe, urugero nk'ubwato bw'urugendo.
Abarwayi akenshi baba barigeze gukora ingendo cyangwa kuba mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyangwa mu tundi duce twatewe n'icyorezo cyangwa bagirana imishyikirano n'abantu banduye cyangwa abarwayi mu byumweru bibiri bishize mbere y'uko icyo cyorezo kigaragara.
Icyakora, byavuzwe ko abantu bashobora gutwara virusi nta bimenyetso birenze ibyumweru bibiri kandi abarwayi bakize bakava mu bitaro bashobora kongera gutwara virusi, ibyo bikaba bitanga umuburo wo kongera igihe cyo gushyirwa mu kato.
Abarwayi bafite umubare usanzwe cyangwa ugabanutse w'utugingo tw'amaraso tw'umweru (cyane cyane utw'imyakura) mu gihe cy'imyakura.
Urugero, indwara ya lymphopenia ifite ingirabuzima fatizo zera z'amaraso &lt; 4×109/L harimo ingirabuzima fatizo z'amaraso &lt; 1×109/L, n'umubare w'aspartate aminotransferase n'indwara ya virusi byazamutse mu barwayi 1,099 ba COVID-19.
Imyinshi mu barwayi bagaragaje ko mu maraso yabo habayeho kongera imisemburo y'umwijima n'imisemburo n'umusemburo witwa myoglobin, mu gihe abenshi bagaragaje ko habayeho kongera imyanda y'imyakura n'imyakura y'imyakura.
Mu barwayi barwaye indwara zikomeye, igipimo cya D- dimer, ikinyabutabire cyongera fibrin mu maraso, cyararengeje, kandi umubare w'indwara z'amaraso wagabanutse buhoro buhoro.
Ibimenyetso bidasanzwe mu mashusho y'umuco w'igituza biboneka ku barwayi benshi ba COVID-19 kandi bigaragazwa n'ibice bibiri by'ibice cyangwa kubura uburabyo mu bihaha.
Abarwayi bakunze kurwara indwara z'ubuhumekero butameze neza, indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha n'indwara y'ubuhumekero budafite ubushobozi (ARDS).
Iyo indwara ya ARDS ibayeho, ubukana bw'amaraso, amazi menshi n'imyanya y'uruhu iba iri ku kigero cyo hejuru, bituma imikorere y'umwuka w'umubiri idakora neza.
Imikorere mibi y'utugingo tw'ibihaha tw'ubwoko bwa mbere n'ubwa kabiri, ituma igipimo cy'umushongi w'umubiri kigabanuka kandi igatuma ubukana bw'ibihaha bwiyongera, bityo bigatuma ibihaha bidabasha kwaguka kandi bigatuma ibyago byo guhagarara by'ibihaha byiyongera.
Ku bw'ibyo, akenshi ibipimo bibi cyane byo mu gatuza biba bihuje n'ubukana bukabije bw'iyo ndwara.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, isesengura rya mbere ry'indwara ya COVID-19 ryerekanye ko hari udukoko tw'imyakura twanduye, tw'urusobe rwa hyaline, n'udukoko tw'imyakura twinjiye mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, n'udukoko tw'imyakura tw'imyakura tw'imyakura tw'imyakura mu bihaha by'umurwayi wapfuye azize iyo ndwara, bihuye n'indwara y'ubwandu bwa virusi na ARDS kandi bisa n'iby'abarwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Kugaragaza RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu buryo bwo gusubiza mu buryo bwa polymerase (RT-PCR) byakoreshejwe nk'ingingo z'ingenzi mu gusuzuma COVID-19.
Icyakora, kubera igipimo kinini cy'abanduye nabi, gishobora kwihutisha icyorezo, ibimenyetso byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi byatangiye gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma indwara (bitakiri bishingiye gusa kuri RT-PCR) mu Bushinwa ku ya 13 Gashyantare 2020.
Ibintu nk'ibyo kandi byabayeho igihe basuzumaga indwara ya SARS.
Ku bw'ibyo, kugira ngo umuntu ashobore kumenya neza indwara afite, ni ngombwa ko asuzuma amateka yayo, ibimenyetso byayo, ibipimo byo muri laboratwari n'ibimenyetso by'imiti.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda rya Feng Zhang ryasobanuye uburyo bwo gukoresha uburyo bwa SHERLOCK bushingiye kuri CRISPR mu gutahura SARS-CoV-2, bushobora gutahura ibice bya RNA bya SARS-CoV-2 byakozwe ku gipimo cya 20 × 10-18 mol/L kugeza kuri 200 × 10-18 mol/L (amakopi 10-100 kuri microlitiro y'ibikoresho) hakoreshejwe inkoni y'ibishishi mu gihe kitarenze isaha, nta bikoresho byinshi bikenewe.
Twizeye ko ubu buryo bushya bushobora kongera cyane ibyiyumvo no korohereza abantu mu gihe buzabonerwa ibimenyetso mu bipimo byo mu buvuzi.
Kubera kubura ubunararibonye mu kuvura iyi virusi nshya, abaganga bashobora cyane cyane kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19, mu gihe bagerageza uburyo butandukanye bwo kuvura bwakoreshejwe cyangwa bwatanzwe mbere mu kuvura izindi virusi nk'iyi SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV n'izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi (Imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe2).2).
Muri ubwo buvuzi harimo ubuvuzi buriho n'ubufite ubushobozi bwo gukoreshwa n'imiti igabanya ubukana bw'agakoko gatera SIDA, imiti igabanya ubukana bw'umubiri, siteroyi, plasma y'abarwayi bakize, imiti y'Abashinwa n'ubufasha mu by'imitekerereze.
Ndetse n'umushongi wavuye ku barwayi bakize, wateganyijwe gukoreshwa mu buvuzi.
Amashyirahamwe y'imiti arimo guhatana kugira ngo ahingure udukoko tw'ubwirinzi n'inkingo zo kurwanya iyo virusi.
SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane cyane ibihaha mu ntangiriro kandi birashoboka ko yibasira, mu rugero ruto, izindi ngingo zigaragaza ACE2, nk'urwego rw'igifu n'impyiko.
Icyakora, indwara zo guhumeka z'ibyorezo n'iz'ibyorezo ni zo ziteza ibibazo byinshi kandi ni zo zituma abantu benshi bapfa.
Bityo, ubufasha bwo guhumeka ni ingenzi mu kugabanya ibimenyetso no gukiza ubuzima kandi bukubiyemo imiti rusange ya ogisijeni, ogisijeni ihindagurika cyane, guhumeka bidakoreshejwe, no guhumeka mu buryo bw'imashini bitewe n'uburemere bw'indwara.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bikomeye by'ubuhumekero bagomba gushyigikirwa n'imashini yo mu mubiri (ECMO), uburyo bwo kuvura umutima n'ibihaha bukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara z'umutima cyangwa z'ubuhumekero zishobora gushyira ubuzima mu kaga.
Byongeye kandi, kubungabunga ubusumbane bw'ibinyabutabire, gukumira no kuvura ubwandu bw'ibanze n'imyanda y'ibinyabutabire, no kurinda imikorere y'ingingo z'ingenzi na byo ni ngombwa ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2.
Birazwi ko cytocin zituruka ku gukaza umurego kw'umubiri mu barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Cytokine storm ni uburyo bwo kwitabira indwara ziterwa n'ubukana bw'ibinyabutabire, bigaragazwa no gusohora cytokines zirimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ na MCP-1.
Izi cytokines zituma ingirabuzimafatizo z'umubiri zisohora ingirabuzimafatizo nyinshi z'ubushake, ari zo mpamvu nyamukuru zitera indwara ya ARDS n'imikorere mibi y'ingingo nyinshi.
Gukumira ubwandu ni ngombwa mu kuvura ibiza by'imiti yitwa cytokines, cyane cyane ku barwayi barwaye indwara ikomeye.
Koritoseroide na tocilizumab, umuti urwanya IL6 ukoreshwa mu kuvura cytocin.
Ubundi buryo bwo kuvura indwara z'umusemburo mu gihe cy'ibiza bya sitokine ni uguhindura uburyo bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya indwara z'umusemburo wa T; guhagarika IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF; kubuza JAK; blinatumomab; guhagarika ibimenyetso bya sitokine 4; n'imiti igabanya HDAC.
Steroids, nk'imiti igabanya ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, zakoreshejwe cyane mu kuvura SARS mu kugabanya ubukana bw'ibyangiritse mu bwonko.
Icyakora, gukoresha steroid mu rugero rwagutse ntibyagize akamaro ku ndwara ikomeye y'ibihaha mu barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19.
Ahubwo, bishobora gutera ingaruka zikomeye, cyane cyane indwara y'amagufwa y'amaraso, bigatuma umuntu atabona ibisubizo by'ibibazo afite.
Nyamara, ingamba ngufi za corticosteroids mu bipimo biri hagati y'ibiri hasi n'ibiri hagati y'ibiri hejuru, zasabwe gukoreshwa mu bwitonzi ku barwayi ba COVID-19 barwaye cyane.
Mu gihe cyo kwandika iyi nkuru, nta muti wa virusi ushoboye kwemezwa.
Icyakora, kwinjiza mu mitsi imiti ya Remdesivir, ikoreshwa nk'imiti ikoreshwa mu kuvura indwara ya COVID-19, byagaragaye ko igira ingaruka nziza ku murwayi wo muri Amerika urwaye COVID-19.
Remdesivir ni umuti mushya wa virusi wakozwe na Gilead mu mizo ya mbere mu kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi ya Ebola na Marlburg.
Nyuma, remdesivir yagaragaje kandi ko ishobora kubuza izindi virusi za RNA z'uruti rumwe harimo virusi za MERS na SARS.
Ishingiye kuri ibyo, Gilead yahaye Ubushinwa uwo muti kugira ngo ukoreshwe mu igerageza ku bantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi ibisubizo byitezwe cyane.
Byongeye kandi, baricitinb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ ritonavir na ribavirin byatangajwe ko ari uburyo bwo kuvura bw'ibanze ku barwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bukabije.
Kurwara igifu, kugira isesemi, kuruka, kwangirika kw'umwijima n'ibindi bintu bishobora kubaho nyuma yo gufatanya imiti ya lopinavir/ ritonavir.
Imikorere y'ubu buryo bwo kuvura hamwe n'indi miti ikoreshwa mu barwayi, igomba kugenzurwa neza.
Plasma y'abarwayi bakize n'imikorere y'abanduye
Gufata amaraso y'abarwayi bakize indwara yandura kugira ngo avurwe n'abandi barwayi bayirwaye cyangwa kugira ngo abantu bafite amagara mazima barinde kwandura iyo ndwara, bimaze igihe kirekire.
Mu by'ukuri, abarwayi bakize akenshi bagira ingano y'amaraso menshi y'udufashi tw'umubiri twirinda icyo cyorezo.
Imyanya ndangagitsina ni immunoglobuline (Ig) ikorwa na B lymphocyte mu kurwanya udukoko dutera indwara n'ibindi bintu by'amahanga kandi imenya molekile zidasanzwe ziri muri utwo dukoko kandi zikazitesha agaciro mu buryo butaziguye.
Bishingiye kuri ibyo, plasma yakusanyijwe mu maraso y'itsinda ry'abarwayi bakize COVID-19 maze bayitera abarwayi 10 barwaye cyane.
Ibimenyetso byabo byagiye bihinduka mu masaha 24, biherekejwe no kugabanya ubuhumekero n'ubwandu bwa virusi ndetse no kongera umwuka wa ogisijeni mu maraso.
Icyakora, hakenewe igenzura no gusobanura kugira ngo uburyo bukoreshwe ku kigero kinini mbere yuko imiti yihariye itegurwa.
Byongeye kandi, kubera ingaruka z'ubuvuzi, hari ibyago bimwe na bimwe bifitanye isano na plasma bigomba gusuzumwa neza.
Urugero, udukoko tw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri dushobora gutuma umubiri udakora neza, bigatuma habaho indwara yo kugabanya imisemburo y'ibinure (syndrome de libération de cytokines), ishobora gushyira ubuzima mu kaga.
Ubusanzwe, ingano y'abanduye amaraso iba iri hasi, kandi plasma ikenerwa cyane mu kuvura abarwayi barwaye indwara ikomeye.
Biragoye guhanga no gukora za 'antibodies' zihariye mu buryo bwihuse ku buryo byafasha kurwanya icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Bityo rero, ni ingenzi kandi ni iby'ingirakamaro cyane gutandukanya uturemangingo twa B n'abarwayi bakize no kumenya kode z'ibinyabuzima zigaragaza za 'anticorps' z'ingirakamaro cyangwa kureba niba hari 'anticorps' z'ingirakamaro zirwanya poroteyine z'ingenzi za virusi.
Muri ubwo buryo, dushobora kongera vuba cyane uburyo bwo gukora za rukingo.
TCM yakoreshejwe mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye mu Bushinwa mu myaka ibihumbi.
Ariko kandi, ingaruka zayo ahanini zishingiye ku guhuza ibintu byinshi mu buryo butandukanye bitewe n'indwara igaragazwa hashingiwe ku bitekerezo bya TCM.
Ibyinshi mu bikoresho bikora neza biracyari mu nzira cyangwa ntibiramenyekana neza kuko bigoye kubikuramo no kubimenya cyangwa kubikoresha mu buryo bwiza.
Muri iki gihe, kubera kubura uburyo bwiza kandi bwihariye bwo kuvura COVID-19, TCM yabaye imwe mu miti ikomeye yo kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje kugeza ku rugero ruciriritse cyangwa abakize indwara zikomeye.
Urugero, ibipimo bya Shu Feng Jie Du na Lian Hua Qing Wen byagaragaye ko ari ingirakamaro mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ibipimo byo ku rwego rwo hejuru byo gukira mu kuvura abarwayi ba COVID-19 byagaragaye mu ntara zitandukanye zo mu Bushinwa zakoresheje TCM mu barwayi 87% barimo Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%), na Hunan (50%), mu gihe intara ya Hubei yakoresheje TCM mu barwayi bayo ba COVID-19 hafi 30% gusa, yari ifite igipimo cyo ku rwego rwo hasi cyo gukira (13%).
Ariko kandi, ibi ni ugereranya mu buryo bugaragara cyane kuko hari ibindi bintu byinshi bigira ingaruka nko umubare n'uburemere bw'abarwayi bigomba kujyanwa mu igenzura.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Boli Zhang na bagenzi be basohoye ubushakashatsi bugereranya uburyo bwo kuvura bw'iburengerazuba (WM) bwonyine n'uburyo bwo kuvura bw'ibanze bwa WM na TCM.
Basanze igihe cyo kongera ubushyuhe bw'umubiri, ibimenyetso bigahita, no kujya mu bitaro ari gito cyane mu itsinda ry'abakurikiranye WM+TCM ugereranyije n'abakurikiranye WM gusa.
Igitangaje cyane, ni uko igipimo cy'ibimenyetso by'indwara (kuva ku byoroheje kugeza ku bikomeye) cyari hasi cyane mu itsinda rya WM+TCM ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM gusa (7.4% ugereranyije na 46.2%) kandi ubwandu bwari hasi mu itsinda rya WM+TCM ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM gusa (8.8% ugereranyije na 39%).
Nyamara ariko, ubuziranenge n'umutekano wa TCM biracyategereje kugeragezwa neza ku kigero kinini no mu bigo byinshi.
Byari kuba byiza kandi gusobanura uburyo bw'imikorere no gusobanura neza ibice by'ingirakamaro by'imiti ya TCM cyangwa imirwi yabyo niba bishoboka.
Abarwayi bakekwaho cyangwa bemejwe ko barwaye COVID-19 akenshi bagira ubwoba bwinshi bw'iyo ndwara yandura cyane ndetse ishobora no kwica, kandi abantu bari mu kato na bo bagira umunaniro, irungu n'uburakari.
Byongeye kandi, ibimenyetso by'iyo ndwara, urugero nk'umuriro mwinshi, kubura umwuka uhagije mu mubiri no gukorora, hamwe n'ingaruka mbi z'imiti, urugero nk'ibitotsi biterwa na za 'corticosteroids,' bishobora gutuma umuntu arushaho guhangayika no guhangayika.
Mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo cya SARS, hari ibimenyetso byinshi by'indwara zo mu mutwe harimo kwiheba, guhangayika, guhungabana, guhungabana mu mitekerereze, ibimenyetso by'uburwayi bwo mu mutwe, uburwayi bwo kwiyahura.
Gukurikirana no gushyira abantu mu kato, nk'igice cy'ibikorwa byo kurwanya icyorezo cya COVID-19, bishobora gutuma abantu barushaho guhangayika no kwicira urubanza ku ngaruka z'icyorezo, kuba mu kato no gutesha agaciro imiryango yabo n'incuti zabo.
Bityo, abarwayi ba COVID-19, abakekwaho ubwandu n'ababa bahuye na bo, ndetse n'abaturage bose bakeneye ubufasha, bagomba kwitabwaho mu by'ubuzima bwo mu mutwe.
Ubufasha mu by'imitekerereze bugomba kuba bukubiyemo gushyiraho amatsinda y'indwara zo mu mutwe, gutangaza amakuru y'ukuri kandi buri gihe ku ndwara ya SARS-CoV-2 n'uburyo bwo kuyivura, no gukoresha ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki n'ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki kugira ngo hatagira uhuza cyane n'undi.
Inkingo z'ingirakamaro ni ingenzi mu guhagarika uruvange rw'ubwandu kuva mu matungo n'abantu banduye kugera ku bantu barwaye kandi akenshi zikomeza imiti igabanya ubukana bwa virusi mu kurwanya ibyorezo biterwa na virusi nshya.
Hakozwe ingamba zo gukora inkingo zishingiye kuri poroteyine ya S kugira ngo zitange za antibody zidakora kandi zikomeye kandi zidakora ku mubiri cyangwa zirebe ko zirinze SARS-CoV.
Inkingo z'abantu z'ubuzima zisuzuguritse zagiye zisuzumwa mu ngero z'inyamaswa ku ndwara ya SARS.
Icyakora, ingufu za in vivo z'izi nkingo z'abakandida ku bantu bakuze no ku ngero z'abantu bafite ubwandu bw'indwara z'ubwoko butandukanye ndetse n'ubwirinzi bwazo ku ndwara ziterwa n'ubwandu bw'agakoko gatera indwara z'inyamaswa, ntibiramenyekana mbere y'uko hatangira icyigisho cy'ubuvuzi.
Ibi bishobora kuba biterwa n'uko SARS imaze imyaka 17 yarapfuye kandi nta muntu mushya wigeze avurwa kuva icyo gihe.
Ku rundi ruhande, hari abantu bake cyane kandi bagaragara mu buryo butandukanye muri MERS mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, bakagera no mu tundi turere bitewe n'uko mu duce turimo indwara z'ubwoko butandukanye, hari ibyago by'ubwandu bw'inyamaswa.
Uburyo bwo gukingira bwagiye bukoreshwa mu kurwanya MERS hifashishijwe virusi itakoreshejwe, plasmide za ADN, virusi z'ubwoko butandukanye, utunyangingo duto cyane, utunyangingo tumeze nk'utwo virusi n'utundi duce duto tw'indwara tw'ubwoko bumwe na bumwe, kandi bumwe muri bwo bwakozwe mu ngero z'inyamaswa.
Gushyiraho urukingo rw'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 rwiza kandi rwiza ku bantu badafite ubwirinzi ni igikorwa cyihutirwa kandi cy'ingenzi mu kurwanya icyorezo gikomeje.
Icyakora, biragoye gutsinda iki kibazo kubera igihe kirekire (ku kigereranyo cy'amezi 18) gikenewe mu gukora urukingo n'impinduka z'ubwoko bwa CoV.
Nk'indwara nshya, COVID-19 imaze gutangira kugaragaza uburwayi bwayo bwose mu barwayi ibihumbi.
Mu bihe byinshi, abarwayi bashobora gukira buhoro buhoro nta ngaruka mbi.
Icyakora, kimwe na SARS na MERS, COVID-19 ifitanye isano n'ubwandu bwinshi n'urupfu mu barwayi bafite uburwayi bukomeye.
Ku bw'ibyo, kubaka uburyo bwo gusobanura indwara ni ngombwa ku bigo by'ubuvuzi kugira ngo bitange serivisi zabo mu mwanya wa mbere, cyane cyane mu duce tudafite amikoro menshi.
Dushingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe kugeza ubu, ibi bikurikira bishobora kugira ingaruka cyangwa bifitanye isano n'uburwayi bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 (Imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe33):
Imyaka: Imyaka ni yo yari ingenzi cyane mu kugaragaza indwara ya SARS, kandi ni na ko bimeze kuri COVID-19.
COVID-19 yibasiye cyane cyane abantu bari mu kigero cy'imyaka 30-65 aho 47.7% by'abo barwayi bari barengeje imyaka 50 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 8,866 nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Abarwayi basabaga kwitabwaho mu buryo bwihariye bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara ziterwa n'indwara ziterwa n'indwara kandi bari bakuze cyane kurusha abatazifite (ku myaka 66 ugereranyije na 51), ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko imyaka ari yo igaragaza uko abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazaba bameze.
Igitsina: SARS-CoV-2 yanduje abagabo benshi kurusha abagore (0.31/100.000 ugereranyije na 0.27/100.000), nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Indwara n'ibibazo: Abarwayi barwaye COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane bashobora kurwara umutima cyane no kugira ibibazo by'imitsi.
Ibikorwa by'umutima nabyo ni byo byateye urupfu rw'abarwayi ba SARS.
Byatangajwe ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no guhuza na cholangiocytes zifite ACE2-positive, bishobora gutuma impyiko zidakora neza ku barwayi ba COVID-19.
Birakwiriye ko tumenya ko imyaka n'indwara ziterwa na yo bifitanye isano rya bugufi kandi ko bishobora kugira ingaruka ku wundi muntu.
Ibimenyetso bidasanzwe byo muri laboratwari: Umubare wa poroteyine C-reactive (CRP) mu maraso ugaragaza uburemere bw'ubuhumekero cyangwa imvune mu ngingo kandi byatangajwe ko ari ikintu gishobora gutuma indwara idakira, igakira, kandi amaherezo igakira.
Hari kandi n'ibitekerezo by'uko hari isano hagati y'urugero rwa CRP n'uburemere n'uburwayi bwa COVID-19.
Byongeye kandi, urugero rw'isukari (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT), na creatine kinase (CK) rwiyongereye na byo bishobora gufasha mu kumenya uko bigenda.
Ibyo byuma biboneka mu ngingo nyinshi, cyane cyane mu mutima no mu gifu, kandi bikurwaho mu gihe hari imyanya yangiritse.
Ku bw'ibyo, ni byo bimenyetso bisanzwe bigaragaza ko umutima cyangwa impyiko zidakora neza.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi: Radiografi y'igituza n'iterambere ry'ibipimo by'igihe cy'ibimenyetso by'uburwayi bigomba gusuzumwa hamwe n'ibindi bibazo mu kwemeza ingaruka n'ibibazo bya COVID-19.
Gukoresha Steroids: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, Steroids ni imiti igabanya ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri ikoreshwa cyane nk'umuti wunganira mu ndwara zitandura mu kugabanya ubukana bw'ibikomere by'ubuhumekero.
Kubera ko ingano y'indwara ya corticosteroids yari isanzwe ikoreshwa cyane mu barwayi ba SARS barembye, abenshi mu barokotse basanzwemo indwara y'ubuhumekero bw'amaraso (osteonecrose avasculaire) bubatera ubumuga mu buzima bwabo bwose n'ubuzima bubi.
Bityo, mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, za steroid zigomba gukoreshwa mu gipimo gito kandi mu gihe gito ku barwayi ba COVID-19.
Imihangayiko yo mu mutwe: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19, abarwayi benshi bagize imihangayiko idasanzwe kuko akenshi bahoraga mu kato igihe kirekire kandi bafite impungenge nyinshi kandi bakibonera urupfu rw'abagize umuryango wabo ba hafi n'abandi barwayi.
Ni ngombwa cyane gutanga ubujyanama mu by'imitekerereze no kubafasha igihe kirekire kugira ngo aba barwayi basubire mu buzima busanzwe.
Nk'uko ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku mibare y'abaturage bugaragaza, COVID-19 isa n'aho ifite ibimenyetso bitandukanye n'iby'indwara ya SARS.
Uretse kwongera kwiyongera mu nzira y'ubuhumekero yo hasi, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kongera kwiyongera mu nzira y'ubuhumekero yo hejuru kandi igateza ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso mu gihe cy'ubwandu bwo mu ntangiriro, kimwe n'izindi CoV zitera ibicurane bisanzwe.
Ku bw'ibyo, abarwayi banduye mu gihe cya mbere cyangwa mu gihe cyo kwifungura bashobora gukora virusi nyinshi mu bikorwa bya buri munsi, bigatuma kurwanya icyorezo bigorana cyane.
Icyakora, kwanduzanya SARS-CoV byafatwaga nk'aho biba igihe abarwayi barwaye cyane, mu gihe ubwandu bwinshi butari bwaba mu ntangiriro.
Bityo, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho ubu kirakomeye cyane kandi biragoye kugenzura kurusha icyorezo cya SARS.
Muri iki gihe mu Bushinwa hari imihati ikomeye irimo gukorwa harimo gufunga Wuhan n'imijyi ihakikije no gushyira mu kato abaturage hafi ya bose mu rwego rwo guhashya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo ibyo bikorwa byangije cyane ubukungu n'ibindi bice by'igihugu, umubare w'abarwayi bashya uragenda ugabanuka, bigaragaza ko icyorezo cyoroheje.
Igitekerezo cyiza ni uko iki cyorezo kizarangira muri Werurwe, igihe cyo kugabanuka kikazamara amezi 3-4.
