Itsinda ry'Abanyakanada ryatangaje ko SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye mu bipimo byo mu muhogo no mu muhogo by'abarwayi bakize bakava mu bitaro mu byumweru 2 mbere yaho, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko virusi iherutse kumenyekana ishobora kuba icyorezo cy'ibihe bitandukanye nk'icy'ibicurane.
Icyakora, hari ibimenyetso by'uko mu Bushinwa hari icyizere bitewe n'umubare w'abanduye mushya ugabanutse, bigaragaza ko ingamba z'ubu zishobora kuba zarakoreshejwe.
Mu mizo ya mbere, byahanuwe ko Ebola yari kuzateza abantu bagera kuri miriyoni imwe, naho abagera kuri miriyoni imwe bagapfa.
Icyakora, binyuriye mu gushyira abantu mu kato kandi bakabatandukanya n'abandi, amaherezo icyo cyorezo cyaje kugenzurwa.
Birashoboka ko kimwe na SARS-CoV, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugabanuka mu kwanduzanya kandi amaherezo ikaza gupfa cyangwa ikavamo virusi idashobora gutera indwara ikorana n'abantu.
Gereranya icyorezo cya COVID-19 n'icy'indwara ya SARS na MERS (Igishushanyo cya 55)
SARS-CoV-2 yandura cyane binyuze mu gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura, kandi wenda binyuze mu guhura mu buryo butaziguye n'ibikoresho byanduye virusi.
Iyi virusi kandi yasanzwe mu busa, ibyo bikaba bituma habaho uburyo bushya bwo kwanduzanya binyuze mu busa no mu kanwa.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa ku barwayi 138 bwagaragaje ko 41% by'abo barwayi bashobora kuba baraterwaga n'indwara z'ibyorezo, harimo abarwayi 17 barwaye izindi ndwara mbere n'abakozi 40 b'ubuzima.
Ku bw'ibyo, abantu bagombye kwitondera cyane kugira ngo barinde abandi, cyane cyane abaganga, abakozi b'imiryango, abagize umuryango, abo bakorana, ndetse n'abari hafi aho bagirana imishyikirano n'abarwayi cyangwa abanduye.
Uburyo bwa mbere bwo kwirinda bushobora gukoreshwa mu kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura ni ukwambara udupfukamunwa; gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi n'udupfukamunwa tw'ubwoko bwa N95 (urukurikirane # 1860s) bifasha mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Udupfukamunwa tw'ubwonko dukoreshwa mu kubaga turinda ibitonyanga by'amazi biva ku muntu ushobora kuba yanduye guhita mu kirere cyangwa kwibanda ku bintu, aho bishobora kwandurira abandi.
Icyakora, udupfukamunwa twa N95 (urukurikirane # 1860s) ni two gusa dushobora kurinda umuntu guhumeka virions ntoya cyane iri hagati ya 10 na 80 nm, aho 5% gusa bya virions ari zo zishobora kwinjira burundu; SARS-CoV-2 isa na SARS-CoV mu bunini kandi zombi ziri hafi 85 nm.
Kubera ko uduhimba dushobora kwinjira no mu masike eshanu z'ubuvuzi ziteretse hamwe, abavura bagirana imishyikirano y'ibanze n'abarwayi bagomba kwambara masike za N95 (ingingo ya #1860s) ariko ntibagire masike z'ubuvuzi.
Uretse udupfukamunwa, abaganga bagomba kwambara imyenda yo kwicungira kugira ngo barusheho kugabanya guhura n'ubwandu bw'indwara.
Virusi zishobora no kwanduza umuntu binyuze mu maso.
Ku ya 22 Mutarama 2020, umuganga yanduye SARS-CoV-2 nubwo yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95; virusi ishobora kuba yarinjiye mu mubiri we binyuze mu maso ye arwaye.
Ku bw'ibyo, abaganga bagomba no kwambara udukingirizo tw'amaso cyangwa uturindantoki mu gihe bakorana n'abarwayi.
Ku baturage muri rusange bari mu duce twanduye cyangwa dushobora kwandura, byasabwe cyane ko buri wese yoza intoki ze akoresheje isabune yica udukoko kenshi, akagerageza kuguma mu nzu mu gihe yiherereye kandi agabanya guhura n'abantu bashobora kwandura.
Abantu bagomba kwirinda umurwayi mu gihe bamaze metero eshatu.
Ibyo bikorwa ni uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura ndetse no gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
