Impinduka n'ihinduka ry'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byatumye virusi ya corona (CoV) n'ibinyabuzima byayirwaye, harimo n'abantu, bifatanya mu kwihinduriza mu myaka ibihumbi n'ibihumbi.
Mbere ya 2003, hari abantu babiri bafite CoVs (HCoVs) bazwiho gutera indwara zidakomeye, nk'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye (SARS) n'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) byahinduye ibintu bigaragaza ukuntu ubwandu bwa HCoV bushobora guteza akaga kandi bugashyira ubuzima mu kaga.
Igiterwa cya SARS-CoV-2 mu Bushinwa bwo hagati mu mpera za 2019 cyongeye gushyira CoV mu mucyo kandi kidutangaza kubera ubwandu bwayo buhambaye ariko bugabanya ubwandu ugereranyije na SARS-CoV.
Kwandura HCoV ni indwara iterwa n'inyamaswa kandi gusobanukirwa inkomoko y'indwara iterwa n'inyamaswa ya HCoV byadufasha cyane.
HCoVs nyinshi zakomotse ku ducurama aho zitatera indwara.
Imiti ikingira imwe muri izo HCoV na yo irazwi.
Kumenya inyamaswa z'inyamaswa bifite ingaruka ku burinzi bw'indwara z'abantu.
Gushakisha imikoranire ya CoV n'inyamaswa bishobora no gutanga ibisobanuro by'ingenzi ku ndwara ya CoV mu bantu.
Muri iyi raporo, turatanga isesengura ry'ubumenyi buriho ku ndwara zirindwi za HCoV, twibanda ku mateka y'aho zavumbuwe ndetse n'inkomoko yazo n'ubwandu bw'ubwoko.
Icy'ingenzi ni uko tugereranya kandi tukagaragaza itandukaniro hagati ya za HCoV zitandukanye duhereye ku iterambere rya virusi no kongera guhuza ibinyabuzima.
Icyorezo cy'indwara ya CoV 2019 (COVID-19) kiri kuvugwa muri iyi nkuru.
Byongeye kandi, ibisabwa kugira ngo impinduka z'abanduye zigende neza n'ingaruka z'ihindagurika rya virusi ku buremere bw'indwara na zo ziragaragazwa.
Coronaviruses (CoVs) ni zo zigize umuryango wa Coronaviridae, ugizwe n'itsinda ry'udukoko twa RNA tw'uruhu rumwe, tw'imiterere myiza.
Izi virusi zifite genome nini cyane iri hagati ya kilobase 26 na 32 mu virusi za RNA ziswe CoVs kubera imiterere yazo imeze nk'ikamba mu cyuma cya elegitoronike.
Mu miterere, CoV zifite genome zitari zashyizwe mu bice bitandukanye, zifite gahunda imwe.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu bya genome birimo ibipimo bibiri binini byanditseho (ORF1a na ORF1b), bihindurwa muri pp1a na pp1ab replicase polyproteins.
Izi poroteyine nyinshi zikomeza gutunganywa kugira ngo zitange poroteyine 16 zitari iz'imiterere, zitwa nsp1~16.
Igice gisigaye cya jenome kirimo ORFs kuri poroteyine z'imiterere, harimo spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) na nucleoprotein (N).
Poroteyine nyinshi z'inyongera zigena ubwoko bwa CoV na zo zigaragazwa n'ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoV.
Dushingiye ku itandukaniro riri mu miterere ya poroteyine, CoVs zigizwe n'imiryango ine (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV), muri yo, beta-CoV irimo HCoVs nyinshi kandi igabanyijemo imiryango ine (A, B, C na D).
Ibihamya bya phylogenetic byerekana ko udusimba n'udukoko dukonjesha ari byo bitanga ibinyabuzima byinshi bya alpha-CoV na beta-CoV, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zitanga cyane ibinyabuzima bya gamma-CoV na delta-CoV.
Mu myaka ibihumbi, CoVs zakomeje kunyura ku nzitizi z'ubwoko kandi zimwe muri zo zigize udukoko dukomeye two mu bantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana abantu barindwi bafite CoV (HCoVs).
Muri zo harimo HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ni alpha-CoVs.
Izindi beta-CoV eshanu zirimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, coronavirus y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS-CoV), coronavirus y'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS-CoV) na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 akenshi zitera ibimenyetso byoroheje, nk'ibicurane n'igifu.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 iherutse kumenyekana ni indwara zandura cyane, zitera indwara zikomeye z'ubuhumekero bwo hasi mu barwayi benshi cyane bafite amahirwe menshi yo kugira indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye ubwoba (ARDS) n'ibimenyetso byo hanze y'ibihaha.
