Kuva icyo gihe, ubumenyi bwinshi bwarakwirakwijwe binyuze mu bushakashatsi bwimbitse kuri HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi bitera ibimenyetso byigaragaza.
Mu by'ukuri, igitekerezo cyakiriwe cyane ko kwandura HCoV muri rusange nta ngaruka kugeza igihe SARS yadutse.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye mu 2003 ni kimwe mu byateje akaga gakomeye mu mateka y'iki gihe, cyandura abantu barenga 8,000, n'umubare w'abapfa ugera kuri 10%.
