Mu yandi magambo, byombi bishobora kuba byararokotse ibyorezo bya kera bya HCoV.
HCoV zitera indwara zikomeye ku bantu n'abantu bagaragaje indwara zikomeye za HCoV zarakemutse.
Kugira ngo ibyo bibe, HCoV zigomba kwiyongera mu bantu ku buryo buhagije kugira ngo zemererwe kwiyongera kw'impinduka z'imiterere z'imiterere zangiza ibintu by'ingenzi bigabanya ingano y'abanduye.
Muri ubwo buryo, uko igihe kirekire icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kigumaho n'abantu benshi cyandura, ni na ko bishoboka ko cyakira abantu.
Iyo yifashe neza, kwandura kwayo ku bantu byaba bigoye guhagarika binyuze mu gushyirwa mu kato cyangwa mu bindi bikorwa byo kurwanya ubwandu.
Mu myaka myinshi, izo CoV enye z'abantu zagiye zikwirakwira mu bantu, zitera ibicurane mu bantu bafite ubumuga.
Izo virusi ntizikeneye ikigega cy'inyamaswa.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV ziteje indwara cyane ntizihuza n'abantu neza kandi ntizishobora gukomeza kwanduzwa mu bantu.
Bakeneye gukomeza no kwiyongera mu bigega byabo by'indwara z'ibikoko no gushaka amahirwe yo gukwirakwira ku bantu bashobora kwibasirwa, bishoboka ko binyuze mu nyamaswa imwe cyangwa nyinshi z'inyamaswa z'inyamaswa z'inyamaswa.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite ibintu bisa na SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV ndetse na HCoVs enye z'abaturage.
Ni indwara yandura cyane nk'iyo mu baturage, nibura muri iki gihe.
Icyakora, ni indwara zandura cyane kurusha HCoVs ziterwa n'abaturage kandi zandura gake kurusha SARS-CoV cyangwa MERS-CoV.
Biracyari kugenzurwa niba izagera ku bantu burundu kandi igakwirakwira mu bantu nta kintu kibungabunga cyangwa inyamaswa z'inyamaswa.
Mbere yo kuganira ku nkomoko y'inyamaswa za HCoV, bizadufasha kuganira ku bisobanuro n'ibiranga abanduye ba HCoV mu buryo bw'ubwihindurize, ibidukikije, ibigega, abahuza n'ababyongera.
Inyamaswa ikora nk'inyamaswa y'ubwihindurize ya HCoV iyo ifite umwuzukuru ifitanye isano ya bugufi ifitanye isano ya bugufi ku rwego rwa nucleotide.
Virusi y'umwuzukuru ubusanzwe ihinduka neza kandi ntabwo iteza indwara muri uyu muyobozi.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, ikigega cy'indwara cyakira HCoV mu buryo buhoraho kandi bw'igihe kirekire.
Muri ibyo bihe byombi, abanduye banduye mu buryo bw'ibanze kandi ni bo bakira HCoV cyangwa virusi y'ababyeyi bayo.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, iyo HCoV iherutse kwanduzwa n'umuntu ugenga mbere gato y'uko igera ku bantu cyangwa mu gihe ikimukikije, ntiyihutira guhura n'uwo muntu mushya kandi akenshi iba ishobora gutera indwara.
Uyu mubyimba wa intermédiaire ushobora kuba isoko y'ubwandu bw'abantu kandi ukagira uruhare mu gutuma virusi yiyongera mu buryo buhoraho hanyuma ikajya ku bantu kugira ngo yongere ubwandu bw'abantu.
HCoV ishobora kwandura indwara idakira mu gihe idashobora gukomeza kwanduzwa n'undi muntu uyirwaye.
Ahubwo, HCoVs zishobora no kwihuza n'inyamaswa z'inyamaswa z'inyamaswa z'inyamaswa kandi zigashyiraho ubwandu bw'igihe kirekire.
Muri iki gihe, nyir'ubwite wa kabiri ahinduka nyir'ubwite w'ibikoresho.
Amakuru y'ubuvuzi bw'indwara yagaragaje nyuma ko umuntu wanduye SARS yari afite amateka y'imibonano n'inyamaswa zo mu ishyamba.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe nyuma y'aho ku bijyanye n'ubwandu bwa virusi bwagaragaje ko abacuruza amatungo bafite umubare munini w'abanduye IgG barwanya SARS-CoV ugereranyije n'abatuye isi muri rusange.
Ibinyamushongo byo mu bwoko bwa palm civet (Paguma larvata) n'imbwa ya racoon mu masoko y'inyamaswa z'abazima byamenyekanye bwa mbere ko bitwara virusi zisa na SARS-CoV zisa na SARS-CoV.
Ibi byashyigikiwe mu buryo butaziguye n'uko nta kindi SARS cyatangajwe nyuma yo kwica ibinyamanswa byose mu masoko.
Icyakora, byavuzwe ko inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa palm civet zitwikiriye mu maso zo mu gasozi cyangwa mu mirima zitagurishwa mu masoko y'inyamaswa nzima zagize ingaruka mbi cyane kuri SARS-CoV, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa palm civet zitwikiriye mu maso zishobora kuba ari zo zonyine zituma SARS-CoV ikomeza kubaho, ariko ko atari zo zituma ikwirakwira.
By'umwihariko, kubera ko 80% by'inyamaswa zitandukanye ziri ku masoko yo mu mujyi wa Guangzhou zifite za antibody zihangana na SARS-CoV, ntibishoboka ko amoko menshi y'inyamaswa zifite ibibyimba bito ashobora no kuba ari zo zinyuranye zikomeza SARS-CoV.
Ibi byose bisa n'aho ari ibifite SARS-CoV.
Ubushakashatsi bwakurikiyeho ku nyamaswa z'ibanze z'inyamaswa za SARS-CoV bwagaragaje ko hari ubwoko bwa CoV bw'ingwe bufitanye isano ya bugufi, bwitwa SARS-related Rhinolophus bat CoV HKU3 (SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3), iboneka mu nguge z'ibishishwa by'amafarashi zo mu Bushinwa.
Izi mpiri zifite ibimenyetso by'indwara z'agakoko gatera SIDA (SARS-CoV) n'imiterere y'urusobe rwazo rwa SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3.
Iyi n'izindi CoV z'ingurube zifite 88-92% by'imiterere y'imiterere ya nucleotide ihuriyeho na SARS-CoV.
Ibyo byigwa byashyizeho urufatiro rw'igitekerezo gishya cy'uko udukoko two mu bwoko bw'imbeba dutera indwara duhora tuvuka.
Hariho CoVs nyinshi zisa na SARS (SL-CoVs) na zo zigeze kumenyekana mu ducurama, ariko nta n'imwe uretse imwe yitwa WIV1 ishobora gutandukanywa nk'indwara nzima.
Ingirabuzimafatizo ihindura angiotensin mu muntu 2 (ACE2) izwiho kuba ari yo ifata SARS-CoV.
WIV1 yakuwe mu kimenyetso cy'ibinure by'imbeba yagaragaye ko ikoresha ACE2 y'imbeba, iy'inyoni n'iy'umuntu nk'urwego rw'ibinure mu kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Igishishikaje ni uko ibipimo by'abafite SARS bari bamaze gukira, byashoboye kuvanaho virusi ya WIV1.
Kugeza ubu, WIV1 ni yo nkomoko ya SARS-CoV ifitanye isano ya hafi cyane n'imbeba, ikaba ifite homologie y'urusobe rwa nucleotide ingana na 95%.
Nubwo hari isano ikomeye hagati y'izi virusi zombi, muri rusange abantu bemera ko WIV1 atari virusi y'ababyeyi ya SARS-CoV kandi ko udusimba atari yo nyir'ubwite wa SARS-CoV.
Ubushakashatsi ku miterere y'ibinyabuzima buhuza MERS-CoV n'itsinda rimwe na CoV-HKU4 n'irindi rya CoV-HKU5.
Virusi ya CoV-HKU4 n'iya MERS-CoV z'ingurube zikoresha receptor imwe, dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4), mu kwinjira kwa virusi.
Urutonde rwa RNA polymerase rw'ubwoko bwa RNA rw'ubwoko bwa MERS-CoV rushingiye kuri RNA, mu buryo bw'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima, rwegereye cyane abangana na beta-CoVs z'urukoba zatoraguwe mu Burayi no muri Afurika.
Kugeza ubu, nta MERS-CoV nzima ishobora kuboneka mu ducurama tw'inyamaswa.
MERS-CoV na CoV-HKU25 ya mudubu ifitanye isano ya hafi na yo, ifitanye isano ya 87% gusa n'indi.
Bityo, udukoko dushobora kuba tutari ibigega by'ubwirinzi bwa MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubushakashatsi bwakorewe mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati bwagaragaje ko ingamiya z'ingore zifite virusi itera indwara ya MERS-CoV, kimwe n'ingamiya zo mu bihugu byinshi bya Afurika.
MERS-CoV nzima isa n'iyo mu bantu yabonetse mu byuma byo mu mazuru by'ingamiya z'ingamiya, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko ingamiya ari zo zigize iyi virusi.
Birashishikaje kandi ko ibimenyetso byoroheje ariko virusi nyinshi zasheshe byagaragaye mu ngamiya zanduye MERS-CoV mu buryo bw'igerageza.
Ni ngombwa ko tumenya ko ingamiya zanduye zitandura binyuze mu nzira y'ubuhumekero gusa, ahubwo nanone binyuze mu nzira y'umuhogo n'umunwa, ari na yo nzira y'ibanze ituma ingirabuzimafatizo zituruka ku birondwe.
Icyakora, ibibazo biracyariho kuko abantu benshi banduye MERS batigeze bahura n'ingamiya mbere y'uko bagaragaza ibimenyetso, bikaba byashoboka ko byatewe n'ubwandu bw'abantu cyangwa inzira zitamenyekanye z'ubwandu ziterwa n'inyamaswa zitamenyekanye zanduye MERS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite 96.2% ya nucleotide ihuriyeho na CoV RaTG13 ya mu bwoko bw'ingona yavuye mu bwoko bwa Rhinolophus affinis.
Nk'uko bimeze kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, itandukaniro ry'imiterere hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 ni rinini cyane ku buryo nta mubano w'ababyeyi ushobora gushyirwaho.
Ni ukuvuga ko udukoko dushobora kuba tutari two tugenga SARS-CoV-2 keretse mu gihe cya vuba aha habonetse udukoko tumeze nkaho.
Birashoboka ko inyamaswa z'ibice by'ibanze z'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 zigomba kuba ziri mu nyamaswa z'inyamaswa zigurishwa kandi zicirwa ku isoko rya Huanan ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja, aho abenshi mu banduye COVID-19 ba mbere baherekejwe, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko bishoboka ko hari ikinyamaswa cyanduza abantu.
Ubushakashatsi butandukanye buherutse gukorwa bushingiye ku gupima metagenome bwagaragaje ko itsinda ry'inyamaswa z'ibinyabuzima ntoya ziri mu kaga ziswe ingona (Manis javanica) zishobora no kuba zirimo beta-CoVs z'abasekuruza zifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2.
Izi genome nshya za CoV ya pangolin zifite 85-92% ya homologie y'urusobe rwa nucleotide na SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko kandi, bifitanye isano ya bugufi na RaTG13 hamwe na 90% by'ubwoko ku rwego rwa nucleotide.
Zishyira hamwe mu bwoko bubiri bw'ubwoko bw'indwara zisa na SARS-CoV-2 mu giti cy'ibinyabuzima, imwe muri zo ifite uruvange rw'indwara zisa na SARS-CoV-2 (RBD) zifite 97.4% by'urusobe rwa aside.
Mu buryo bunyuranye cyane, RBD za SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 ziratandukanye cyane, nubwo zigaragaza igipimo cyo hejuru cy'imiterere y'urusobe rw'ibinyabuzima mu bwoko bwose.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe ku nyamaswa z'ibinyamanswa zirwaye bwagaragaje kandi ko hari udukoko twanduza virusi twabonetse mu bipimo by'ibihaha, bikaba byaragaragaye ko dufitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2.
Ubu bushakashatsi bwakoresheje uburyo butandukanye bwo gukusanya no gucunga intoki kugira ngo haboneke urutonde rw'igice cya jenome rugizwe na 86.3% by'igihimba cya virusi cyose.
Ntidushobora guca ukubiri n'uko ingona ari imwe mu nyamaswa z'inyamaswa z'inzobere mu kwanduza SARS-CoV-2.
Icyakora, muri iki gihe nta gihamya igaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse ku nyamaswa yitwa pangolin bitewe n'ubwumvikane buke hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na beta-CoVs zifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2.
Byongeye kandi, intera iri hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 ni nto cyane ugereranyije n'iri hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na beta-CoVs zifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2 z'inyamaswa zitwa pangolin.
Inzira y'ubwihindurize bwa SARS-CoV-2 mu ducurama, mu bifi n'ibindi binyabuzima biracyari gushyirwaho.
Mu gihe homologie y'urusobe rw'ibinyabuzima iri hejuru cyane y'iy'ibinyabuzima bya RBDs yagaragaye hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na pangolin, beta-CoVs ifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2, SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 zifite homologie y'urusobe rw'ibinyabuzima iri hejuru cyane.
Birashoboka cyane ko urugero rwagutse rw'ubusabane hagati ya RBDs ya pangolin SARS-CoV-2-related beta-CoVs na SARS-CoV-2 biterwa n'ihinduka ry'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima riterwa n'amahitamo.
Igitekerezo cy'uko habaho kongera guhuza beta-CoV ifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2 ya pangolin na RaTG13 mu bwoko bwa gatatu bw'inyamaswa zo mu gasozi.
Nk'ingufu ituma habaho ubwihindurize, kongera guhuriza hamwe biriho cyane mu bwoko bwa beta-CoV.
Urubanza ruracyakomeje ku nkomoko ya SARS-CoV-2 ituruka ku nyamaswa.
Uretse HCoVs zifite ubwandu bwinshi, hasuzumwe inkomoko y'ubwoko bw'inyamaswa ya HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-NL63 na HCoV-HKU1.
Ibihamya by'ibinyabuzima byerekana ko HCoV-NL63 na HCoV-229E byombi bishobora kuba byaturutse kuri CoVs z'ingurube, mu gihe virusi z'ababyeyi za HCoV-OC43 na HCoV-HKU1 zisanzwe ziboneka mu binyabuzima.
Hari amakuru avuga ko CoV y'ikinyugunyugu yitwa ARCoV.2 (Appalachian Ridge CoV) yagaragaye mu kinyugunyugu cy'amabara atatu cyo muri Amerika ya Ruguru yagaragaje isano ya bugufi na HCoV-NL63.
Ku rundi ruhande, HCoV-229E yari ifitanye isano mu buryo bw'imiterere n'indi CoV y'ikinyugunyugu, yitwa Hipposideros/GhanaKwam/19/2008, yagaragaye muri Ghana, mu gihe kandi hari abakekwaho kuba ari ingamiya.
Kugira ngo byumvikane neza, ubumenyi buriho ku nkomoko y'inyamaswa za HCoV zizwi, bwasuzumwe mu ishusho ya 1 n'itabula ya 2.
Isesengura ry'ibinyabuzima ryatumye haboneka ibimenyetso by'uko HCoVs zigeze kwanduzwa mu bwoko butandukanye.
Igihe HCoV-OC43 yanyuraga mu bwoko bugatera abantu mu matungo yo mu ngo ahagana mu 1890, havutse icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Amateka y'ubwandu bw'indwara ya HCoV-229E hagati y'amoko ntabwo asobanutse neza.
Hasanzwe alpha-CoVs z'ingwe zifitanye isano ya bugufi na HCoV-229E.
Hagati yabo hari alpha-CoV ya alpaca.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi bishyigikira ko virusi ishobora kwanduzwa n'imbeba igera ku bantu.
Icya mbere, abantu ariko si alpacas bashobora kuba bahuye n'imbeba mu gace k'ibidukikije bahuriyeho.
Ahubwo abantu bagirana imishyikirano ya bugufi n'izo nyamaswa.
Icya kabiri, alpha-CoVs z'ingona zifitanye isano na HCoV-229E ziratandukanye kandi ntizitera indwara mu ngona, mu gihe alpha-CoV ya alpaca yatumye indwara z'ubuhumekero zitangira mu matungo yanduye.
Amaherezo, alpaca alpha-CoV ntiyabonetse mu nyamaswa zo mu gasozi.
Bityo, ntibishoboka ko alpaca yavana alpha-CoV ifitanye isano na HCoV-229E ku bantu.
Mu by'ukuri, udukoko ni two dukwirakwiza virusi zandura abantu, harimo virusi ya rabies, Ebola, Nipah na Hendra.
Ku bw'ibyo, ntibitangaje cyane ko udusimba dushobora kwanduza abantu HCoV-229E mu buryo butaziguye.
Ubundi, mu gihe alpha-CoVs z'ingwe zikora nk'ibikoresho bya HCoV-229E, alpaca na dromedary camels zishobora gukora nk'abashyitsi bo hagati batanga virusi ku bantu, nk'uko byagenze kuri MERS-CoV.
MERS-CoV ni urugero rwiza rw'ubwandu bw'ubwoko butandukanye buturuka ku ducurama bugera ku ngamiya z'ingore no ku ngamiya z'ingore bugera ku bantu.
Inkomoko y'ubwihindurize bwa MERS-CoV mu ducurama yari izwi igihe yamenyekanaga bwa mbere kandi kandi yakomejwe n'ibyaje kugaragara nyuma yaho.
Biragaragara ko udukoko dutanga ubwoko bwinshi bw'indwara kugira ngo abantu bahindure utuntu duto tw'ibinyabuzima, kandi ngo tubashe kwanduzanya.
Ubuzima burebure, gutura mu duce twinshi, guhura neza n'abandi no kugira ubushobozi bwo kuguruka, ni ibintu byiza bituma udusimba tuba "abanduza virusi".
Ku rundi ruhande, MERS-CoV imaze imyaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo igaragara ku ngamiya z'ingore.
Iyo ngamiya ni yo ihinduka cyane, kuko iba ifite ubushobozi bwo kuba mu mazi.
MERS-CoV ituma indwara iba nke cyane kandi igakomeza kugira igipimo cyo guhinduka gike muri izi nyamaswa.
Kwandura kwayo mu buryo budasanzwe ku bantu ni impanuka kandi abantu bakomeza kuba abaterwa na MERS-CoV kuko kuyandura kwayo bidashobora gukomeza.
Bitandukanye n'uruhare rw'ingamiya mu kwanduzanya MERS-CoV, uruhare rwa pangolin, niba rubaho, mu kwanduzanya SARS-CoV-2 rutandukanye.
By'umwihariko, beta-CoVs za pangolin zifite ubukana bukomeye mu nguge.
