Ku bw'ibyo, ntibishoboka gutamba ingamiya zose mu rwego rwo kurwanya MERS, nk'uko byagiye bikorwa mu masoko y'inyamaswa zo mu gasozi mu Bushinwa mu kwirinda ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2.
Kugira ngo hahagarikwe ibyorezo bya MERS bikomeza kugaragara, hagomba gufatwa ingamba z'ubushakashatsi mu gukora inkingo z'ingirakamaro zo kurwanya MERS-CoV ku ngamiya, hamwe n'ibindi bikorwa byo kurwanya ubwandu.
Kubera ko tudashobora kurandura izi virusi, hari igihe haboneka ubwoko bushya bw'iyo virusi butuma habaho ibyorezo.
Hari ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoV ziterwa n'ibinyabuzima mu ishyamba.
By'umwihariko, CoV z'imbeba zifite ubushobozi bwo gutera indwara z'ibikoko ni nyinshi cyane.
Hari amahirwe menshi ko izi CoV ziterwa n'inyamaswa zishobora kwiyongera no kongera kwihuza, bigatuma habaho CoV nshya zishobora kwanduzwa cyane cyangwa zikaba zangiza abantu mu gihe kizaza.
Umuco wo kurya inyamaswa zo mu gasozi mu duce tumwe na tumwe tw'u Bushinwa wagombye gucibwa kugira ngo abantu n'inyamaswa badakomeza guhura bitari ngombwa.
Kubera ibigeragezo bya SARS, MERS na COVID-19, hagombye gushyirwaho gahunda nziza yo kwitegura no guhangana na byo.
Mu by'ukuri, hari virusi nyinshi zimaze igihe kirekire cyane ku isi.
Ziguma mu bigega byazo bwite kugeza igihe habonekeye uburyo bwo kwanduzanya.
Nubwo udusimba dufite ibintu byinshi bituma twandura, abantu bashobora kugabanya amahirwe yo guhura n'udusimba n'utundi dukoko mu gihe abantu bigishijwe kutagendana na two.
Kugenzura by'igihe cyose mu nyamaswa zifata inda ni ngombwa kugira ngo dusobanukirwe neza imiterere y'ubutaka bwa CoVs n'ibinyabuzima by'ibanze byayo, bizagaragaza ko ari ingirakamaro mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'inyamaswa ku bantu n'iz'ibindi byorezo mu gihe kizaza.
Mu gusoza, uburyo bwiza bwo kwirinda indwara y'ubwandu bw'ibinyabuzima ni uko abantu bakomeza kwirinda ahantu habigenewe, aho virusi z'ubwandu bw'ibinyabuzima ziba.
Ibice byinshi by'urujijo rw'inkomoko ya SARS-CoV-2 biterwa n'ubwoko bw'inyamaswa biracyariho.
Icya mbere, niba udusimba twohereje virusi y'umwuzukuru wa SARS-CoV-2 ku bifi byo mu bwoko bwa pangolin, bizashimisha kureba mu bihe udusimba n'ibifi byo mu bwoko bwa pangolin bishobora kubamo ahantu hamwe.
Icya kabiri, niba udusimba tugira uruhare rugaragara mu kwanduzanya n'abantu, uburyo abantu bagirana imibonano n'udusimba ni bwo bukwiye gusuzumwa.
Icya gatatu, niba inyamaswa y'inkazi ya gatatu ikora nk'inyamaswa y'inyamaswa y'inyamaswa y'inyamaswa y'inyamaswa, uburyo ikorana n'ubwoko butandukanye harimo abantu, udusimba n'inyamaswa z'ibinyamanswa bigomba gusobanuka.
Amaherezo, kubera ko inyamaswa nyinshi zirya ibinyamubiri harimo n'iz'imbere mu rugo zishobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2, hakwiye gukorwa igenzura n'igerageza ry'ubwandu.
Niba ari udukoko, ingunzu cyangwa ikindi gikoko cy'inyamaswa, byitezwe ko SARS-CoV-2 cyangwa virusi z'ababyeyi bayo zimeze kimwe na zo zizagaragara mu bakiriye mu buryo bw'ibanze mu gihe kizaza.
Ibikorwa byo gukomeza gukora iperereza muri aka gace bizagaragaza inzira y'ubwihindurize bwa SARS-CoV-2 mu matungo, bigira ingaruka zikomeye mu gukumira no kurwanya COVID-19 mu bantu.
Guhindura ibipimo byo gupima COVID-19 ubwandu bikekwaho  n'ubwandu bwemejwe birakenewe
Ku itariki ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryasohoye amabwiriza yihuse yo gutanga inama ku bijyanye no gusuzuma no kuvura ubwandu bwa coronavirus nshya yo mu mwaka wa 2019 (2019-nCoV), kandi aya mabwiriza yatangaga ubunararibonye bwacu kandi agatanga umurongo mwiza wo kurwanya iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Icyakora, indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara nshya, ubumenyi n'ubumenyi dufite bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ibyagezweho mu buvuzi; bityo rero, ingamba zo gusuzuma no kuvura na zo zikomeza kuvugururwa.
Muri iyi baruwa, twashubije igitekerezo kimwe ku mabwiriza yacu kandi dutanga ibipimo bishya byo gupima ubwandu bukekwaho kuba n'ubundi ubwandu bwemejwe dukurikije amabwiriza mashya yo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 (verisiyo ya karindwi) yatanzwe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Abanyamerika.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV) yateje icyorezo, ubu cyitwa coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) ku mugaragaro kandi virusi yitwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yagaragaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryakoze amabwiriza yihuse yo gutanga inama kandi yasohotse kuri interineti mu bushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi bwa gisirikare ku ya 06 Gashyantare 2020.
Kuva icyo gitabo cyasohoka, abantu benshi baracyitayeho.
Ariko kandi, zirikana ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi n'ubumenyi dufite bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ibyagezweho mu buvuzi; bityo rero, ingamba zo gusuzuma no kuvura na zo zikomeza kuvugururwa.
Urugero, amabwiriza yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 yatanzwe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Abashinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), hagati ya 16 Mutarama 2020 na 3 Werurwe 2020, yasohoye impapuro zirindwi zose hamwe n'ibindi bintu byahinduwe cyane.
Ubu ubuyobozi bwacu bwahawe ibitekerezo na Zhou et al., batanze igitekerezo cyoroshye cyo gutanga amanota gishingiye ku buhanga bwabo mu buvuzi.
Akazi kabo kongereye ibimenyetso bishya ku mabwiriza yacu kandi kandi ni ingirakamaro cyane kuri iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Twishimira umurimo w'ingenzi bakora kandi turabashimira.
Icyakora, umurimo wabo ukeneye kandi kuvugururwa ukurikije amabwiriza mashya yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (igerageza rya karindwi) n'inyigo ziherutse gukorwa.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu gitabo cya karindwi (3 Werurwe 2020), kugira ngo umuntu akomeze kuba umuganga, bisaba ko habaho ikintu kimwe mu bintu by'amateka y'icyorezo hamwe n'ibintu bibiri by'ibimenyetso byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi kugira ngo haboneke isesengura ryuzuye, cyangwa se bisaba ko habaho ibintu bitatu by'ibimenyetso byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi niba nta mateka y'icyorezo asobanutse:
Amateka y'indwara: (1) amateka y'urugendo cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu bice biyikikije, cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho abantu banduye COVID-19 bari bamaze iminsi 14 batangiye kugaragaza ibimenyetso; (2) amateka y'abamenyanye n'abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 (bakoze ikizamini cya nucleic acid cyemeza ko banduye); (3) amateka y'abamenyanye n'abarwayi barwaye umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu bice biyikikije, cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho COVID-19 yari imaze iminsi 14 itangiye kugaragara; (4) amateka y'abamenyanye n'itsinda ry'abantu banduye (≥ abantu 2 barwaye umuriro n'ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero mu byumweru 2 mu duce duto, nko mu rugo, mu biro, mu ishuri, n'ibindi).
Ibimenyetso by'uburwayi: (1) umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero; (2) ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) umubare w'utugingo duto duto tw'amaraso ugaragaza ko ingirabuzimafatizo zisanzwe, zagabanutse cyangwa zagabanutse mu gihe cy'itangira.
Gushakisha umuntu wemejwe ko yanduye bigomba gushingira ku muntu ukekwaho ubwandu ufite ibimenyetso by'ubwandu cyangwa ibipimo by'amaraso nk'ibi bikurikira: (1) ibipimo bya PCR mu gihe nyacyo bigaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ari yo; (2) ukurikirana kwa virusi yose igaragaza ko ari imwe mu ndwara z'ubwoko bushya z'agakoko ka koronavirusi; (3) ibimenyetso bya IgM n'iby'umubiri wa IgG mu gusuzuma SARS-CoV-2 mu iseru; cyangwa impinduka y'umubiri wa IgG ugaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ari yo, cyangwa se igipimo cy'umuriro cyongereyeho inshuro ≥4 mu gihe cyo gukira kurusha mu gihe cy'indwara ikaze.
Turabona ko ibizamini bya PCR mu gihe nyacyo bya nucleic acid mu nzira y'ubuhumekero cyangwa ibipimo by'amaraso byongerewe ku nshuro ya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) n'iya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020).
Igishushanyo cy'amaraso cyerekana indwara cyongerewe mu cyiciro cya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); hanyuma ibimenyetso bya seroloji byongerwa mu cyiciro cya karindwi.
Izi mpinduka zishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakomeje gukora kugira ngo bashake ibikoresho byiza byo gupima aside ya nucleic kugirango bagaragaze vuba, kimwe n'ibipimo byo mu nzira y'ubuhumekero harimo no gufata ibipimo by'amaraso, byongereye iboneka ry'ibipimo bitandukanye, kandi byashyigikiye kuzana igisubizo cyiza cya antibody mu bipimo byemejwe.
Uretse n'ibyo, hari ibimenyetso byinshi bitwibutsa kwitonda ku barwayi badasanzwe bafite ibimenyetso n'abadafite ibimenyetso.
Ku bw'ibyo, urutonde rw'ibanze rwa Zhou et al. rugomba kuvugururwa, kuko bashyize mu cyiciro cy'umuntu udafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi nk'umuntu ufite ibyago bike.
Ubwo buryo bwo gutanga amanota na bwo bukeneye kwemezwa mu bindi bikorwa by'ubuvuzi no mu bushakashatsi.
Mu gusoza, twizeye ko hari ibindi bimenyetso bizagaragara kandi dusaba abasomyi gutanga ibitekerezo byabo.
Ku gusuzuma ubwandu bukekwa n'ubundi bwiyemejwe, turasaba gukurikirana no kubahiriza amabwiriza mashya y'ibihugu byabo.
Itsinda ryacu rizongera kandi kuvugurura amabwiriza yacu mu gihe gikwiriye kugira ngo ritange ubufasha.
Bangladesh yatangaje ko abantu batanu bapfuye bishwe na COVID-19, ni bwo bwa mbere buvugwa buri munsi
Ejo, Bangladesh yemeje ko abantu batanu bashya bapfuye bazize COVID-19 kuri uwo munsi.
Iyi ni yo mibare y'abantu benshi bapfuye ku munsi umwe bitewe n'iyi virusi.
Kugeza ejo, Ikigo cya Bangladesh gishinzwe iby'indwara z'ibyorezo, kurwanya indwara n'ubushakashatsi (IEDCR) cyatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye w'abanduye wari ukubiyemo abantu 114 bari barwaye n'abamaze gukira 33 bari mu rugo.
Abantu 17 bapfuye baramaze kumenyekana.
Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru ku rubuga rwa interineti, umuyobozi wa IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, yavuze ko mu bapfuye harimo abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Dr Meerjady yavuze ko babiri muri bo bari bafite imyaka iri hejuru ya 60, babiri bari hagati ya 51 na 60, naho umwe afite imyaka iri hagati ya 41 na 50.
Yavuze kandi ko babiri mu bapfuye bakomokaga i Dhaka.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku ya 11 Werurwe.
Umuyobozi w'ibitaro yabwiye Anadolu Agency, ikinyamakuru cy'aho, ko umwe mu bapfuye ari Jalal Saifur Rahman, umuyobozi wa Komisiyo ya Bengali yo kurwanya ruswa, wari urwariye mu bitaro bya Kuwait Maitree.
Ku wa Gatandatu, mu itangazo ryashyizwe kuri videwo, Minisitiri w'Ubutwererane n'Amapine muri Bangladesh Obaidul Quader yavuze ko imodoka zitwara abagenzi zizamara igihe kirekire kurusha uko byari biteganyijwe, kugeza ku wa Gatandatu utaha.
Iri soko rya rusange ryari ryatangiye gufungwa ku ya 26 Werurwe kandi ryari riteganyijwe kurangira ku wa Gatandatu tariki ya 4 Mata.
Gucuruza ibintu by'ibanze - imiti, lisansi n'ibyokurya - byari bikiri byemewe.
Abantu ba mbere banditswe ko banduye COVID-19 muri Bangladesh ni abantu babiri bagarutse bavuye mu Butaliyani, ndetse n'umugore wa umwe muri bo, ku itariki ya 8 Werurwe.
Ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, abo batatu bari bamaze gukira.
SARS-CoV-2 irarenga miliyoni imwe y'ubwandu ku isi
Ku wa Kane, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 warenze miliyoni ku isi, nk'uko byagaragajwe n'ibikoresho bya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins.
Nibura abantu ibihumbi 52 bapfuye bahitanwe na COVID-19, indwara iterwa na coronavirus.
Iki gikorwa cy'ingenzi cyabaye ku munsi umwe Malawi yemeje ubwandu bwa mbere bwa coronavirus na Zambia yabonye urupfu rwa mbere rufitanye isano na coronavirus.
Koreya ya Ruguru yatangaje ko kuva ku wa Kane, ari kimwe mu bihugu bike byasigaye bitanduye coronavirus.
Ku munsi w'ejo, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko abantu 1,051,635 banduye, harimo 79,332 mu masaha makumyabiri n'ane yabanjirije isaha ya saa kumi z'ijoro z'i Burayi bwo hagati (0800 UTC) ku itariki ya 4 Mata.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, habonetse abarwayi barenga ibihumbi 244 ba coronavirus, bahuriye ku bantu nibura 5,900 bapfuye.
CBS News yatangaje, ivuga amakuru ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins, ko hari abantu barenga 1.000 bapfuye muri Amerika ku wa Gatatu batewe n'indwara za coronavirus.
Hirya no hino ku isi, ibihugu byatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyo ndwara.
Ku wa Kane, Sergei Sobyanin, umuyobozi w'umujyi wa Moscou, yongereye igihe cy'amabwiriza yo gufunga umujyi kugeza ku ya 1 Gicurasi.
Ku rwego rw'igihugu, Perezida Vladimir Putin yatangaje ko Abanyarwanda bazakomeza guhembwa batiriwe bajya ku kazi kugeza ku ya 30 Mata.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Porutugali yemeye ko igihe cy'ibihe bidasanzwe cyongerwaho iminsi 15, maze iyo nama yemezwa n'abantu 215 bemeye, icumi bayirwanya, n'umwe wayirwanyije.
Arabiya Sawudite yongereye amasaha yo gutaha mu mijyi yera ya Mecca na Medina kugira ngo azagire umunsi wose; mbere, amasaha yo gutaha yari hagati ya saa tatu z'amanywa na saa kumi n'ebyiri za mu gitondo gusa.
Thailand yateganyaga gushyiraho amasaha yo gutaha hagati ya saa kumi z'ijoro na saa yine za mu gitondo.
Guverineri wa Ohio, Mike DeWine, yatangaje ko leta yongereye igihe cyo kuguma mu rugo kugeza ku ya 1 Gicurasi.
Amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya yagabanyije umubare w'impapuro z'isuku ku gicuruzwa
Ku Cyumweru no ku wa Gatandatu nimugoroba, amaduka yo muri Australia yitwa Woolworths na Coles yagabanyije ibipimo by'ibyo bagura ku mpapuro z'isuku ku buryo buri mudandazo wabaga ufite amakarito abiri na rimwe mu maduka yose yo mu gihugu.
ALDI kandi yashyizeho imipaka y'ipaki imwe, ku wa mbere.
Ibyo bihano byashyizwe ku mbuga za kasho no ku mbuga za Facebook z'izo nzu.
Abaguzi bavuga ko bari guhaha kubera ubwoba bwa COVID-19 mu gihe abantu baba bakeneye kwicumbikira bonyine.
Ku wa Gatatu, Woolworths na yo yagabanyije ibicuruzwa by'impapuro z'isuku ku byo kuzana mu rugo ku isanduku imwe ku busabe.
Izi mpinduka zakurikiye ihagarikwa ry'ibikoresho bine ku bucuruzi bwashyizweho na Woolworths na Coles ku ya 4 na 5 Werurwe.
Coles, mu itangazo ryayo ryashyizwe ahagaragara ku wa 8 Werurwe, yatangaje ko kubera ko hari ibicuruzwa byinshi bifunze, "amaduka menshi aracyari kugurisha mu gihe kitarenze isaha nyuma yo gutanga", maze avuga ko icyifuzo "kitigeze kibaho", mu gihe ALDI, mu butumwa bwo kuri Facebook ku wa Kabiri, yavuze ko "bitunguranye".
Umuvugizi wa Woolworths yavuze ko mu cyumweru gishize, ibicuruzwa byazamutse cyane.
Mu cyumweru gishize, iduka rya Costco ryo muri Canberra na ryo ryashyizeho imipaka ku bicuruzwa bibiri.
Kugira ngo yongere kugabanya ibura, Coles yategetse ibicuruzwa binini cyane ku batanga ibicuruzwa kandi yongerera umubare w'ibicuruzwa bitangwa, Woolworths yategetse ibicuruzwa byinshi, mu gihe ALDI yatumye ibicuruzwa byo ku wa Gatatu byari biteganyijwe biboneka hakiri kare.
Russell Zimmerman, umuyobozi mukuru w'Ishyirahamwe ry'Abacuruzi bo muri Ositaraliya, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera ibicuruzwa byabo, ariko amategeko y'inzego z'ibanze agenga igihe imodoka zigomba gutangiriraho ibicuruzwa, bituma bigorana.
Yiteze ko ibiciro by'umusaruro bizamuka, kuko abaguzi bazaba bagerageza guhaza ibyifuzo, kandi ibicuruzwa by'ibanze bizaba bike.
Ku wa Kabiri, ALDI yatangaje ko nyuma yo gusohora ibicuruzwa hakiri kare, amaduka amwe n'amwe adashobora gutangaza ibitaramo byo ku wa Gatatu.
Mu nkuru yatanzwe na News.com.au, Dr Gary Mortimer, impuguke mu bucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi bw'ibanze wo muri Kaminuza y'ikoranabuhanga ya Queensland, yavuze ko amaduka yuzuza ibicuruzwa buri mugoroba.
Yavuze ko impapuro z'isuku ari ibintu biremereye, bigatuma umubare w'ibikoresho uba muke, kandi iyo zigurishijwe, zisigara zitagira aho zibika, bigatuma abantu bumva ko zibuze.
Russell Zimmerman yabwiye ABC News ati "Coles na Woolworths bafite igitekerezo cy'uko iyo mu bubiko haba hari ibintu byinshi, niba ibicuruzwa nk'ibikoresho byo mu bwiherero n'ibimera byo mu bwogero bishobora kugurwa kandi bikaba bihari mu bwinshi, ushobora kugabanya ubwoba".
Umukozi ukora impapuro z'isuku zisubiwemo witwa Who Gives a Crap yavuze ko ku wa Gatatu w'icyumweru gishize nta bikoresho bari bafite.
Kimberly-Clark, ikora ibikoresho byo gusukura imyanda, na Solaris Paper ikora Sorbent, byashimangiye ko bakora amasaha 24 ku munsi kugira ngo bakomeze gutanga, nk'uko bivugwa na News.com.au.
Urubuga rwa Domain.com, ruvuga ku bijyanye n'imitungo, rwatangaje ko hari abagurisha amazu batanga impapuro z'isuku ku buntu ku wa mbere ugiye gutanga, mu cyamunara i Melbourne, ubwo cyamunara zari nke kubera ko abaguzi bari bafite igihe cyo kuruhuka mu mpera z'icyumweru kirekire cy'umunsi w'umurimo.
Mu nomero yo ku wa Kane y'ikinyamakuru cya buri munsi cyandikwaga i Darwin (NT News), harimo n'umwandiko w'amapaji umunani wari ugenewe gucibwa kugira ngo ukoreshwe nk'impapuro z'isuku.
Mu mizo ya mbere, amaduka ntiyari ashishikajwe no gushyiraho amategeko abuza abaguzi kugura ibintu runaka, nk'uko byavuzwe na ABC Australia ku ya 3 Werurwe, aho yavuze ko nta gahunda yo gushyiraho amategeko abuza abaguzi kugura ibintu runaka.
Russell Zimmerman yongeyeho ko ibindi bikoresho nabyo bikenewe cyane, birimo udupfukamunwa, imiti yo guhanagura, ibicuruzwa byumye, gukaraba intoki n'ifu.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, hanze ya Ositaraliya, ku Cyumweru nimugoroba, isoko rikomeye ryo mu Bwongereza Ocado ryagaragaye rigabanya kugura impapuro z'isuku za Andres mu dupaki tubiri tw'ibikoresho 12.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19  indwara iterwa na coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  ari icyorezo.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryerekeza gusa ku buryo indwara yageze kure, ntabwo ryerekeza ku buryo abantu bafite ubwandu bw'icyorezo bafite ibyago, OMS yavuze ko ari ngombwa ko leta zifata ingamba:
"Ibihugu byose biracyafite ubushobozi bwo guhindura uko iki cyorezo kiza.
Niba ibihugu byamenye, bikora ibizamini, bivura, byigenga, bikurikirana kandi bigashishikariza abaturage babyo gutabara", ni ko Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS yavuze.
"Turahangayikishijwe cyane n'uko abantu benshi cyane bakwirakwira kandi bakaba bafite ubukana bukabije, kandi nanone turahangayikishijwe n'uko abantu benshi cyane batagira icyo bakora".
Dukurikije uko Dr. Tom Frieden, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara no Kuzirinda, yabivuze, icyo cyorezo "nta kindi cyari cyarigeze kibaho".
Mu magambo yasohowe na CNN muri Gashyantare, yavuze ko "uretse ibicurane, nta kindi cyorezo cy'ibicurane byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero cyigeze kigaragara kuva cyatangira kugaragara kugeza igihe cyakomeje gukwirakwira ku isi hose".
Ghebreyesus yagaragaje igitekerezo nk'icyo, avuga ko "nta kindi gihe twigeze tubona icyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus".
Yakomeje agira ati "kandi nta kindi gihe twigeze tubona icyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa icyarimwe".
