Ibi bivuze ko virusi ikwirakwira mu baturage, kandi bamwe mu baturage ntibazi aho banduye cyangwa uko banduye. Abashinzwe ubuzima bita ku muntu ushobora kuba yanduye barasabwa gukoresha ingamba zisanzwe zo kwirinda, kwirinda guhura n'abandi no kurinda amaso. Gukurikirana abo bahuye ni uburyo bw'ingenzi ku nzego z'ubuzima bwo kumenya inkomoko y'ubwandu no kwirinda ko bwakwirakwira.
Gukoresha amakuru y'aho umuntu ari kuri telefoni zigendanwa na leta muri iyo mpamvu byatumye abantu bahangayikishwa n'ibanga ry'ubuzima bwabo, Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe arenga 100 asohora itangazo risaba ko ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura buhagarikwa.
Porogaramu zitandukanye za terefone zigendanwa zashyizwe mu bikorwa cyangwa zasabwe gukoresha ku bushake, kandi guhera ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'abahanga arenga icumi yakoraga ku bisubizo byubaka ubuzima bwite, nk'ikoreshwa rya Bluetooth mu kwandikisha aho umukoresha ari hafi ya terefone zigendanwa.
Abakoresha nyuma bahabwa ubutumwa niba baragiranye imishyikirano ya bugufi n'umuntu wanduye COVID-19. Hari ibitekerezo bitari byo bigenda byigaragaza ku buryo bwo kwirinda kwandura; urugero, gusukura izuru no gukaraba mu kanwa n'amazi yo mu kanwa ntibigira icyo bigeraho.
Nta rukingo rwa COVID-19 ruriho, nubwo imiryango myinshi irimo gukora kugira ngo ruvumbuke.
Gukaraba intoki ni ingenzi mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo.
Ikigo cya CDC gitanga inama yo gukaraba intoki kenshi n'isabune n'amazi nibura amasegonda makumyabiri, cyane cyane nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero cyangwa igihe intoki ziba zanduye cyane; mbere yo kurya; no nyuma yo guhumeka, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Ibyo biterwa n'uko iyo virusi ivuye mu mubiri w'umuntu, yica isabune yo mu rugo, igatuma ikuramo udukoko tw'imyanda.
CDC kandi yanatanze inama yo gukoresha umuti wica udukoko mu ntoki usanzwe ukoreshwa n'inzoga, ufite nibura 60% by'inzoga mu gihe isabune n'amazi bitaraboneka.
OMS igira abantu inama yo kwirinda gukora ku maso, izuru cyangwa umunwa batabanje gukaraba intoki.
Imyanya ishobora gukingirwa n'imiti itandukanye (mu munota umwe nyuma yo kwanduzwa n'imiti yica udukoko ku gice cy'icyuma kidafite ingese), harimo 6271% ya éthanol, 50100% ya isopropanol, 0,1% ya sodium hypochlorite, 0,5% ya hydrogène peroxyde na 0,27,5% ya povidone-iode.
Izindi miti, urugero nka benzalkonium chloride na chrohexidine gluconate, ntizikora neza cyane.
CDC irasaba ko mu gihe umuntu akekwaho cyangwa yemejwe ko yanduye COVID mu kigo nk'ibiro cyangwa ubwiherero, ahantu hose nko mu biro, mu bwiherero, ahantu rusange, ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki abantu bakoresha nk'amatabuleti, imashini zikorana n'utwuma, ibyuma by'ibikoresho, ibyuma bya kure n'ibyuma bya ATM bikoreshwa n'abarwaye, bigomba kwandura.
Imiryango y'ubuzima yagiriye abantu inama yo kwisiga mu kanwa no mu mazuru igihe bakoroye inkokora cyangwa igihe basimuye, kandi bagacaho ako kanya.
Abantu bashobora kuba baranduye, basabwa kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi, kuko kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya umubare n'intera utwo dupfukamunwa dutanga mu gihe tuvuga, dutitira cyangwa dukorora.
OMS yatanze amabwiriza y'igihe n'uburyo bwo gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Stephen Griffin, impuguke mu by'indwara zo mu bwoko bwa virusi muri Kaminuza ya Leeds, yagize ati "Kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya abantu guhora bakora ku maso, ari na byo bituma abantu banduza iyo badafite isuku y'intoki".
OMS yasabye abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza kwambara udupfukamunwa gusa mu gihe bafite ibyago byinshi, nk'abita ku muntu urwaye COVID-19, nubwo bemera ko kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda gukora ku maso.
Ibihugu byinshi byatangiye gushishikariza abaturage gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, CDC irasaba abantu kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'ubwoko butari ubwa muganga, twakozwe mu mwenda. Ubushinwa bwatanze inama y'uko abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza bakoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ubwoko bumwe, cyane cyane iyo begeranye n'abandi bantu (metero 1 cyangwa munsi yayo).
Hong Kong irasaba kwambara agapfukamunwa mu gihe utwaye imodoka cyangwa mu gihe uri ahantu hari abantu benshi.
Abashinzwe ubuzima muri Thailand barimo gutera abantu inkunga yo gukora udupfukamunwa tw'impu mu ngo zabo no kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza.
Repubulika ya Tchèque na Slovakiya byakuyeho itegeko ryo kujya hanze mu ruhame utambaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa utambaye amazuru n'umunwa.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye abantu bose kwambara agapfukamunwa mu gihe bagiye ahantu hahurira abantu benshi kugira ngo birinde n'abandi.
Leta ya Autriche yategetse ko umuntu wese winjira mu iduka ry'ibyokurya agomba kwambara agapfukamunwa.
Israel yasabye abaturage bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu ruhame.
Taiwan, imaze gukora udupfukamunwa miliyoni icumi ku munsi kuva mu kwezi kwa gatatu, yasabye abagenzi bari mu modoka zitwara abagenzi n'imodoka zitwara abagenzi mu mihanda yo hagati y'imijyi kwambara udupfukamunwa ku itariki ya 1 Mata.
Panama yashyizeho itegeko ryo kwambara agapfukamunwa igihe cyose ugiye hanze, kandi igasaba ko abantu badashobora kugura agapfukamunwa bakorera mu ngo zabo bakagakora.
Udupfukamunwa twakoreshejwe cyane no mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Maleziya na Singapuru.
Kwirinda kwegerana (zwi no ku izina ry'urwikekwe) bikubiyemo ibikorwa byo kurwanya ubwandu bigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara binyuze mu kugabanya guhura cyane kw'abantu.
Uburyo bwo kubigeraho ni nko gushyira abantu mu kato; kubuza abantu kujya mu bindi bihugu; no gufunga amashuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo, ibibuga by'imikino, amazu ya sinema cyangwa ibigo by'ubucuruzi.
Abantu bashobora gushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kwirinda abantu mu kuguma mu rugo, kugabanya ingendo, kwirinda ahantu hari abantu benshi, gukoresha indamukanyo zitagaragaza aho umuntu ahuriye n'abandi no kwirinda abandi.
Ubu ibihugu byinshi birasaba cyangwa bigasaba abantu kwirinda cyane mu turere twugarijwe n'iki cyorezo.
Umubare munini w'abantu bateranira hamwe wavuzwe n'inzego za leta z'Amerika n'imiryango y'ubuzima wahise ugabanuka uva ku bantu 250 (niba nta COVID-19 yamenyekanye mu karere) ukagera ku bantu 50, nyuma yaho ukagera ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwabujije abantu benshi guteranira hamwe. Abakuze n'abafite uburwayi nk'igisukari, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko ukabije w'amaraso n'uburwayi bw'umubiri, kandi bafite uburwayi bukomeye, CDC yabasabye kuguma mu rugo igihe cyose bishoboka mu duce twugarijwe n'icyorezo. Mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima zatangiye gusimbuza ijambo "kwirinda" "kwirinda mu buryo bw'umubiri", kugira ngo basobanure ko intego ari ukugabanya guhura n'abantu mu gihe bakomeza gushyikirana, haba mu buryo busanzwe cyangwa kure.
Gukoresha ijambo "kwirinda" byateje impungenge ko abantu bagomba kwitandukanya n'abandi mu buryo bwuzuye, aho kubatera inkunga yo gukomeza gushyikirana n'abandi binyuze mu bundi buryo. Hari abayobozi batanze amabwiriza y'ubuzima bw'imyororokere yo gukoresha mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Muri byo harimo inama yo kuryamana n'umuntu ubana na we gusa, udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso byayo.
Abantu bagaragaweho COVID-19 n'abakeka ko banduye basabwe kwicungira mu rugo.
Inzego z'ubuzima zatanze amabwiriza arambuye ku bijyanye no kwicungira ukwabo mu buryo bukwiye. Leta nyinshi zategetse cyangwa zisaba ko abaturage bose batuye mu duce twibasiwe n'iyo ndwara bajya mu kato.
Amabwiriza akomeye cyane yo kwishyirira mu kato yatanzwe ku bantu bari mu matsinda y'ibyago byinshi.
Abantu bashobora kuba baragaragaye bafite COVID-19 n'abaherutse kujya mu gihugu cyangwa akarere karimo ubwandu bw'indwara bakanguriwe kwiherera mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe bagaragaye bwa nyuma.
Uburyo bwo kurwanya icyorezo ni uguhagarika cyangwa guhashya, no kugabanya.
Gufunga bikorwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo hakiri kare kandi bigamije gukurikirana no gutandukanya abanduye ndetse no gushyiraho izindi ngamba zo kurwanya ubwandu no gukingira kugira ngo indwara itagera ku baturage.
Iyo bitagishoboka guhashya ikwirakwira ry'iyo ndwara, imbaraga zitangira gukoreshwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo: hafatwa ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo no kugabanya ingaruka zayo ku nzego z'ubuzima no ku muryango.
Uburyo bwo guhuza ingamba zo kwirinda no kugabanya ubukana bw'ibiza bushobora gukorwa icyarimwe.
Gukumira bisaba ingamba zikomeye cyane kugira ngo iki cyorezo kiveho binyuze mu kugabanya umubare w'ubwandu bw'ibanze ku bantu bari munsi ya 1. Kimwe mu byo umuntu akora mu guhangana n'icyorezo cy'indwara zandura ni ukugerageza kugabanya igihe cy'ikirenga cy'icyorezo, kizwi nko kugabanya ibipimo by'icyorezo.
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo kurengerwa n'ubuvuzi kandi bigatanga igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Mu bikorwa by'ubutabazi bishobora gukemura iki cyorezo harimo ingamba zo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nko kugira isuku y'intoki, kwambara udupfukamunwa no kwitarura abantu; ingamba z'abaturage zigamije kwirinda abantu, nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika ibikorwa by'iteraniro; uruhare rw'abaturage mu gushishikariza abantu kwemera no kwitabira ibyo bikorwa; ndetse n'ingamba z'ibidukikije nko gusukura. Mu Bushinwa hafashwe ingamba zikomeye zigamije guhashya iki cyorezo, igihe ubukana bw'iki cyorezo bwari bumaze kugaragara, nko gushyira mu kato imigi yose no gushyiraho amategeko akomeye yo kubuza ingendo.
Ibihugu bindi na byo byafashe ingamba zitandukanye zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yatangije ikoranabuhanga ryo gupima abantu benshi no gushyira mu kato abantu bari mu gace runaka, kandi itanga imiburo ku ngendo z'abantu banduye.
Singapore yatanze inkunga y'amafaranga ku banduye biyemeje kujya mu kato kandi igafatira amande menshi abananirwa kubikora.
Taiwan yongereye umusaruro w'udupfukamunwa kandi ihana abantu kubika ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Imyiteguro y'u Bwongereza na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika igaragaza ko kugabanya (kugabanya ariko kutabura icyorezo) no kugihagarika (guhagarika icyorezo) bifite imbogamizi zikomeye.
Politiki nziza yo kugabanya ubukana bw'ibiza ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abantu bakeneye ubuvuzi ku kigero cya 2/3 n'abapfa ku kigero cya kabiri, ariko bikaguma bituma abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana bapfa kandi inzego z'ubuzima zikagira ikibazo cy'ubwiyongere bw'abantu.
Gukumira bishobora kwifuzwa ariko bigomba gukomeza igihe cyose virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse, niba ari rwo rwabanje), kuko ubundi ikwirakwira risubira inyuma vuba iyo ingamba zigabanyirijwe.
Kutabogama igihe kirekire mu guhashya icyorezo bitera ibiciro by'imibereho n'ubukungu.
Nta miti yihariye ya virusi yemewe ku miti ya COVID-19, ariko hari ibikorwa byo kuyikora birimo no kugerageza imiti iriho.
Kunywa imiti igabanya uburibwe, kunywa amazi no kuruhuka bishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso by'iyo ndwara.
Bitewe n'uburemere bw'indwara, bishobora kuba ngombwa ko ahabwa imiti ikoreshwa umwuka wa ogisijeni, akanywa amazi mu mitsi, kandi agafashwa guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu afashe za siteroyi, bishobora gutuma ibyago bimwongerera.
Imiti itandukanye yari yemewe mbere mu kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi iri gukorwaho iperereza kugira ngo ikoreshwe mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS kandi yatangaje ko hari "imiti gakondo n'iy'iwacu" ishobora koroshya ibimenyetso biterwa na SARS-CoV-19.
Kongera ubushobozi no guhuza ubuvuzi n'ibyo abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye bivugwa na OMS nk'ingamba z'ibanze zo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
ECDC n'ibiro by'akarere k'u Burayi bya OMS byatanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze ku bijyanye no kwimura ibikoresho ku byiciro byinshi, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu bikorwa byo gupima COVID-19, guhagarika uburyo bwo gupima igihe cyose bishoboka, gutandukanya no gushyira mu kato abarwayi banduye COVID-19, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi bavuye mu bitaro by'indembe binyuze mu gutoza abakozi no kongera umubare w'imashini zitanga umwuka n'ibitanda.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku birebana n'aho umuntu wa mbere wanduye (uwo bitaga umurwayi wa mbere) ashobora kuba yaraturutse.
Umuntu wa mbere uzwiho icyorezo cya coronavirus ashobora kuba yarapfuye tariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan, Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wagendaga wiyongera buhoro buhoro.
Ibi ahanini byari bifitanye isano n'isoko ry'ibicuruzwa by'ibicuruzwa by'inyanja rya Huanan, ryagurishaga n'inyamaswa nzima, kandi igitekerezo kimwe ni uko virusi yavuye muri kimwe muri ibyo bikoko; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, ko ifite inkomoko y'ubwandu bw'ibinyabuzima. Igikeri cy'indwara y'amahaha y'impyiko itagira icyorezo cyamenyekanye cyamenyekanye ku ya 26 Ukuboza, gifatwa na muganga Zhang Jixian wo mu bitaro by'intara ya Hubei, wabimenyesheje Wuhan Jianghan CDC ku ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan baburiye bagenzi babo ko hari "coronavirus isa na SARS".
Abaganga umunani muri abo, harimo na Li Wenliang, barahanwe n'abapolisi kubera ko bakwirakwizaga ibihuha by'ibinyoma, naho undi witwa Ai Fen, abahawe inama n'abari bamurongoye kubera ko yatumye abantu bahangayika.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan yaje gushyira ahagaragara itangazo ku mugaragaro ku ya 31 Ukuboza maze imenyesha OMS.
Abategetsi bashinzwe ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan bari bamaze kubona amakuru ahagije y'ubwandu bw'ibicurane bitazwi, bituma batangira iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama. Mu ntangiriro z'iki cyorezo, umubare w'abanduye wikubye kabiri hafi buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yakwirakwiriye mu zindi ntara z'Ubushinwa, ifashwa n'impunzi z'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa na Wuhan ari ikigo cy'ingendo n'aho hakorerwa ingendo zikomeye z'indarayi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko hari abantu bashya bagera hafi ku 140 banduye mu munsi umwe, barimo abantu babiri i Beijing n'umwe i Shenzhen.
Amakuru yemewe nyuma y'aho agaragaza ko abantu 6,174 bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020.Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatsinze Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani ku mubare munini w'abanduye ku isi.Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, abantu barenga miliyoni 1,61 baramaze kumenyekana ku isi hose; abantu barenga 97,000 barapfuye naho abasaga 364,000 barakira.
Ibihugu n'uturere bigera kuri 200 byagize nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije u Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza rw'abantu no gushyiraho igenzura ku mipaka.
Mu bikorwa by'igihugu harimo ingamba zo kwirinda nk'igenzurwa ry'abantu (zwi ku izina rya Guma mu rugo, Gucumbikira mu nzu cyangwa Guma mu rugo) n'igihe cyo gutaha. Guhera ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera hafi kuri miliyoni 300, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abatuye Amerika, bari mu buryo runaka bwo gufunga, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari mu gifungo muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 bari mu gifungo muri Afurika y'Epfo, n'abantu bagera kuri miliyari 1,3 bari mu gifungo mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu buryo runaka bwo gufunga, biyongera bagera kuri miliyari 2.6 nyuma y'iminsi ibirihafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye COVID-19 yagaragaye tariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; raporo imwe itemejwe igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere wemejwe yanduye ari uwa 17 Ugushyingo.
Umuganga Zhang Jixian yabonye umuganda w'abantu barwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, ibitaro bye bigahita bimenyesha Wuhan Jianghan CDC ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ibizamini bya mbere byagenewe ibipimo by'abarwayi ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 byagaragaje ko hari coronavirus isa na SARS.
Itangazo rusange ryashyizwe ahagaragara na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan ku ya 31 Ukuboza.
OMS yabimenyeshejwe uwo munsi.
Ubwo aya makuru yatangazwaga, abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan baragabishijwe na polisi kubera "gukwirakwiza ibihuha" ku cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta "gihamya isobanutse" y'ubwandu bw'umuntu ku wundi.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukabije bwaje kuvugwa na Xi Jinping umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti b'Ubushinwa nk'"intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Mu cyiswe "igikorwa cy'igenzura rikomeye mu mateka y'abantu", ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama hatangajwe ko hashyizweho akarere kagenzurwa n'ubuvuzi gahagarika ingendo zijya n'izisohoka mu mujyi wa Wuhan, kageze no mu mijyi 15 yose ya Hubei, hagira abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 57.
Imodoka bwite zari zarabuzanyijwe muri uwo mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (25 Mutarama) byahagaritswe ahantu henshi.
Abategetsi kandi batangaje ko bagiye kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Huoshenshan, byuzuye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hubatswe urundi bitaro, Urw'i Leishenshan, kugira ngo rwitwarire abandi barwayi.
Uretse ibitaro biherutse kubakwa, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 byo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, nk'ibigo by'amakoraniro na sitade, bihinduka ibitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho izindi ngamba zo gukumira icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga ibyangombwa by'ubuzima ku bagenzi no kongera iminsi mikuru y'impeshyi.
Kaminuza n'amashuri hirya no hino mu gihugu na byo byafunzwe.
Intara za Hong Kong na Macao zashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye, cyane cyane ku mashuri n'amashuri makuru.
Mu turere dutandukanye two mu Bushinwa, hashyizweho uburyo bwo gukorera kure.
Ingamba zo guhagarika ingendo zashyizweho mu gihugu cya Hubei no hanze yacyo.
Imodoka zitwara abagenzi zatangiye guhinduka, kandi amazu ndangamurage yo hirya no hino mu Bushinwa yafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Mu mijyi myinshi hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo kugenzura urujya n'uruza rw'abaturage, kandi byatekerejwe ko abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bari mu buryo runaka bwo guhagarika kujya hanze. Nyuma y'uko iki cyorezo cyinjiye mu cyiciro cy'isi yose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira virusi "kuva" mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho gahunda y'iminsi 14 yo gushyira mu kato ku bantu bose bavuye mu bindi bihugu binjira muri uwo mujyi. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Ubushinwa bw'ibanze bwanduje umuntu umwe gusa mu minsi itanu yabanjirije uwo, muri iki gihe binyuze ku muntu wari uvuye muri Istanbul agarutse i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa Li Keqiang yatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bwanduye mu gihugu mu by'ukuri ryahagaritswe kandi ko icyorezo cyagenzurwa mu Bushinwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, ingendo zari zibujijwe muri Hubei, uretse Wuhan, zagabanyijwe nyuma y'amezi abiri hashyizweho gahunda yo gufunga. Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira ku bafite visa cyangwa ibyangombwa byo gutura bizahagarikwa guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, nta makuru arambuye y'igihe iyi politiki izarangirira.
Abashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bazajya basaba viza mu biro by'ubuserukizi cyangwa bya ba ambasaderi b'Ubushinwa.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yashishikarije inganda n'inganda kongera gufungura ku ya 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga inguzanyo z'amafaranga ku masosiyete. Inama y'Igihugu yatangaje umunsi wo kuboroga, utangira n'umunsi w'akababaro w'iminota itatu ku itariki ya 10:00 z'amanywa, tariki ya 4 Mata, uhuriye n'umunsi mukuru wa Qingming, nubwo leta nkuru yasabye imiryango kujya igaragaza ko yubaha abantu ku rubuga rwa interineti mu kubahiriza intera kugira ngo birinde ko COVID-19 yongera kwaduka.
COVID-19 yemejwe ko yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020 ivuye mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare habaye ukwiyongera gukomeye kw'abanduye, ahanini biterwa n'iteraniro ryabereye i Daegu ry'umuteguro mushya w'idini uzwi ku izina rya Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abitabiriye Shincheonji basuye Daegu baturutse i Wuhan bakekwaho kuba ari bo bateje iki cyorezo.
Kugeza ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9,336 b'iri torero, 1,261 cyangwa 13% bavuze ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko hari ingamba zo kwirinda ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 2,000 bemejwe ko banduye muri Koreya, ku ya 29 Gashyantare bagera ku 3150.
Ibigo byose bya gisirikare bya Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'ibizamini byemeje ko abasirikare batatu banduye iyi virusi.
Amategeko y'indege na yo yarahindutse. Koreya y'Epfo yatangije gahunda yafashwe nk'iyikomeye kandi iteguwe neza ku isi yo gupima abaturage kugira ngo barebe niba nta bwandu bafite, no gutandukanya abantu bose banduye ndetse no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gupima bwagaragaje ko abimukira bashya baturutse mu bindi bihugu bagomba kwipimisha ibimenyetso binyuze mu porogaramu ya telefoni, gupima virusi mu modoka, ku munsi ukurikiyeho bakabona ibisubizo, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima kugira ngo abantu bagera ku 20.000 bapimwe buri munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo ifatwa nk'aho yagize icyo igeraho mu kurwanya iki cyorezo nubwo itashyize mu kato imigi yose. Mu mizo ya mbere, abaturage bo muri Koreya y'Epfo bari batandukanye ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yabyitwayemo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon acibwa ku butegetsi kubera ibyo bavuga ko ari uburyo Leta ikoresha nabi iki cyorezo, cyangwa se bashima uko yabyitwayemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo ifite umubare muto w'abanduye ku munsi umwe mu byumweru bine bishize.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bashya bavuye mu mahanga bazajya mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko itangazamakuru ryabitangaje ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ibyifuzo byo gufashwa gupima virusi biturutse mu bihugu 121 bitandukanye.
Irani yatangaje abantu ba mbere banduye SARS-CoV-2 ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare i Qom, aho Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi yatangaje ko abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma yaho kuri uwo munsi.
Ingamba za mbere zatangajwe na leta harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, siporo n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, no gufunga za kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yatanze miliyari eshanu z'amafaranga y'amanyarwanda yo kurwanya iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twatewe n'iki cyorezo, kandi ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi yatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo urujya n'uruza rwinshi hagati y'imijyi mbere y'umwaka mushya wa Nowruz w'Abaperesi rwakomeje.
Insengero z'Abashiya i Qom zakomeje gufungurirwa abagenzi kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020. Muri Gashyantare, Irani yabaye ihuriro ry'ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi nyuma y'u Bushinwa.
Mu gihe hari abivuga ko iki cyorezo cyapfukanywe muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byari byamaze kubona abanduye muri Irani kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko iki cyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha abanduye 388 batangajwe na leta ya Irani kuri iyo tariki.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, kandi 23 mu bagize 290 bayo bagaragaweho virusi ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura nta nkomyi abarwanashyaka baharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe bazira gutandukana mu mahoro, no kurekura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zikwiriye.
Ryavuze ko hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwira kwa virusi mu bigo bifunze nk'ibigo by'ifungurwa, nabyo bidafite ubuvuzi buhagije.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye ku munsi umwe, ni bo benshi mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Nibura abanyapolitiki 12 ba Irani n'abayobozi ba leta bari barapfuye cyangwa bari barapfuye bazize iki cyorezo ku ya 17 Werurwe.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari ifite abarwayi bashya 50 buri saha n'urupfu rushya buri minota icumi bitewe na coronavirus.
Nk'uko bivugwa n'umuyobozi wa OMS, hari aho abantu banduye muri Irani bashobora kuba bakubye incuro eshanu abo batangajwe.
Hari kandi abavuga ko ibihano Amerika yafatiye Irani bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'icyo gihugu bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Komiseri Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ushinzwe Uburenganzira bw'Ikiremwamuntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu bigabanywa ku bihugu byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Byemejwe ko iki cyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubwo abashyitsi babiri b'Abashinwa bageragezwaga bagasanga baranduye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Abanduye batangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose z'indege ziva cyangwa zijya mu Bushinwa kandi igatangaza ibihe bidasanzwe.
Nyuma yaho, havumbuwe umubare utandukanye w'abanduye COVID-19, hatangiriye ku bantu 16 bemejwe ko banduye muri Lombardie ku ya 21 Gashyantare. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya rigamije gukumira icyorezo, harimo no gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50,000 bo mu mirenge 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "Mu duce twugarijwe n'icyorezo, kwinjira no gusohoka ntibizemewe.
Gufunga ibikorwa by'akazi n'imikino byamaze gutegekwa muri utwo duce".Ku ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza zose zifunga mu gihugu hose kuko Ubutaliyani bwageze ku bantu 100 bapfuye.
Imikino ikomeye yose, harimo n'imikino y'umupira w'amaguru ya Serie A, yagombaga kubera inyuma y'inzugi zifunze kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yahagaritswe burundu nibura ukwezi kumwe.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse ko ibikorwa byose by'ubucuruzi bihagarikwa uretse amaduka manini n'amavuriro. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani cy'Ubuvuzi, Ubuvuzi, Ubuvuzi no kwita ku barwayi ba mu mutwe (SIAARTI) cyasohoye inama z'imyifatire y'abaganga ku bijyanye n'amabwiriza yo gupima ashobora gukoreshwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwateye u Bushinwa mu bihugu bifite abantu benshi bapfuye bazize coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutangaza ko hari abantu 3,405 bapfuye bazize iki cyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje indege icyenda za gisirikare zifite ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari hamaze kuboneka abarwayi 128,948, abantu 15,887 bapfuye, n'abamaze gukira 21,815, abenshi muri abo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardie.
Raporo ya CNN yagaragaje ko kuba mu Butaliyani hari abantu benshi bageze mu za bukuru no kuba abantu bose banduye virusi batashoboraga gupimwa kugeza ubu, bishobora kuba ari byo bituma umubare w'abahitanwa n'iyo ndwara wiyongera.
Igisubizo cy'Ubwongereza kuri iyi virusi cyabanje kugaragara nk'igihugu cyoroshye cyane mu bihugu byibasiwe, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'Ubwongereza ntiyigeze ishyiraho uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kwirinda abantu cyangwa ingamba zo gushyira abantu mu kato ku baturage bayo.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko leta yanenzwe kubera ko ititaye ku buryo abantu bahangayikishijwe n'ibibazo by'abaturage. Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje ko atagomba gukora ingendo zidakenewe no guhura n'abantu, asaba abantu gukorera mu rugo igihe cyose bishoboka kandi bakirinda ahantu nko mu tubari, muri resitora no mu mazu ya sinema.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro nk'amabyiniro n'amazu y'imyidagaduro bigomba gufunga vuba bishoboka, kandi yasezeranyije kwishyura 80% by'imishahara y'abakozi kugeza ku £2,500 ku kwezi kugira ngo barinde ubushomeri muri iki gihe cy'ibibazo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda abantu, abuza abantu kujya hamwe barenze babiri kandi abuza ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze gusa mu gihe bibaye ngombwa.
Bitandukanye n'ingamba za mbere, izo ngamba zashyizweho na polisi zashyizweho binyuze mu gutanga amande no gutatanya abantu.
Ubucuruzi bwinshi bwategetswe gufunga, usibye ubucuruzi bufatwa nk'ubw'ingenzi, harimo amaduka manini, farumasi, banki, amaduka acuruza ibikoresho, aho bakorera lisansi n'amatara.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, umuntu wa mbere wari urwaye COVID-19 yemejwe mu ntara ya Washington iri mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bw'inyanja ya Pasifika, ku mugabo wari wavuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Itsinda ry'abashinzwe kurwanya Coronavirus ryo mu biro bya Perezida ryashinzwe ku ya 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubutegetsi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko ubuzima bw'abaturage bwihutirwa, kandi bushyiraho amategeko abuza abava mu Bushinwa kwinjira.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara ikigo cy'ubuzima rusange cya mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika cyatangaje ko cyakoze ibikoresho byacyo byo gupima.
Nubwo Amerika yabigenje ityo, yatangiye gupima vuba, bituma abantu batamenya uko icyo gihe icyo cyorezo cyari gikomeye.
Ibizamini byangijwe n'ibikoresho byo gupima bitagira ubushobozi byakozwe na leta muri Gashyantare, kubura kwemerwa na leta ya federasiyo ku bikoresho byo gupima bitari ibya leta (binyuze mu nzego z'uburezi, ibigo n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, n'amabwiriza abuza abantu kuba bakwiriye gupimwa kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (nyuma yaho hagombaga gutangwa icyemezo cya muganga).
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, ikinyamakuru The Washington Post cyatangaje ko ibizamini byagiye bikorwa muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika bitarenga ibihumbi 4.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko hari hasigaye ibipimo 14.000.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje iti: "Abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso kandi bagategekwa n'abaganga bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi kugira ngo bapimwe". Nyuma y'urupfu rwa mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika rwatangajwe muri leta ya Washington ku ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko hari mu bihe bidasanzwe, igikorwa cyahise gikurikirwa n'ibindi bihugu.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, kandi hagati muri Werurwe, amashuri yo hirya no hino mu gihugu yari yafunzwe. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Amerika yamenyeshejwe ingaruka za coronavirus nshya ku gihugu n'itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'indwara zo mu Bwongereza bo muri Imperial College London.
Kuri uwo munsi Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ry'inyongera ry'ingengo y'imari yo kwitegura no guhangana na Coronavirus, ryatanze miliyari 8.3 z'amadolari mu nkunga z'ibihe bidasanzwe ku bigo bya leta kugira ngo bikemure iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho amategeko abuza abakozi kujya mu mahanga, ahagarika inama, kandi ashishikariza abakozi gukorera mu rugo.
Ibikorwa by'imikino n'ibihe by'umwaka byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko hari guhagarikwa ingendo mu Burayi hafi ya bwose, usibye mu Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, kuva ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Bukeye bwaho, yagutse ibihano bigera no mu Bwongereza na Irilande.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ibihe bidasanzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu, byatanze amafaranga ya leta kugirango akemure ikibazo.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ubucuruzi bwinshi bwarafunzwe cyangwa bugabanyirizwa amasaha mu gihugu cyose cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika mu kugerageza kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari cyemejwe mu ma leta yose 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko umujyi wa New York wari ufite abantu 10,700 banduye coronavirus, baruta umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko kwirinda abantu basa n'aho ari byo byagize icyo bigeraho, kuko imibare y'abanduye yagabanutseho kabiri iva ku minsi 2.0 igera ku minsi 4.7.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, muri New York hari hamaze kuboneka abantu 32,308 banduye iyi virus, naho abantu 672 bapfuye bayanduye. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yatangaje ko ifite abanduye coronavirus benshi kurusha ikindi gihugu icyo ari cyo cyose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Kugeza ku ya 8 Mata, muri Amerika hamaze kuboneka abantu 400,335 banduye iyi virus, naho abantu 12,841 bapfuye.
Nk'uko itangazamakuru ryabitangaje ku wa 30 Werurwe, Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Trump yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwa USNS Comfort bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1.000, bwashyize icyicaro i New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, Amerika yari ifite umubare ntarengwa w'abantu 884 bapfuye bazize coronavirus mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Muri leta ya New York, abantu barenga 100.000 ku itariki ya 3 Mata. Ibiro bya Perezida byanenzwe ko byagabanyije agaciro k'icyo cyorezo no kugenzura ubutumwa butangwa binyuze mu gutegeka abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi guhuza itangazo rusange n'ibitabo bijyanye n'iyi virusi n'ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Kwemera muri rusange uburyo Trump yakemuye iki kibazo byatangiye gutandukana bitewe n'impande zombi.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika n'abatanga ibitekerezo banenze Amerika kubera ko ishingiye ku bicuruzwa by'ingenzi, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi by'ingenzi, bituruka mu Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'ingendo z'indege ryakoreshejwe mu kwerekana no guhanura uburyo bwo gukwirakwira kandi ryatangajwe muri The Journal of Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa Mutarama 2020.
Dukurikije amakuru yo mu mwaka wa 2018 yatanzwe n'Ishyirahamwe Mpuzamahanga ry'Ubwikorezi bw'Indege, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ni byo bihugu byagize umubare munini w'abagenzi bavuye i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byatangajwe ko ari ahantu hakunzwe cyane n'abantu baturuka i Wuhan.
Bali ni wo wavuzwe ko utabishoboye cyane mu mijyi 20 ikunzwe cyane mu gutegura, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya ari yo yafashwe nk'aho itabishoboye cyane. Ositaraliya yashyize ahagaragara gahunda yayo yo guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) ku ya 7 Gashyantare.
Ryavuze ko hari byinshi bitaramenyekana kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izashimangira kugenzura imipaka no gutumanaho mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko habayeho ikibazo cy'umutekano muke mu buzima bw'abantu.
Kubera guhagarika ingendo z'abantu benshi mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateguye kwimura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba dipolomasi muri ako gace, ahanini binyuze mu ndege zafatiriwe n'igihugu cyabo, abategetsi b'u Bushinwa batanga uruhushya.
Kanada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, u Buyapani, u Buhindi, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, u Bufaransa, Arijantine, u Budage na Tayilande ni byo bihugu bya mbere byateguye guhungisha abaturage babyo.
Pakistan yavuze ko itazavana abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yakuye muri icyo gihugu abaturage 34 b'igihugu cya Burezili cyangwa abagize imiryango yabo, hiyongeraho Abanyapolonye bane, Umushina n'Umuhinde.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'u Buhindi bavuye mu ndege muri Polonye, aho indege ya Burezili yahagaze mbere yo gukomeza inzira ijya muri Burezili.
Abaturage ba Burezili bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasília.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abanyakanada 215 (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere, na 39 bari mu ndege ya kabiri yari yaraguzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika) bakuwe i Wuhan bajya muri CFB Trenton kugira ngo bashyirwe mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abanyakanada 185 baturutse i Wuhan yageze kuri CFB Trenton.
Abategetsi ba Australia bakuye abaturage 277 ku itariki ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare mu kigo cyo gufungira ku kirwa cya Noheli, cyari cyahinduwemo ikigo cy'ihagarikwa ry'abantu, aho bamaze iminsi 14.
Indege y'ubwirinzi y'abimukira ya Nouvelle-Zélande yageze muri Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (harimo bamwe baturutse muri Ositaraliya no mu nyanja ya Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cya gisirikare i Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangaje ko zigiye gucyura Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 b'Abanyakanada bari bavanywe muri Diamond Princess, yageze i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'u Buhinde yatangiye gucyura abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yari yaraguzwe na guverinoma ya Afurika y'Epfo yasubije abaturage 112 b'Afurika y'Epfo.
Igerageza ry'ubuvuzi ryakozwe mbere yo kugenda, kandi Abanyafurika y'Epfo bane bagaragazaga ibimenyetso bya coronavirus basigaye inyuma kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abanyafurika y'Epfo gusa bagaragaye bafite ikizamini cya negativu nibo basubijwe mu gihugu cyabo.
Ibisubizo by'ibizamini byemeje ko abanyafurika y'epfo bose, harimo abakozi bo mu ndege, abapilote, abakozi bo muri hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, bose bagumye mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 muri The Ranch Resort.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangiye gukuraho igice cy'ingabo zazo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, minisiteri y'ububanyi n'amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Iran) byoherereje ubufasha Ubushinwa.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bifatanyije mu gufasha kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'u Bushinwa byibasiwe n'iyi virusi, bivugwa ko itsinda rimwe ryo mu karere ka Chicago ryashoboye kohereza udupfukamunwa 50,000 tw'ubwoko bwa N95 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama. Umuryango w'ubutabazi bw'abantu Direct Relief, ku bufatanye na FedEx, wohereje udupfukamunwa 200,000 hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho byo kurinda umuntu, harimo n'utugati n'imyambaro, binyuze mu ndege y'ubutabazi bw'agateganyo ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union Hospital bitarenze ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bagiye gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ku kigo cy'isi cyita ku buzima (OMS) kugira ngo kifashishe mu bushakashatsi bw'inkingo no mu buvuzi, ndetse no kurinda "abantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo".
Interaksyon yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Filipine ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 muri Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapour yatangaje ko izohereza imfashanyo y'amadolari miliyoni 2.26 mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, u Burusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje ko izatangaza impano y'utugofero tw'ubuvuzi miliyoni 18 mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze ibikoresho bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi birimo imyenda 10,000 ya Hazmat, Amerika nayo yatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa kandi isezeranya inkunga y'inyongera ya miliyoni 100 z'amadolari mu bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo. Nyuma y'uko abanduye mu Bushinwa basa n'aho bahagaze neza, iki gihugu cyatangiye kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu bitandukanye byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'u Burusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'impuguke mu gufasha u Butaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yoherereje Addis Ababa, Ethiopia ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.1 by'imiti, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'imyambaro 60,000 yo kurinda kugira ngo itangirwe n'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bwa Afurika.
Nyuma yo kohereza ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, udupfukamunwa 100,000 na ventilateri 5 muri Panama.
Ma kandi yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada. U Buholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Georgia na Repubulika ya Tchèque bagaragaje impungenge bafite ku bipfunyika n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe n'Abashinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yakuye mu gihugu ibikoresho 58,000 by'ubushakashatsi bya Coronavirus byakozwe n'Abashinwa bifite ubushobozi bwo gupima 30% gusa, mu gihe mu Buholandi ho bafashe udupfukamunwa 600,000 tw'Abashinwa twari dufite inenge.
Ububiligi bwasubije mu bikorwa udupfukamunwa 100,000 tudakoreshwa, twibwiraga ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, inkunga y'Ubushinwa yakiriwe neza mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Amajyepfo na Afurika. Ku ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubufasha bw'imvura n'ubushyuhe ku bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye imbaraga z'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa mu gucunga no gukumira iki cyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002/2004, aho abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bashinjwaga ibanga ryatumye imihati yo kwirinda no kugabanya ubwandu ihagarara, n'icyorezo kiriho ubu aho leta nkuru "yagiye itanga amakuru buri gihe kugira ngo yirinde ubwoba mbere y'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya wa Lunar".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza icyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ibanze cyo gushyiraho itegeko ribuza gutwara abantu n'ibintu mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Gauden Galea uhagarariye OMS yavuze ko nubwo "nta gushidikanya ko atari inama OMS yatanze", ariko kandi ko ari "ikimenyetso cy'ingenzi cyane cy'uko yiyemeje kugabanya icyorezo aho cyibasiwe cyane" kandi avuga ko "ntaho gihuriye n'amateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko abantu banduye indwara y'ibicurane mu mahanga no kongera umubare w'abanduye mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi mu buzima rusange gihangayikishije amahanga yose (PHEIC), kikaba ari icya gatandatu PHEIC kivugwa kuva icyo cyemezo cyatangira gukoreshwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cyo mu 2009.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko PHEIC yatewe n'uko "hashobora kuba hari ibyago byo gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'abifite amikoro yo hagati, bidafite uburyo bwiza bwo kwita ku buzima.
Mu gusubiza ku ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry'amabwiriza yo guhagarika ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zibuza ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi" kandi ko "WHO idatanga inama yo kugabanya ubucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga inkunga ya miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira imyiteguro ya gisirikare mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, ivuga ko byihutirwa gushyigikira ibyo bihugu "bitafite uburyo bwo kumenya abantu banduye virusi, kabone n'iyo yaba igaragaye".
Tedros yakomeje atanga itangazo avuga ko "dukomeye gusa nk'urukuta rwacu rw'inzitane" maze asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "gushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura byinshi nyuma". Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru yemeje ko COVID-19 ari izina ry'iyo ndwara.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, António Guterres, yemeye gutanga "imbaraga z'umuryango wose wa Loni mu guhangana n'icyo kibazo".
Iki ni cyo cyatumye hashyirwaho itsinda rya ONU rishinzwe kurwanya ibibazo, ryemerera guhuza ibikorwa byose by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, OMS ivuga ko bizabatuma "bibanda ku bikorwa by'ubuvuzi mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora gukoresha ubumenyi bwazo mu guhangana n'ingaruka zikomeye z'iki cyorezo mu mibereho y'abaturage, ubukungu n'iterambere".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda rya misiyo ihuriweho na OMS riyobowe n'u Bushinwa ryatangijwe kugira ngo ritange impuguke mpuzamahanga n'iz'ishami rya OMS mu Bushinwa zifasha mu gucunga no gusuzuma "uburemere n'ubwandu bw'iki cyorezo" binyuze mu kwakira amahugurwa n'inama n'ibigo by'ingenzi byo ku rwego rw'igihugu no gukora ingendo zo gusura "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo guhangana ku rwego rw'intara n'akarere, harimo n'imijyi n'imidugudu". Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "isi igomba gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus", ivuga ko nubwo hakiri kare cyane kubita icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba kuba "mu cyiciro cyo kwitegura".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo kiri gutera imbere muri Iran, OMS yoherejeyo itsinda rya misiyo ihuriweho kugira ngo rigenzure uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko isesengura ry'ibyago bya coronavirus ku rwego rw'isi yose rizakuzwa rivuye kuri "high" rijya kuri "very high", urwego rwo hejuru cyane rwo kugabura no gusuzuma ibyago.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda y'ubwiherero mu by'ubuzima ya OMS, mu itangazo yatanze, yaburiye ko "Ibi ni ibigeragezo kuri buri butegetsi ku isi: Mukanguke.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba igiye kuza kandi mugomba kuba mwiteguye", asaba ko ingamba nziza zo guhangana na yo zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibibi cyane".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu adatuma abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage batangaza icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko gutangaza bene ibyo byaba bivuze ko "mu by'ukuri twemera ko umuntu wese ku isi azagerwaho n'iyo virusi".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko OMS "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'imiterere iteye impungenge y'ikwirakwira n'uburemere, ndetse n'imiterere iteye impungenge yo kutagira icyo ikora". OMS yagiye inengwa bikomeye kubera ibyo ifatwa nk'uburyo butari bukwiye bwo guhangana n'icyorezo, harimo no gutangaza ibyago by'indwara y'uburwayi bw'abaturage bitinze no gushyira virusi mu byiciro by'icyorezo.
Mu byo abantu bamusubije harimo n'ibisabwa umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, ngo asezere, byashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000 ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke nyinshi z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu zashimangiye kubahiriza uburenganzira bwa buri muntu wese mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo gufashwa mu kurokora ubuzima kandi ko leta ari yo ifite iyo nshingano.
Uwo muryango washimangiye ko kutagira amikoro cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagombye na rimwe kuba impamvu yo kurobanura abantu mu buryo bunyuranyije n'amategeko.
Abahanga bashimangiye ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abari mu matsinda mato, abageze mu za bukuru, abimukira, abatagira aho baba, abari mu buzima bubi cyane, abari mu buroko, ndetse n'impunzi n'andi matsinda ataramenyekana akeneye inkunga ya leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ya leta irimo gukemura ibibazo by'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage byatewe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Ubumwe n'Ubutwererane mu by'Ubukungu n'Iterambere watangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru ku gihe kandi arambuye ku buryo ibihugu byo ku isi byose byabyitwaramo, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku ngamba zo gukomeza uburyo bw'ubuzima n'ubukungu bw'isi kugeza ku guhangana n'ingaruka z'ikumira n'ibihano ku ngendo, iki kigo cy'ikoranabuhanga kirimo n'ikigo gishinzwe gukurikirana politiki z'ibihugu, kigamije gufasha ibihugu kwigira ku bindi no koroshya uburyo bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo cya Coronavirus ku isi hose.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Minisitiri w'Ibiro bya Minisitiri w'Ubwongereza Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Bresil Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro kubera uburyo yakemuye icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi batari bake bo mu ntara z'ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti b'u Bushinwa (CPC) birukanywe ku mirimo yabo yo gushyira mu kato mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, ikimenyetso cy'uko batishimiye uko inzego za politiki zitabiriye iki cyorezo muri utwo turere.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo batekereza ko iyi ntambwe yari igamije kurinda umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti b'Abashinwa Xi Jinping uburakari bw'abaturage kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Ubushinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian, banze kwemera ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan, bahitamo kwemera ibitekerezo by'ubupfumu ku bijyanye na COVID-19 ikomoka muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubuyobozi bwa Donald Trump bwa Amerika bwise coronavirus "virusi y'Ubushinwa" cyangwa "virusi ya Wuhan" buvuga ko "gushyiraho igenzura byongereye virusi ubu yabaye icyorezo ku isi", ibyo bikaba byarakomwe mu nkokora na bamwe mu bamunenga bavuga ko ari ivangura ry'amoko kandi "bitesha [abantu] ku bushobozi ubutegetsi bwe bufite bwo kurwanya iki cyorezo".
Ikinyamakuru Daily Beast cyabonye ubutumwa bwa leta ya Amerika bugaragaza amayeri yo gutumanaho bigaragara ko akomoka mu Nama y'Umutekano w'Igihugu, aho iyo gahunda yatanzwe ivuga ko "Byose byerekeye Ubushinwa.
Turabwirwa kugerageza gutangaza ubu butumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo inama z'abanyamakuru no kugaragara kuri televiziyo".Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byatangaje ko imihati y'Ubushinwa yo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byibasiwe na virusi ari igice cy'ibikorwa byo kwamamaza bigamije kugira ingaruka ku isi.
Umuyobozi ushinzwe politiki y'amahanga muri EU Josep Borrell yaburiye ko hari "igice cya politiki kirimo urugamba rwo kugira ingaruka binyuze mu gukata no 'politike y'ubuntu'".
Borrell kandi yavuze ko "Ubushinwa buri gushishikariza ubutumwa ko, bitandukanye na Amerika, ari umufatanyabikorwa ufite inshingano kandi wizewe".
Ubushinwa kandi bwasabye Amerika gukuraho ibihano kuri Syria, Venezuela na Iran, mu gihe bivugwa ko bwohereza imfashanyo muri ibi bihugu bibiri bya nyuma.
Impano ya Jack Ma y'udupfukamunwa 100,000 yageneye Cuba yabujijwe n'ibihano bya Amerika ku ya 3 Mata.
Abategetsi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika kandi bashinjwa kuyobya imfashanyo zagenewe ibindi bihugu bakajya kuziha igihugu cyabo.
Kandi hari impaka zijyanye n'udupfukamunwa zavuzwe hagati y'ibindi bihugu, nk'u Budage, Autriche n'Ubusuwisi; na Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe ibikoresho bifasha guhumeka amagana byari bigenewe Espagne.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yanenze ko Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi utagaragaje ubufatanye n'Ubutaliyani bwazahajwe na coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani muri EU, yavuze ko "Ubushinwa bwonyine bwitabiriye ku buryo bw'impande zombi.
Nta gushidikanya ko ibyo bidatanga ikimenyetso cyiza cy'ubwiyunge bw'u Burayi".
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma yo kuvugana kuri telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya Vladimir Putin yategetse ingabo z'Uburusiya kohereza abaganga b'ingabo, imodoka zihariye zo kwanduza indwara n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyasubiyemo amagambo yavuzwe n'umuntu utazwi witwa "umunyapolitiki ukomeye" wavuze ko 80 ku ijana by'imfashanyo z'u Burusiya "nta cyo zimaze cyangwa ko nta cyo zigeze zimarira u Butaliyani".
Uwo muyobozi yashinje u Burusiya gutangira ibikorwa byo kwishimisha "mu rwego rwa politiki n'ububanyi n'amahanga".
Perezida wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'u Butaliyani Luigi Di Maio banze ibyo bitangazamakuru byavuze kandi bagaragaza ko bashimira.
Uburusiya kandi bwohereje indege itwara imizigo irimo ubufasha bw'ubuvuzi muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko "mu gihe [Putin] aha ubufasha bagenzi be bo muri Amerika, atekereza ko igihe abacuruzi b'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi bo muri Amerika bazaba bamaze kwiyongera, na bo bazaba bashobora kubibasubiza bibaye ngombwa".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO "Defender 2020" iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye no mu bihugu bya Baltique, imyitozo ikomeye y'intambara ya NATO kuva intambara y'ubutita irangiye, izaba ku kigero gito.
Umunyamabanga mukuru wa Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament Kate Hudson yanenze imyitozo ya Defender 2020 agira ati "Mu bibazo by'ubuzima rusange biriho ubu, ntibihungabanya ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi bitabiriye gusa ahubwo n'abaturage bo mu bihugu bakoreramo". Guverinoma ya Irani yagezweho cyane n'iyi virusi, aho abadepite bagera kuri makumyabiri banduye ndetse n'abandi bantu 15 b'abanyapolitiki bariho cyangwa bahoze.
Perezida wa Iran Hassan Rouhani yandikiye abayobozi b'isi ibaruwa ku mugaragaro abasaba ubufasha ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020, avuga ko igihugu cye kirimo guhangana n'iki cyorezo kubera kutagira amahirwe yo kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga kubera ibihano Amerika yafatiye Iran. Iki cyorezo cyatumye Amerika isaba ko yakira politiki rusange mu bindi bihugu bikize, harimo kwita ku buzima bwa buri wese, kwita ku bana bose, kureka ingo zishyurwa, no kuzamura amafaranga yo kwita ku buzima bwa rubanda.
Abasesengura ibya politiki bari biteze ko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku buryo Donald Trump ashobora kongera gutorwa mu matora ya Perezida yo mu 2020. Imishyikirano ya dipolomasi hagati y'Ubuyapani na Koreya y'Epfo yarushijeho kuzamba kubera iki cyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "imihati y'Ubuyapani yo gushyira abantu mu kato idafite ishingiro kandi idafite icyo ivuze" nyuma y'aho Ubuyapani butangaje ko umuntu wese uza aturutse muri Koreya y'Epfo azajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri ku bibanza byagenwe na leta.
Mu mizo ya mbere, abaturage bo muri Koreya y'Epfo bari batandukanye ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yabyakiriye.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon ashyirwaho ku karubanda kubera ibyo bavuga ko ari uburyo Leta ikoresha nabi iki cyorezo, cyangwa bashima uko yabyitwayemo. Icyorezo cyatumye ibihugu byemera amategeko y'ibihe bidasanzwe mu rwego rwo guhangana nacyo.
Hari abavuga ko iyo gahunda ishobora gutuma ubutegetsi bukomeza gutegeka.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko y'icyo gihugu yatoye yemerera minisitiri w'intebe, Viktor Orbán, gutegeka binyuze mu itegeko ku gihe kitazwi, guhagarika inteko ishinga amategeko ndetse n'amatora no guhana abafashweho gukwirakwiza amakuru y'ibinyoma ku byerekeye virusi n'uburyo leta itegura icyo kibazo.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyagaragaye ko ari cyo cyateye ibibazo byinshi byo kubura ibikoresho, biterwa n'ikoreshwa ry'ibikoresho ku isi hose mu kurwanya icyo cyorezo, kugura ibintu mu buryo bwo guhangayika, no guhungabanya ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikoresho.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze imiburo ku bijyanye n'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'ukwiyongera kw'ibyifuzo by'abaguzi n'ibizabuza abaguzi.
Ahantu henshi kandi habaye kugura ibintu byinshi bituma ibicuruzwa by'ibanze nk'ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku n'amazi yo mu macupa biva ku maduka, bituma habaho ubukene.
Uruganda rw'ikoranabuhanga cyane cyane rwaratanze umuburo ku bijyanye n'ibihe byo gutumiza ibicuruzwa bya elegitoroniki.
Dukurikije uko umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yabivuze, abantu bakenera ibikoresho byo kwirinda bikubye incuro 100.
Ibyo byateye ko ibiciro byiyongera bikagera ku ncuro makumyabiri ugereranyije n'ibiciro bisanzwe kandi binatuma ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi bidatangwa mu gihe cy'amezi ane kugeza kuri atandatu.
Nanone kandi, byateje ikibazo cy'ibikoresho byo kwirinda ku isi hose, kandi OMS yatanze umuburo w'uko ibyo bishobora gushyira mu kaga abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima.
Muri Ositaraliya, iki cyorezo cyatumye abagura daigou babona uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa byo muri Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Iki gikorwa cyatumye mu masupamaketi amwe n'amwe habaho ubukene bw'ibinyobwa by'abana, nyuma biza guhagarikwa na leta ya Australia. Nubwo umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 ari mwinshi mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, kandi ibyo bikaba byaratumye hakenerwa ibiribwa byinshi, utwo duce twombi twaraciwe ubukene bukabije bw'ibiribwa.
Ingamba zafashwe n'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ubucuruzi bw'ibintu by'ingenzi cyane n'ubucuruzi butemewe n'amategeko, zagize icyo zigeraho, bituma habaho ubukene bukabije bw'ibiribwa bwari bwitezwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Amajyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani afite umusaruro munini w'ubuhinzi ntiwagabanutse cyane, ariko ibiciro bishobora kwiyongera nkuko abahagarariye inganda babivuga.
Amashelfu y'ibiribwa yari ubusa by'agateganyo, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu gihe abayobozi ba leta y'Ubushinwa barekuye inyama z'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage babone ibyo kurya bihagije.
Mu Butaliyani, hari amategeko nk'ayo asaba abahinzi b'ibiribwa kubika amafaranga yo gufashisha mu gihe habaye ibyago nk'ibyo.
Ingaruka mbi ku bukungu bw'isi yumvikanye mu Bushinwa: nk'uko raporo y'itangazamakuru yo ku ya 16 Werurwe ibigaragaza, ubukungu bw'u Bushinwa bwahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 kubera ingamba zafashwe na leta zo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi, ndetse n'ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi bwagabanutseho 20.5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa bw'ibanze ari ihuriro rikomeye ry'ubukungu n'inganda, icyorezo cya virusi cyagaragaye ko ari ikibazo gikomeye cyateje ihungabana mu bukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demarais wo mu kigo cy'ubutasi cya Economist Intelligence Unit yavuze ko amasoko azakomeza guhindagurika kugeza igihe hazabaho isura isobanutse y'ingaruka zishobora guturuka muri ibyo.
Muri Mutarama 2020, bamwe mu bahanga mu gusesengura ibijyanye n'ubukungu bavuze ko ingaruka z'icyorezo ku bukungu bw'isi zishobora kurenga iz'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 20022004.
Umuntu umwe w'impuguke wo muri kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis, yavuze ko ingaruka z'ibyo bikorwa ku isoko ry'ibikoresho ku isi zishobora kugera ku myaka ibiri.
Umuryango w'ibihugu bitanga peteroli (OPEC) bivugwa ko "wacitse intege" nyuma yo kugwa cyane kw'ibiciro by'ibikomoka kuri peteroli bitewe n'ibyifuzo bike biva mu Bushinwa.
Amasoko y'imigabane ku isi yose yaragabanutse ku ya 24 Gashyantare kubera ukwiyongera gukomeye kw'umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'u Bushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge z'icyorezo cya coronavirus, ibipimo bitandukanye by'imigabane muri Amerika birimo NASDAQ-100, S&amp;P 500 Index, na Dow Jones Industrial Average byatangaje ko byagabanutse cyane kuva mu 2008, Dow igabanuka amanota 1,191, ari nayo igabanuka rinini ku munsi umwe kuva mu gihe cy'ibibazo by'imari mu 200708.
Ibipimo bitatu byose byasoje icyumweru bigabanutseho 10%.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Scope Ratings GmbH yemeje indangamuntu ya leta y'Ubushinwa, ariko ikomeza kugira icyizere cyo kugabanya.
Imicungire y'imigabane yongeye kugwa bitewe n'ubwoba bw'icyorezo cya coronavirus, igiciro cyayo cyagabanutse cyane ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe.
Abantu benshi bumva ko ubukungu buzagabanuka.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu Mohamed El-Erian yashimye ingamba z'ibihe bidasanzwe zafashwe n'amabanki akomeye n'ibihugu.
