Kubera iyo mpamvu, kompanyi nyinshi z'indege zahagaritse ingendo kubera ko abakiriya bari bake, harimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines na Qantas, mu gihe kompanyi y'indege y'akarere ya Flybe yo mu Bwongereza yasenyutse.
Ingaruka z'ibyo byago ku ruganda rw'amato y'ubwato, zari zitigeze zigera ku rugero rungana n'urwo.
