Gusura abacuruzi mu Burayi no muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo byagabanutseho 40%.
Abacuruzi bacuruza mu buryo bw'amafaranga mu bihugu byo muri Amerika y'Amajyaruguru no mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, bariyongereyeho 50-60%.
Ibi kandi byatumye urujya n'uruza rw'abanyamaguru mu bigo by'ubucuruzi mu kwezi kwa gatatu rugabanukaho 3343% ugereranyije na Gashyantare.
Abafite amaduka ku isi hose bashyizeho izindi ngamba, nko kongera isuku, gushyiraho ibyuma bifata ubushyuhe kugira ngo barebe ubushyuhe bw'abaguzi, no guhagarika ibikorwa. Nk'uko Komisiyo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ishinzwe ubukungu muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo ibivuga, ubukene buterwa n'icyorezo bushobora gutuma abantu bari hagati ya miliyoni 14 na 22 barushaho gukena muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo kurusha uko byari kugenda iyo hataza kubaho icyorezo.
Muri Mutarama na Gashyantare 2020, mu gihe icyorezo cyari ku isonga mu mujyi wa Wuhan, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 5 bo mu Bushinwa batakaje akazi kabo.
Abenshi mu bakozi b'abimukira bo mu byaro bagera hafi kuri miliyoni 300 bo mu Bushinwa bari baraye mu bihugu byo mu gihugu hagati cyangwa bari bafungiye mu ntara ya Hubei. Muri Werurwe 2020, Abanyamerika barenga miliyoni 10 batakaje akazi kabo kandi basaba ubufasha bwa leta.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora gutwara akazi miliyoni 47 muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika kandi umubare w'abashomeri ushobora kugera kuri 32%, nk'uko byemezwa na Banki y'Igihugu y'Igihugu y'Igihugu y'Imiteguro ya Leta ya St. Louis. Gufunga mu Buhinde byatumye abakozi b'Abanyamahanga babarirwa muri za miriyoni mirongo (bahembwa binyuze mu mishahara ya buri munsi) batagira akazi. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'Ikigo cya Angus Reid bwagaragaje ko 44% by'ingo zo muri Kanada zahuye n'ubushomeri bw'uburyo runaka. Abakozi hafi 900,000 batakaje akazi muri Esipanye kuva aho hashyizweho gukumira mu kwezi kwa Werurwe 2020.
