Ubufaransa n'Ubwongereza byemeye gahunda y'ubudage yo kwishyura abakozi bakora igihe gito.
Urwego rw'ubuhanzi n'umurage ndangamuco rwatewe cyane n'icyorezo, bigira ingaruka ku mikorere y'imiryango ndetse n'abantu ku giti cyabobaba abakora cyangwa abikoreraku isi hose.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuhanzi n'umuco yagerageje gushyigikira inshingano zabo (akenshi zitangirwa amafaranga na leta) zo guha uburenganzira ku mutungo ndangamuco mu baturage, kubungabunga umutekano w'abakozi babo n'abaturage, no gushyigikira abahanzi aho bishoboka.
Muri Werurwe 2020, ku isi hose no mu byiciro bitandukanye, inzu ndangamurage, ibitabo, ibibanza by'imyidagaduro n'ibindi bigo by'umuco byari byarafunzwe igihe kitazwi n'imurikagurisha ryabyo, ibirori n'imyidagaduro byahagaritswe cyangwa byasubitswe.
Mu gusubiza, habaye imihati ikomeye yo gutanga serivisi zindi binyuze mu buryo bwa digitale. Indi ngaruka iherutse kandi yihuta y'iki cyorezo ni uguhagarika imirimo y'idini, ibirori bikomeye bya siporo, n'ibindi bikorwa by'imibanire, nk'ibirori by'umuziki n'ibitaramo, inama z'ikoranabuhanga, n'imurika imideli.
Uruganda rwa sinema na rwo rwahuye n'ibibazo. Vatikani yatangaje ko imihango yo kwizihiza Icyumweru cyera i Roma, iba mu cyumweru cya nyuma cy'igihe cy'icyunamo cya Gikristo, yahagaritswe.
Diyosezi nyinshi zasabye abakristu bakuze kuguma mu rugo aho kujya mu misa ku cyumweru; amadini amwe na amwe yatumye amateraniro y'itorero aboneka kuri radiyo, kuri interineti cyangwa kuri televiziyo mu gihe andi atanga gahunda yo gusenga mu modoka.
Kubera ko Diyosezi ya Roma Gatolika yafunze insengero zayo n'insengero zayo, kandi Intara ya Mutagatifu Petero igahita isenywa n'abagenzi b'Abakristo, izindi nzego z'amadini na zo zahagaritse imirimo yo gusenga kandi zitangira guteranira mu nsengero, mu misigiti, mu masinagogi, mu nsengero no mu masengero.
Minisiteri y'Ubuzima ya Irani yatangaje ko amasengesho yo kuwa gatanu yahagaritswe mu duce twatewe n'icyorezo kandi nyuma yaho insengero zarafunzwe, mu gihe Arabiya Sawudite yabujije abanyamahanga bakora ingendo z'ubutagatifu ndetse n'abaturage bayo kwinjira mu duce twera twa Mecca na Medina.
Iki cyorezo cyateje ihungabana rikomeye cyane ku ngengabihe y'imikino ku isi kuva mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi.
Imikino myinshi ikomeye yahagaritswe cyangwa isubikwa, harimo 201920 UEFA Champions League, 201920 Premier League, UEFA Euro 2020, 201920 NBA season, na 201920 NHL season.
Iki cyorezo cyasenye gahunda za Olempike zo mu mpeshyi zo mu 2020, zari ziteganyijwe gutangira mu mpera za Nyakanga; Komite Mpuzamahanga ya Olempiki yatangaje ku ya 24 Werurwe ko iki gikorwa "kizasubikwa kikajya mu minsi iri inyuma ya 2020 ariko bitarenze impeshyi ya 2021". Kasino n'ahandi hantu hakinirwa imikino ku isi hose hafunguwe kandi amarushanwa ya poker y'ubuzima yasubitswe cyangwa yahagaritswe.
Ibi byatumye abakinnyi benshi bajya kuri interineti, aho imbuga nyinshi z'imikino yo kuri interineti zitangaza ko umubare w'abitabiriye imikino y'amahirwe wiyongereye cyane. Uruganda rw'imyidagaduro narwo rwagize ingaruka, amakipe atandukanye y'umuzika ahagarika cyangwa akahagarika ingendo z'ibitaramo.
