Bamwe mu bahanzi basuzumye uburyo bwo gukomeza gukora no gusangira imirimo kuri enterineti nk'uburyo bwo guhitamo imiterere isanzwe yo kumurika ibihangano, nk'ibitaramo byo kumurika imideli cyangwa gukora "ibirori" bishingiye kuri interineti ku bahanzi gukora, gukwirakwiza no kumenyekanisha imirimo yabo.
Kuri interineti, imivugo myinshi yo kuri interineti ifite insanganyamatsiko ya coronavirus yakwirakwiriye kuko benshi bahindukiriye gusetsa no kwirangaza mu gihe nta cyizere gihari.
Kuva icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangira, abantu bafite inkomoko mu Bushinwa no mu Burasirazuba bwa Aziya, ndetse n'abaturutse mu bihugu byugarijwe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19, barushijeho kurengerwa n'urwikekwe, urwikekwe rw'abanyamahanga n'ivangura rishingiye ku moko.
Mu bihugu byinshi, cyane cyane mu Burayi, muri Aziya y'i Burasirazuba, muri Amerika y'Amajyaruguru no mu karere ka Aziya na Pasifika, abantu bagiye bagaragaza ko bafite ubwoba, bashidikanya kandi ko batabakunda.
