Ibizamini byo muri laboratwari byo gupima indwara y'ubwandu bwa coronavirus yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi ifitanye isano na yo ya SARS-CoV-2 bikubiyemo uburyo bwo gutahura ko virusi iriho n'ubwo kumenya ko hari udukoko twanduza twatewe n'ubwandu.
Kuba virusi ziboneka mu bipimo byemezwa na RT-PCR, igaragaza RNA ya koronavirusi.
Iki kizamini ni cyihariye kandi kigamije gutahura gusa RNA ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza ubwandu buherutse cyane cyangwa bukomeje.
Kugaragaza za 'antibodies' (serology) bishobora gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini by'abasirikare b'umubiri bigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye, harimo n'abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyane ku buryo batabivuga cyangwa batagaragaza ibimenyetso.
Ibipimo by'urupfu rw'iyo ndwara n'urwego rw'ubudahangarwa bw'ubwoko mu baturage bishobora kumenyekana neza hifashishijwe ibivuye muri iki kizamini.
Kubera gupima ku rugero ruciriritse, kugeza muri Werurwe 2020 nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku bijyanye n'ubwandu bwa virusi mu baturage bacyo.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyakoze ibizamini ku bantu barenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini mu bipimo byakozwe mu bihugu bitandukanye.
Ibi bishobora no kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku bipimo by'urupfu byatangajwe, bikaba bishobora kuba birenze urugero mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo guhinduranya inyandiko (rRT-PCR) mu gihe nyacyo, ikizamini gishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero byafashwe hakoreshejwe uburyo butandukanye, harimo no gufata isamuti yo mu mazuru cyangwa isamuti y'amahembe.
Ibisubizo muri rusange biboneka mu masaha make kugeza ku minsi 2.
Igishushanyo mbonera cya RT-PCR gikoreshwa mu gupima mu muhogo ni icyo kwizerwa mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'indwara.
Nyuma y'aho, virusi ishobora kuzimira mu muhogo mu gihe ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku bantu banduye bapimwe mu cyumweru cya kabiri, ikindi ni uko ibipimo bishobora gutorwa mu nzira z'umwuka zimbitse hakoreshejwe catéters zo gukoramo cyangwa hakakoreshwa ibipimo byo gukorora (umwanda).
Imwe mu ncuro za mbere y'ibizamini bya PCR yakozwe muri Charité i Berlin muri Mutarama 2020 hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo guhererekanya amakuru mu gihe nyacyo (rRT-PCR), kandi ni yo yashingiyeho ibikoresho 250.000 byo gukwirakwiza byakozwe n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
Ubwongereza nabwo bwari bwakoze ikizamini ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Isosiyete yo muri Koreya y'Epfo Kogenebiotech yatangije ikigo cy'ubuvuzi, gishingiye kuri PCR cyo gupima SARS-CoV-2 (PowerChek Coronavirus) ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
Igerageza gushaka ubwoko bwa "E" busanzwe bw'indwara ya koronavirusi ya beta, n'ubwoko bwa RdRp bwihariye kuri SARS-CoV-2.Mu Bushinwa, BGI Group ni kimwe mu bigo bya mbere byahawe uruhushya rwo gukoresha mu buryo bwihutirwa n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe Ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa ku gikoresho cyo gupima SARS-CoV-2 gishingiye kuri PCR. Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) kiri gutanga ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cya 2019-Novel Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) mu gihe nyacyo RT-PCR ku bigo by'ubuvuzi binyuze mu ikoranabuhanga mpuzamahanga.
Kimwe mu bipimo bitatu bya jenoside mu mashusho ya kera y'ibikoresho byo gupima cyatumye habaho ibisubizo bidafite ishingiro kubera ibipimo bidakora neza, n'ikibazo cy'ibipimo muri CDC i Atlanta; ibi byatumye ingero nkeya ku munsi zigera ku 100 zikorwa neza muri Gashyantare 2020.
Ibizamini bikoresha ibice bibiri ntibyemejwe ko ari ibyiringirwa kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, kandi kugeza icyo gihe ni bwo laboratoire za leta n'iz'ibanze zemerewe gutangira gupima.
Iki kizamini cyemejwe n'ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti (Food and Drug Administration) mu gihe cy'amabwiriza y'uko gikoreshwa mu bihe bidasanzwe. Ibitaro by'ubucuruzi byo muri Amerika byatangiye gupima mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020.
Guhera ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko COVID-19 igeragezwa mu gihugu hose hashingiwe kuri RT-PCR.
Quest Diagnostics na yo yashyizeho ibipimo bya COVID-19 mu gihugu hose guhera ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta bipimo by'ibanze byatangajwe; gufata ibipimo no kubitunganya bigomba gukorwa hakurikijwe ibisabwa na CDC.
Mu Burusiya, ikizamini cya COVID-19 cyakozwe kandi gitangwa n'Ikigo cya Leta cy'Ubushakashatsi mu by'Ubumenyi bw'Urugingo n'Ikoranabuhanga VECTOR.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, iki kizamini cyanditswe na Serivisi ya Leta ishinzwe kugenzura ubuvuzi. Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, Mayo Clinic yatangaje ko yateguye ikizamini cyo gutahura ubwandu bwa COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Roche Diagnostics yahawe uruhushya na FDA rwo gukora ikizamini gishobora gukorwa mu masaha 3.5 mu bwinshi, bityo imashini imwe ikora ibizamini bigera ku 4,128 mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa (EUA) ku ma Laboratoire ya Abbott kugirango ikore igerageza kuri sisitemu ya Abbott ya m2000; FDA yari yaratanze uruhushya rusa n'urwo kuri Hologic, LabCorp, na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cepheid na yo yahawe EUA na FDA kugirango ikore ikizamini kimara iminota 45.
FDA yemeje ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi gikoresha ikoranabuhanga ryo kongerera ingufu za nucleic acid mu buryo bw'ubushyuhe (isothermal nucleic acid amplification technology) aho gukoresha PCR.
Kubera ko ibyo bidasaba ko habaho imihindagurikire y'ubushyuhe, ubwo buryo bushobora gutanga ibisubizo byiza mu minota itanu gusa, naho ibisubizo bibi bikaboneka mu minota 13.
Muri iki gihe muri Amerika hari imashini zigera ku 18,000 kandi Abbott iteganya kongera inganda kugira ngo zigeze ku bipimo 50,000 ku munsi. Igerageza rikoresha umuti wa monoclonal wifatanya by'umwihariko na poroteyine ya nucleocapsid (poroteyine ya N) ya coronavirus nshya ririmo rirakorwa muri Taiwan, rifite icyizere ko rishobora gutanga ibisubizo mu minota 15 kugeza kuri 20 nk'uko bigenda ku bipimo bya grippe byihuse.
Isuzuma ryakozwe mu kwezi kwa Werurwe 2020 ryagaragaje ko "amashusho ya radiographie y'igituza nta gaciro kanini afite mu gusuzuma indwara mu bihe bya mbere, mu gihe ibipimo bya CT [computed tomography] bishobora kuba biriho mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira".
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe kuri CT birimo impande ebyiri z'ibirahuri byinshi by'ibirahuri bifite impande, ibinyuranye n'ibisanzwe n'ibiri inyuma.
Iyo indwara igenda irushaho gukomera, habaho kuba umuntu arusha abandi imbaraga, kandi akagira imbaraga zo kwihangana.
Ubushakashatsi bugereranya PCR na CT i Wuhan aho icyorezo cyatangiriye, bwagaragaje ko CT ifite ibyiyumvo byinshi kurusha PCR, nubwo idasobanutse neza, aho ibintu byinshi byerekana amashusho yayo bihuza n'ibindi bibazo by'ibicurane n'indwara.
Guhera muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika cy'Ubuvuzi bw'Imirase cyatangaje ko "CT itagomba gukoreshwa mu gupima cyangwa nk'igerageza rya mbere ryo gupima COVID-19". Guhera muri Werurwe 2020, CDC itanga inama yo gukoresha PCR mu gupima bwa mbere.
Igice cy'igisubizo cy'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya ubwandu ni ugukora za 'antibodies' zirimo IgM na IgG.
Ibi bishobora gukoreshwa mu gutahura ubwandu mu bantu guhera ku minsi 7 cyangwa irenga nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso, mu kumenya ubudahangarwa, no mu kugenzura abaturage. Ibizamini bishobora gukorwa mu ma laboratoire nkuru (CLT) cyangwa mu gupima ahantu ho kwivuza (PoCT).
Sisitemu zikorana n'ikoranabuhanga zifite ubushobozi bwo gukora cyane mu ma laboratoiri menshi y'ubuvuzi zizashobora gukora ibi bipimo ariko kuba zizabaho bizaterwa n'umubare w'ibikoresho buri sisitemu izakora.
Ku bw'iyo miti, hakunze gukoreshwa ibipimo by'amaraso y'uruhande rumwe, nubwo ibipimo by'uruhererekane bishobora gukoreshwa mu gukurikirana ibisubizo by'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara.
Mu gihe cyo gukoresha uburyo bwa PoCT, akenshi hafatwa amaraso rimwe gusa binyuze mu gutobora uruhu.
