Kugeza ku ya 7 Mata 2020, ni ibizamini byonyine byemejwe na FDA mu gihe cy'uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, ibizamini bya Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics na Epitope Diagnostics byahawe uburenganzira bw'u Burayi ku bikoresho byabo byo gupima, bishobora gutahura IgG na IgA antibody zica virusi mu bipimo by'amaraso.
