Gukaraba intoki (cyangwa gukaraba intoki), nanone bizwi nka isuku y'intoki, ni igikorwa cyo gusukura intoki z'umuntu mu rwego rwo gukuraho umukungugu, ibinure, mikorobe cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabuni buri gihe mu "bihe bikomeye" by'umunsi birinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'indwara y'ibisebe na kolera, zikwirakwizwa binyuze mu kanwa.
Abantu bashobora kandi kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero nk'ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane bisanzwe, urugero, iyo badakarabye intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, izuru cyangwa umunwa (ni ukuvuga mucous membranes).
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi ku munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ari ngombwa harimo: mbere na nyuma yo gusama, nyuma yo gusukura amabere y'umwana cyangwa guhindura amasahani, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya na mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukorana n'inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Niba nta mazi n'isabune bihari, amaboko ashobora gukaraba n'imyotsi. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) risaba ko umuntu yoza intoki:
Mbere yo guteka, mu gihe uteka na nyuma yo guteka.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindurira umwana ibishyimbo cyangwa se nyuma yo kumujyana mu bwiherero.
Nyuma yo guhumeka, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ku biryo byayo cyangwa ku myanda yayo.
Isuku y'amaboko mu buvuzi ni isuku ikorwa mu gihe cyo kuvura.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa kwitabwaho bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Intego nyamukuru yo gukaraba intoki mu buvuzi ni uguhumanya intoki z'ibimera byateza indwara (indwara, virusi cyangwa ibindi bikoko bishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho bya kirimbuzi bishobora guteza uburwayi cyangwa indwara.
Ibi ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakoresha ibiribwa cyangwa bakora mu buvuzi, ariko kandi ni ingenzi ku baturage muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bigira akamaro kenshi ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, coronavirus n'izindi ndwara zitandura; gukumira indwara zandura zitera igifu; kugabanya indwara z'ubuhumekero;
no kugabanya igipimo cy'impfu z'abana babyarira mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki neza bishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu barushaho gukura.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero n'iz'ibisebe ushobora kugabanuka mu gihe hakozwe impinduka zoroheje mu myifatire, urugero nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Iyo myifatire yoroshye ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa bazize izo ndwara ugera hafi kuri 50%.
Gushyiraho ingamba zo gukaraba intoki bishobora kugabanya ibicurane ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, kandi ibyo bishobora kugereranywa no gutanga amazi meza mu duce dukennye.
48% by'ibyago byo kurwara igicuri byagabanutse bitewe no gukaraba intoki n'isabuni. Gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ni bwo buryo bumwe bw'ingirakamaro kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda igicuri n'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye (ARI), kuko bikorwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage ku isi hose.
Indwara y'ibihaha, ari na yo mpamvu ikomeye ituma abana bapfa, ni yo ahanini ihitana abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, kandi bivugwa ko ihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1,8 buri mwaka.
Indwara y'igifu n'iy'ibihaha ni byo bituma abana bagera hafi kuri miriyoni 3,5 bapfa buri mwaka.
UNICEF ivuga ko gukaraba intoki n'isabuni mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero bishobora kurokora ubuzima bw'abantu benshi kurusha urukingo cyangwa imiti iyo ari yo yose, kuko bigabanya hafi kimwe cya kabiri umubare w'abapfa bazize indwara y'ibisebe, naho abahitanywe n'indwara z'ubuhumekero bikabije bakagabanya kimwe cya kane.
Gukaraba intoki akenshi biba biri kumwe n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku nk'igice cy'ingamba zo gukingira amazi, isuku n'isuku (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki kandi birinda impetigo yandura binyuze mu guhura n'umuntu mu buryo butaziguye.
Ingaruka mbi nke zo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora gutuma uruhu rukomereka bitewe no kumuka kw'uruhu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Danemark mu mwaka wa 2012 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ikibazo cy'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'amaboko, bita eczema cyangwa dermatite y'intoki, cyane cyane mu bakora mu by'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane na byo bifatwa nk'ikimenyetso cy'indwara y'ubuhumyi (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu bikomeye ku munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ari ngombwa mu kugabanya ubwandu bw'indwara binyuze mu busa: nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero (gukorora, gusama), nyuma yo gusukura amabere y'umwana (guhindura amasahani), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya no mbere/nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukorana n'inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Mu bindi bihe umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki neza kugira ngo yirinde kwandura indwara harimo mbere na nyuma yo kuvura igikomere cyangwa igikomere; nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa guhumeka; nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'amatungo cyangwa gukorakora inyamaswa; no nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, abantu bake cyane ni bo bakoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi ku myenda mu bihugu 54 mu 2015 bwagaragaje ko ku kigereranyo, 38.7% by'ingo zikoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki.Ubushakashatsi bwo mu 2014 bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ari yo ifite igipimo cyo hejuru cya 97%, Amerika iri hafi ya 77%, naho Ubushinwa bukaba ari bwo bufite igipimo cyo hasi cya 23%.Ubu hari uburyo butandukanye bwo guhindura imyitwarire bwo kongera abantu bakoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki mu bihe bikomeye. Gukaraba intoki mu matsinda ku bana biga mu masaha runaka y'umunsi ni bumwe mu buryo bwo mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere bwo gushyiraho uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki mu myitwarire y'abana.
"Gahunda y'Ubuvuzi bw'Ingenzi" yashyizweho n'Urwego rw'Igihugu rw'Uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa byo guteza imbere ubuzima n'uburezi bw'abana.
Gukuraho udukoko kabiri mu mwaka, kongeramo gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabuni, gukaraba amenyo buri munsi ukoresheje fluoride, ni byo by'ingenzi muri iyi gahunda y'igihugu.
Nanone kandi, yashyizwe mu bikorwa mu buryo bugira ingaruka nziza muri Indoneziya.
Iyo amazi ashyirwamo amasabune cyangwa imiti yo kumesa, bituma uturemangingo two mu mubiri dutera indwara tuva mu ruhu.
Imikorere y'ibikoresho by'isabune n'ibikoresho by'isuku ni ugugabanya inzitizi zituma amazi adakama, no kongera uburyo bwo gusama.
Amazi yonyine nta cyo avuze mu gusukura uruhu kubera ko ibinure na poroteyine, ari byo bigize ubutaka, bitakemuka mu mazi mu buryo bworoshye.
Icyakora, isuku ifashwa n'amazi menshi.
Kubera ko isabune ikomeye ishobora kongera gukoreshwa, ishobora kuba irimo mikorobe z'ibicurane.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwakozwe ku mikorobe zituruka ku isabune ihumanye, bwagaragaje ko iyo mikorobe idashobora gutembera kuko iyo mikorobe zigeze mu mazi, bayihanagura.
Ikigo cya CDC kiracyemeza ko "isabuni ifite amazi n'ibikoresho byo kuyikoresha nta muntu uyikoresha ari byo byiza".
Hari abantu benshi bifuza kumenya uko amasabune arwanya za bagiteri akora.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya igaragaza ko gukoresha imiti yica udukoko cyangwa imiti yica udukoko mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko bigabanya indwara ziterwa n'udukoko twigirira imiti igabanya ubukana.
Icyakora, amasabune arwanya za bagiteri aba arimo imiti ikoreshwa na za bagiteri, urugero nka triclosan, ifite urutonde rw'utundi dukoko tw'ubwoko bwinshi tw'utundi dukoko twirinda indwara.
Bityo rero, nubwo amoko arwanya imiti igabanya ubukana ataba yatoranyijwe n'amasabune arwanya za bagiteri, ashobora kuba adafite ingaruka nziza nk'uko byatangajwe.
Uretse umukozi w'uruhu n'urundi rukingira uruhu, imiterere ihambaye ishobora kuba irimo aside (acide acétique, aside ascorbique, acide lactique) nk'umugenzuzi wa pH, acide benzoïque ikora mu kurwanya mikorobe n'ibindi bikoresho bifasha uruhu (aloe vera, vitamine, menthol, ibimera). Isesengura ryuzuye ryakozwe na Kaminuza ya Oregon School of Public Health ryerekanye ko isabune isanzwe igira ingaruka nziza nko mu sabune z'ibanze zikoreshwa n'abantu benshi zirwanya za bagiteri zirimo triclosan mu gukumira indwara no gukura za bagiteri ku biganza.
Amazi ashyushye akwiriye gukoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki ntabwo ashyushye bihagije ku buryo yica mikorobe.
Bakteri zikura vuba cyane ku bushyuhe bw'umubiri (37 °C).
Icyakora, amazi ashyushye n'isabune ni meza cyane kurusha amazi akonje n'isabune mu gukuraho amavuta aturuka ku ibidukikije, arimo ubutaka n'udukoko.
Icyakora, mu buryo bunyuranye n'uko abantu benshi babitekereza, ubushakashatsi bwa siyansi bwagaragaje ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye nta ngaruka bigira ku kugabanya mikorobe ziba mu biganza.
Umwandazi w'amaboko cyangwa umuti wica udukoko two mu ntoki ni umuti utariho amazi wo gusukura intoki.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, imiti yo gusukura intoki itari mu mazi (izitwa kandi ko ari imiti yo gusukura intoki, imiti yo gusukura intoki cyangwa imiti yo guhanagura intoki) yatangiye kwamamara.
Inyinshi zishingira kuri isopropyl alcohol cyangwa ethanol zashyizwe hamwe n'imiti ituma ibinyabiziga bihinduka nk'icyatsi cya Carbomer (polymer ya acrylic acid) mu buryo bwa gel, cyangwa umutobe nk'umuti wa glycerine mu buryo bw'amazi, cyangwa ifu kugira ngo bikorohere gukoresha no kugabanya ingaruka zo kumesa za alcohol.
Kongeramo hydrogen-peroxide yagabanutse byongera ibikorwa byo kurwanya mikorobe. Imiti yica udukoko mu biganza irimo nibura 60 kugeza kuri 95% bya alukoro ni imiti yica udukoko.
Imiti yica udukoko duto cyane, mikorobe zitwara imiti itandukanye (MRSA na VRE), igituntu, virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo virusi itera SIDA, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, vaccinia, influenza na hepatite) n'ibicurane.
Imiti yica udukoko tugize intoki irimo 70% by'inzoga yica 99,97% (3.5 log reduction, isa n'igabanuka rya decibel 35) y'udukoko two ku maboko nyuma y'amasegonda 30 tuyikoresheje na 99,99% kugeza kuri 99,999% (4 kugeza kuri 5 log reduction) y'udukoko two ku maboko nyuma y'umunota umwe tuyikoresheje. Imiti yica udukoko tugize intoki igira ingaruka nziza cyane ku mikorobe ariko ikaba idakora neza ku mikorobe zimwe na zimwe.
Imiti yica udukoko two mu biganza ikoreshwa kuri alukoro nta ngaruka igira ku mikorobe yo mu bwoko bwa norovirus (cyangwa Norwalk), ari na yo mpamvu ikunze gutera indwara y'urwungano rw'amaraso. Igikoresho gihagije cyo guhanagura intoki cyangwa inzoga bigomba gukoreshwa mu gusukura neza intoki cyangwa mu kuzipfuka zose.
Imbere n'inyuma y'amaboko yombi ndetse hagati n'impande z'intoki zose, bisukwaho amasegonda agera kuri 30 kugeza amazi, ifu cyangwa umutobe bikamye.
Insonga z'intoki zigomba gukaraba neza, zikajya zisiga mu ntoki zombi. Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitanga inama yo gukaraba intoki mu gihe usukura intoki, cyane cyane igihe intoki ziba zanduye.
Gukoresha cyane izi nzitizi bishingiye ku buryo bworoshye bwo kuzikoresha no ku buryo zihita zica utunyabuzima duto; ariko, ntizigomba gusimbura gukaraba intoki neza keretse igihe isabune n'amazi bitagaragara.
Gukoresha kenshi imiti yica udukoko tw'amaboko irimo inzoga bishobora gutuma uruhu rukonja keretse iyo imiti yo koroshya uruhu n'imiti yo kuruhumuriza yongewe muri iyo miti.
Ingaruka zo kumena za alukoro zishobora kugabanuka cyangwa zikarandurwa hifashishijwe glycerine na/cyangwa ibindi bikoresho byoroshya mu buryo bwo gutunganya.
Mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi, imiti yica udukoko mu ntoki ikoreshwa mu gusukura intoki irimo inzoga, yatuma uruhu rudakara cyane kandi rukagira ubushyuhe buke ugereranyije n'amasabune cyangwa imiti yo gusukura intoki ikoreshwa mu kurwanya mikorobe.
Indwara y'uruhu iterwa n'ubushyuhe, indwara y'inkorora cyangwa ibyiyumvo byo kurenza urugero ku nzoga cyangwa ku bintu byongera ku nzoga biboneka mu byo gukoramo intoki.
Kuba abantu barwara indwara y'uruhu ituma umuntu atakaza ubushobozi bwo guhangana n'uburwayi bw'uruhu, byaje kuba ibintu bishishikaje ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'amazi n'isabune.
Nubwo bikora neza, imiti itari amazi ntiyuhagira intoki ibintu by'ibinyabuzima, ahubwo irazihumanya gusa.
Ni yo mpamvu imiti yica udukoko twanduza intoki idakora neza nk'isabune n'amazi mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, kuko izo ndwara zikiri ku ntoki.
Imiti ihanagura intoki idafite inzoga iba ifite ubushobozi buhambaye bitewe n'ibikoresho n'uburyo ikoreshwamo, kandi mu mateka, imiti ihanagura intoki idafite inzoga n'imiti ihanagura intoki idafite inzoga, ntiyagize icyo igeraho.
Vuba aha, byagaragaye ko imiti ikoresha benzalkonium chloride igira ubushobozi bwo kurwanya mikorobe buhoraho kandi bw'igihe kirekire nyuma yo kuyinywa, bitandukanye n'inzoga, yagaragaye ko igira ingaruka nke nyuma yo kuyinywa kenshi, wenda bitewe n'ingaruka mbi z'uruhu zigenda zigenda zigabanuka.
Abantu benshi batuye mu duce dukennye ntibashobora kubona isabune, ahubwo bakoresha ivu cyangwa ubutaka.
Ivu cyangwa ubutaka bishobora kugira ingaruka nziza kurusha amazi yonyine, ariko bishobora kugira ingaruka nke kurusha isabune.
Ikintu kimwe kibahangayikisha ni uko iyo ubutaka cyangwa ivu byandujwe utunyabuzima duto bishobora gutuma indwara zikomeza gukwirakwira aho kugabanya uko gukwirakwira.
Kimwe n'isabune, ivu na ryo rifasha mu kuvura indwara kuko iyo rihuye n'amazi riba rifite umusemburo.
OMS yatanze inama yo gukoresha ivu cyangwa umucanga mu gihe nta sabune ihari.
Uburyo bukwiye bwo gukaraba intoki bwasabwe n'ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara, bukubiyemo intambwe zikurikira:
Gufata intoki ukoresheje amazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje.
Hari igihe amazi aba ari menshi cyane, ariko iyo amazi ari mu mazi meza, nta cyo aba atwaye.
Jya usukura intoki zawe ukoresheje isabune nyinshi, hakubiyemo n'iz'inyuma, hagati y'intoki n'iz'ibinono.
Amasabuni akura mikorobe ku ruhu, kandi ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko abantu bakunda gukaraba intoki neza iyo bakoresheje amasabuni aho gukoresha amazi yonyine.
Jya usukura mu gihe cy'amasegonda 20.
Iyo umuntu agikubise bituma uruhu rw'umubiri ruhuha, bityo bigatuma rukuraho za mikorobe, kandi iyo akomeje kugikubita igihe kirekire, bituma rukuraho izindi mikorobe.
Jya usukura neza amazi.
Gukaraba intoki mu mazi bishobora kongera kwanduza intoki.
Ujye uyumesa akato cyangwa ureke umareho.
Amaboko y'amazi n'amanyo arushaho kwandura vuba. Ahantu hakunze kubura ni ikiganza cy'iburyo, mu ijosi, hagati y'intoki no munsi y'amano.
Inzara n'ibicurane by'amabara bishobora kuba bifite mikorobe.
Akenshi, hari imiti yo kwisiga kugira ngo intoki zidakama; uruhu rwumye rushobora kwangiza uruhu, ibyo bikaba bishobora kongera ibyago byo kwandura indwara.
Uburyo butandukanye bw'igiciro gito bushobora gukorwa mu koroshya gukaraba intoki aho amazi yo mu musarani na/cyangwa isabune bitaraboneka, urugero nko gusuka amazi mu gikarabiro cyangwa mu nkangara bihanitse bifite imyobo ikwiriye na/cyangwa gukoresha ivu mu gihe bibaye ngombwa mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere. Mu bihe aho amazi aba make (urugero nk'amashuri cyangwa uduce two mu cyaro mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hari ibisubizo byo kugabanya amazi, nk' "ibikarabiro" n'ubundi buryo bw'igiciro gito.
Ikimashini cyitwa tippy-tap ni uburyo bworoshye bwo gukoresha ikimashini gihanitse ku mugozi, n'inkoni ikoreshwa n'ibirenge kugira ngo basuke amazi make ku biganza n'isabune.
Kumesa neza intoki ni ikintu cy'ingenzi mu isuku y'intoki, ariko hari impaka ku buryo bwiza bwo kuzimya mu bwiherero rusange.
Ubushakashatsi bugenda bwiyongera bugaragaza ko utwenda two mu rupapuro tuba dufite isuku kurusha utwuma two kumesa intoki dukoreshwa n'amashanyarazi dusanga mu byumba byinshi byo kwiyuhagiriramo.
Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Westminster, i Londres, kandi bwatewe inkunga n'uruganda rw'impuzamirimo y'impapuro, European Tissue Symposium, mu kugereranya igipimo cy'isuku gitangwa n'impuzamirimo y'impapuro, imashini zimesa intoki z'umwuka ushyushye n'imashini zimesa intoki zigezweho z'umwuka.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumesa intoki mu gikoresho cy'umwuka ushyushye, umubare w'indwara zose zabakiteri wabonetse wiyongereye ku kigereranyo ku ntoki ku kigero cya 194% no ku ntoki ku kigero cya 254%.
Iyo umuntu yumye akoresheje imashini imesa, umubare w'indwara zose ziri ku ntoki wiyongeraho 42%, naho izo mu ntoki ziyongeraho 15%.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumesa intoki ukoresheje agatambaro k'impapuro, umubare w'udukoko muri rusange wagabanutse ugera kuri 76% ku ntoki no ku ntoki ugera kuri 77%. Abahanga mu bya siyansi kandi bakoze ibizamini kugira ngo bamenye niba hari amahirwe yo kwanduza abandi bakoresha ubwiherero n'ibidukikije byo mu bwiherero bitewe n'uburyo bw'umwuko bwa buri bwoko.
Umwumazi w'umwuka uturuka mu cyumba cy'ubwiherero, uhumeka umwuka ku muvuduko wa 180 m/s (650 km/h; 400 mph), washoboraga guhumeka mikorobe mu ntoki no mu cyumba cy'ubwiherero kandi bishobora kwanduza abandi bakoresha ubwiherero n'aho ubwiherero buba ku ntera ya metero 2.
Gukoresha umwumazi w'intoki ukoresha umwuka ushyushye, bikwirakwiza mikorobe mu ntera ya metero 0,25 uvuye ku umwumazi.
Ibikoresho by'impu byerekanaga ko nta mikorobe nyinshi zikwirakwira.Mu 2005, mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt und Umwelt, uburyo butandukanye bwo kumesa intoki bwarahujwe.
Hakozwe ibi bikurikira mu mibare y'udukoko nyuma yo kumesa intoki:
Hariho abacuruzi benshi batandukanye b'ibikoresho byo kumesa intoki, kandi ibyuma byo kumesa intoki byagereranyijwe no kumesa utwenda tw'impapuro.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje utwenda two gukaraba intoki ni ubundi buryo bwo gukora mu gihe cy'urugendo mu gihe nta isabune n'amazi bihari.
Umwandazi w'amaboko ukoreshwa ku bw'inzoga ugomba kuba urimo nibura 60% bya alukoro.
Gukaraba intoki mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi byabaye itegeko nyuma y'igihe kirekire umuganga w'Umuhungariya witwa Ignaz Semmelweis avumbuye ko ari ingirakamaro (mu wa 1846) mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro.
Hari ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bitanga amakuru yo kwibutsa abakozi b'ibitaro ko bagomba gukaraba intoki iyo bibagiwe.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko iyo imiti igabanya ubukana bw'indwara.
Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi ni mu gihe cy'amasegonda 15 nibura, ukoresheje amasabuni menshi n'amazi cyangwa umutobe kugira ngo usigeho ifu kandi usigeho ibice byose by'intoki.
Amaboko agomba guhanagurwa, intoki zikaba zisanzwe ziganje.
Niba hari ibisigisigi biri munsi y'amano, ushobora kubikuraho ukoresheje isutiye.
Kubera ko mikorobe zishobora kuguma mu mazi ku biganza, ni iby'ingenzi ko ubyuhagira neza kandi ukabihanagura ukoresheje agatambaro gasukuye.
Nyuma yo kuyumesa, igikoresho cy'impapuro cy'umwenda kigomba gukoreshwa mu gufunga amazi (kandi mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, gufungura inzugi zose z'aho umuntu ava).
Ibi birinda kongera kwanduza intoki zivuye kuri ibyo bice.
Gukaraba intoki mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bigamije gukuraho udukoko duto dutera indwara ("indwara") no kwirinda ko twandura.
Ikinyamakuru cyitwa The New England Journal of Medicine kivuga ko mu bigo byinshi by'ubuvuzi, abantu benshi badakaraba intoki, kuko abaganga benshi n'abaforomo bibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi, bityo bakanduza abandi mikorobe.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki neza n'indi mirimo yoroheje bishobora kugabanya umubare w'indwara z'amaraso ziterwa n'imashini z'umuyoboro wa kateteri ku kigero cya 66 ku ijana. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryasohoye inyandiko igaragaza uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki n'uburyo bwo kuzigorora mu nzego z'ubuvuzi.
Inyandiko y'ubuyobozi bw'iryo shyirahamwe ku bijyanye n'isuku y'intoki ishobora no kuboneka ku rubuga rwayo rwa interineti kugira ngo rubanda rubisobanukirwe.
Whitby et al. bakoze isuzuma ryerekeye icyo kibazo.
Ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi bishobora gupima no kwemeza isuku y'intoki, niba hakenewe kugaragaza ko amategeko yubahirizwa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima rifite "Ibihe bitanu" byo gukaraba intoki:
nyuma yo guhura n'amaraso/amazi yo mu mubiri
mbere yo gukora igikorwa cyo kugabanya imyanda, kandi
nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.Kongera imiti yica udukoko mu isabune ("isabuni ikoreshwa imiti" cyangwa "irwanya udukoko") bituma umuti wica intoki.
Ibyo bishobora kuba ngombwa mbere yo kubagwa cyangwa mu gihe hari udukoko twirinda imiti. Kugira ngo umuntu 'asukure' intoki ze mbere yo kubagwa, ni ngombwa kugira igikarabiro gishobora gufungurwa no gufungwa nta gukorakora intoki, amazi ya chlorhexidine cyangwa yodi, utwenda tw'imyanda two kumesa intoki nyuma yo kuzisukura, n'isutiye y'imyanda yo gusukura no kugira ikindi gikoresho cy'imyanda cyo gusukura munsi y'amano.
Imirimbo yose yagombye gukurwaho.
Ubu buryo busaba ko ukaraba intoki n'amaboko kugeza ku rukenyerero, ubusanzwe mu minota 26.
Si ngombwa ko umuntu amara igihe kirekire asukura (iminota 10).
Mu gihe usukura, amazi ari ku maboko agomba kurindwa gusubira mu biganza.
Iyo bamaze gukaraba intoki, bazishyiraho umwenda w'umwanda maze bakambara ikanzu y'ubuvuzi.
Kugira ngo udakwirakwiza mikorobe, ni byiza ko ukaraba intoki cyangwa ukoresha umuti wica udukoko mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
Mu kurwanya indwara ziterwa na staphylococcus mu bitaro, byagaragaye ko inyungu ikomeye ituruka mu gusukura intoki yavuye ku 20% bya mbere byo gukaraba, kandi ko inyungu nke cyane y'inyongera yabonetse igihe umubare w'abantu basukura intoki wiyongereye cyane ugasaga 35%.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabune isanzwe bituma indwara ziterwa na bagiteri zandura mu biribwa zikubye inshuro zirenga eshatu ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'isabune irwanya bagiteri. Kugereranya gukaraba intoki n'isupu y'inzoga n'ukugeza intoki n'isabune irwanya bagiteri mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 buri kimwe cyerekanye ko gukaraba intoki n'inzoga byagabanyije ubwandu bwa bagiteri ku kigero cya 26% kurusha isabune irwanya bagiteri.
Ariko isabune n'amazi bifite akamaro kurusha amavuta yo gusokoza intoki akoreshwa kuri alukoro mu kugabanya virusi ya grippe A ya H1N1 na Clostridium difficile mu ntoki. Iterambere mu kwita ku isuku y'intoki mu bigo nderabuzima rishobora kuba rikubiyemo kwigisha abakozi gusukura intoki, kongera uburyo bwo gusokoza intoki zikoreshwa kuri alukoro, no kwibutsa abakozi mu nyandiko no mu magambo.
Hakenewe ubushakashatsi bwinshi ku buryo bumwe muri ubwo buryo bwo kuvura bukora neza mu nzego zitandukanye z'ubuzima.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki n'isabuni birazwi ko ari uburyo buhendutse kandi bw'ingenzi bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza, ndetse no kurya neza.
Icyakora, kubura amazi meza, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo z'abantu, ku mashuri no ku kazi bituma kugera ku myitwarire yo gukaraba intoki ku isi hose bigorana.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro bya Afurika, nta byuma byo gukaraba intoki biri hafi y'ubwiherero bwa buri wese cyangwa ubw'abaturage, nubwo hari uburyo buhendutse bwo kubaka aho gukaraba intoki.
Icyakora, umubare muto w'abantu bakaraba intoki ushobora guterwa n'imigenzo yashinze imizi aho guterwa no kutagira isabune cyangwa amazi.
Guteza imbere no gushyigikira gukaraba intoki n'isabuni bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro y'itegeko, gukangurira abantu kumenya ibyiza byo gukaraba intoki no gutuma abaturage bahindura imyitwarire yabo mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ibyo bikore neza, ni ngombwa gukurikirana no gusuzuma.
Isuzuma ryihariye ryakozwe ku bushakashatsi 70 ryagaragaje ko uburyo bw'abaturage bugira ingaruka nziza mu kongera gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikennye n'ibifite ubukungu buciriritse, mu gihe ubukangurambaga bwo kwamamaza ku mbuga nkoranyambaga butagira ingaruka nziza. Urugero rumwe rwo guteza imbere gukaraba intoki mu mashuri ni "Inzira y'inyenyeri eshatu" ya UNICEF itera amashuri inkunga yo gufata ingamba zoroshye kandi zidakora amafaranga menshi kugira ngo abanyeshuri bakoreshe isabune mu gukaraba intoki, mu bindi bisabwa mu isuku.
Iyo ibipimo by'ibanze byubahirijwe, amashuri ashobora kuva ku nyenyeri imwe agera ku nyenyeri eshatu.
Kubaka aho gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo guteza imbere gukaraba intoki bikorwa hagamijwe kugabanya indwara n'urupfu rw'abana.
Umunsi mpuzamahanga wo gukaraba intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo gukangurira abantu guhindura imyitwarire. Kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-20, UNICEF yashishikarije abantu gukoresha imiterere y'amafoto agaragaza ko umuntu akaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwarebye inyungu rusange yo gukaraba intoki mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere mu bijyanye n'imyaka y'uburumbuke y'ibanze (DALYs) yazibwe.
Icyakora, hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko guteza imbere gukaraba intoki n'isabuni bifite akamaro cyane ugereranyije n'ibindi bikorwa byo kuvura amazi n'isuku.
Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu  cyane cyane ku bantu bari mu mimerere mibi nk'ababyeyi baherutse kubyara cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse mu bitaro  byamenyekanye bwa mbere mu kinyejana cya 19 n'abapayiniya babiri b'isuku y'intoki: umuganga w'Umunya-Hungariya Ignaz Semmelweis wakoraga i Vienne, muri Autriche na Florence Nightingale, w'Umwongereza "washyizeho ubuvuzi bugezweho".
Icyo gihe abantu benshi bari bacyizera ko indwara ziterwa n'impumuro mbi zitwa miasme.
Mu myaka ya 1980, ibyorezo by'indwara ziterwa n'ibiribwa n'indwara ziterwa n'ubuvuzi byatumye Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitera imbere cyane isuku y'intoki nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube mu 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu 2020 byatumye mu bihugu byinshi abantu barushaho kumenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune kugira ngo birinde indwara zandura.
Urugero, mu Budage, hari inyandiko zigaragaza "uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki" zamanitswe iruhande rw'imyobo yo gukaraba intoki mu bwiherero rusange no mu bwiherero bw'amazu y'ibiro n'ibibuga by'indege.
Imvugo ngo "gukaraba intoki" bisobanura ko umuntu atemera ko icyo kintu ari we kiza cyangwa ko ari we kiza.
Ryaturutse mu murongo wa Bibiliya muri Matayo aho Ponsiyo Pilato yogeje amaboko ye ku cyemezo cyo kubamba Yesu Kristo, ariko cyabaye imvugo ikoreshwa cyane mu baturage bamwe na bamwe b'Abongereza.
Muri Macbeth ya Shakespeare, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki ku buryo bwo kwiyuhagira ikizinga cy'ibitekerezo, agaragaza umutimanama we wicira urubanza ku byaha yakoze kandi yatumye umugabo we abikora.
Byagaragaye kandi ko abantu, nyuma yo kwibuka cyangwa gutekereza ibikorwa by'ubwiyandarike, bakunda gukaraba intoki kenshi kurusha abandi, kandi bakishimira ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki cyane.
Byongeye kandi, abantu bemerewe gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gutekereza batyo, ntibakunda gukora ibindi bikorwa byo "kwiyeza", urugero nko kwitangira gukora imirimo.
Amadini ategeka ko abantu bakaraba intoki mu rwego rw'isuku no mu rwego rw'ikigereranyo. Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, hakoreshejwe amazi ariko nta isabune yo gukaraba intoki, ni kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukaraba intoki bikorwa mu madini menshi, harimo idini rya Baha'i, Abahindu, Tevilah na netilat yadayim mu idini rya Kiyahudi, Lavabo mu Bukristo na Wudhu mu idini rya Isilamu. Amadini na yo ategeka ko abantu bakaraba intoki mu buryo bw'isuku, cyane cyane nyuma y'ibikorwa runaka.
Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abayisilamu basabwa gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero.
Kandi, Abahindu, Ababuda, Abasiki, Abayahudi n'Abislamu basabwa gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma yo kurya.
Gucunga akaga ko mu kazi ka COVID-19
Gucunga akaga ko mu kazi ku bw'indwara ya COVID-19 ni ugushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kwirinda impanuka mu kazi no kwirinda indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Gucunga neza akaga ku kazi biterwa n'aho umuntu akorera n'akazi akora, bishingiye ku gusuzuma ibyago by'aho umuntu ashobora kwandura, uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage, n'ibyago by'abakozi bashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima (OSHA), imirimo ituma abantu batandura cyane usanga nta muntu n'umwe uhaba, kandi abafatanyabikorwa bakenera kwirinda indwara, harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gukurikiza amabwiriza yo guhumeka no gusukura no kuvura indwara mu kazi.
Mu mirimo ishobora guteza ibyago byo kwandura mu buryo bw'ikirere harimo n'iyisaba guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegera abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe n'ubwandu bukomeje mu baturage cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Ibi birimo abakozi bahuye n'abaturage muri rusange nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo abantu benshi, hamwe na bamwe mu bacuruzi bacuruza cyane.
Ingamba zo kwirinda akaga kuri iri tsinda, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, zirimo guhumeka ukoresheje amavuta ahumeka neza, kwirinda gusomana no kugira ibikoresho byo kwirinda umuntu aramutse ahanganye na COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubuzima n'abakora mu bigo by'ubupfu bahura n'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19 bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, ibyo bikaba byiyongera ku byago byinshi cyane byo kwandura mu gihe abakozi bakoze ibikorwa byo gukora aérosols ku muntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19, cyangwa bakorakoranya cyangwa bakagira icyo bakora ku bipimo bye.
Ingamba zo kurwanya akaga zigenewe aba bakozi zirimo ingamba zo kugenzura ikoranabuhanga nk'ibyumba by'umwuka uhumeka mu gitutu kibi, n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite bikwiye akazi.
Kwibasirwa na COVID-19 bishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi mu kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kutaba ku kazi bitewe n'uko barwaye, bakeneye kwita ku bandi, cyangwa batinya ko bashobora kwandura.
Imikorere y'ubucuruzi ishobora guhinduka, haba mu bijyanye n'ibicuruzwa bisabwa, ndetse n'uburyo bwo kubona ibicuruzwa (nk'ibicuruzwa mu masaha y'ikirenga cyangwa binyuze mu gutanga cyangwa serivisi zo gutwara imodoka).
Amaherezo, kohereza ibintu biturutse mu bice by'isi byugarijwe cyane na COVID-19 bishobora guhagarara. Gahunda yo kwitegura no guhangana n'indwara zandura ishobora gukoreshwa mu kuyobora ibikorwa byo kwirinda.
Imigambi ivuga ku nzitizi ziterwa n'aho imirimo ikorerwa n'ibikorwa bitandukanye, harimo n'ibitanga umwotsi, ibiterwa n'imiterere y'urugo n'abaturage, n'ibiterwa n'umukozi ku giti cye, urugero nk'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Nanone kandi, zigaragaza uburyo bwo kugenzura bukenewe mu guhangana n'ibyo byago, ndetse n'imigambi y'ubutabazi ku bibazo bishobora kuvuka bitewe n'indwara z'ibyorezo.
Imyiteguro n'imigambi yo guhangana n'indwara zandura ishobora gushingira ku nama z'igihugu cyangwa z'akarere.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo harimo kugabanya ubwandu mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zidakira, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi bigo biri mu nganda.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu karere ubucuruzi bwiherereyemo bugira ingaruka ku bisubizo byafashwe.
Urwego rw'ubuyobozi bwo kugenzura ibyago ni urwego rukoreshwa cyane mu buvuzi n'umutekano ku kazi mu gushyira hamwe kugenzura ibyago hakurikijwe imikorere.
Iyo hatari COVID-19 idashobora gukurwaho, uburyo bwiza bwo kugenzura ni ubuhanga, bukurikirwa n'ubuyobozi, hanyuma ibikoresho byo kurinda umuntu.
Kugenzura mu buhanga bikubiyemo gutandukanya abakozi n'ibiza bijyanye n'akazi batabanje kwishingikiriza ku myitwarire y'abakozi, kandi bishobora kuba umuti mwiza cyane wo gushyira mu bikorwa.
Igenzura ry'ubuyobozi ni impinduka mu buryo bw'imikorere cyangwa mu mikorere y'akazi bisaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwa muntu (PPE) bifatwa nk'ibidakora neza cyane kurusha ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi n'ibikoresho by'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha mu gukumira bimwe mu bintu bishobora gutuma umuntu ahura n'ibiza.
Ubwoko bwose bw'Ibikoresho by'Umutekano Byihariye (PPE) bigomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku kaga bishobora guteza umukozi, bikagenerwa ibikoresho bikwiye (urugero: ibikoresho byo guhumeka), bikagendeshwa neza kandi bikagendeshwa neza, bikagenzurwa buri gihe, bigashyirwamo ibikoresho byo kubungabunga, kandi bigasimbuzwa ibindi, nk'uko bikenewe, kandi bikurwaho, bikagororwa, kandi bigatungwa cyangwa bikirukanwa neza kugira ngo birinde kwanduzwa.
Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima ku kazi (OSHA), kivuga ko akazi gashobora gutuma umuntu atagerwaho n'ibiyobyabwenge gafite ingaruka nke cyane ku bantu n'abandi bakorana.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu zigirwa ku kazi kose zirimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi neza, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, uburyo bwo guhumeka burimo no guhisha iyo bakoroye no kwitsamura, gutanga utwenda n'ibikoresho byo guhana imyanda, kwitegura gukora kure cyangwa mu masaha y'akazi mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, guca intege abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no gukomeza isuku ya buri gihe no kwanduza imyanda ahantu bakorera.
Kumenya no gushyira mu kato abantu bashobora kwandura vuba ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi bari ku kazi.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga inama y'uko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bagomba kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe batagihari umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro n'ibindi bimenyetso mu gihe nibura cy'amasaha 24 badakoresheje imiti igabanya umuriro cyangwa indi miti igabanya ibimenyetso, kandi ko politiki yo kureka uburwayi ihinduka, yemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kwita ku muntu wo mu muryango urwaye, kandi ko abakozi bamenya izo politiki.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, imirimo y'ubwandu buciriritse ikubiyemo iyo isaba guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegera abantu bari muri metero 1.8 utari uzi cyangwa ukekwaho kuba arwaye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba baranduye SARS-CoV-2 kubera ubwandu bukomeje kuba mu baturage aho bakorera, cyangwa kubera ko uwo muntu aherutse gukora ingendo mpuzamahanga ajya ahantu hari ubwandu bwa COVID-19.
Muri ibyo harimo abakozi bagirana imishyikirano n'abaturage muri rusange nko mu mashuri, ahantu hari abaturage benshi, n'ahantu henshi hakorerwa ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi.Ibikorwa byo kugenzura ibi n'iby'amatsinda y'abashobora guhura n'ingaruka zikomeye birimo gushyiraho ibikoresho bikora neza cyane birinda umwuka, kongera umuvuduko w'umwuka, gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nk'ibyuma birinda imyanda yo mu plastike, no gushyiraho idirishya ryo gutwara imodoka kugira ngo abantu bajye mu kazi.Ibikorwa byo kugenzura ibi n'iby'amatsinda y'abashobora guhura n'ingaruka zikomeye birimo gushishikariza abakozi barwaye kuguma mu rugo, gusimbuza inama z'imibonano n'ibiganiro by'imibonano mpuzabitsina, gushyiraho amasaha yo guhinduranya, guhagarika ingendo zidakenewe mu duce dufite icyorezo cya COVID-19, gushyiraho gahunda z'ibihe bidasanzwe zirimo inama yo gusubiza ibibazo by'abakozi, gutanga inyigisho zigezweho n'amahugurwa ku bintu bishobora guteza COVID-19 n'udupfukamunwa n'udupira, abakeneye kwitoza gukoresha imyitwarire n'imyitwarire n'uburyo bwo kuyikoresha, gutanga ibikoresho birinda indwara no gushyiraho ibimenyetso ku bakozi, guhana n'ibiganza, gukaraba intoki cyangwa ibikoresho by'abantu ku giti cyabo, guhana n'ibicuruzwa, guhana n'ibicuruzwa, guhana n'abandi bakozi, guhana n'abandi, guhana n'ibindi bikorwa, harimo guhana n'ibicuruzwa, gukingira mu ruhame, gukingira, gukingira, gukingira, gukingira, gukingira cyangwa gukingira abakozi, no gushyiraho ibikoresho by'abantu ku kazi, cyangwa ibikoresho by'abandi.
Abakozi bari muri iri tsinda ry'abashobora guhura n'ingaruka z'iyi ndwara ntibakunda gukoresha ibyuma byo guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, ingamba zikwiye zo kurinda abakozi n'abandi bagenzi zirimo gutandukanya umurwayi n'abandi ku ntera ya metero 6, gushyiraho umwe mu bakozi bo mu ndege ngo akorere umurwayi, no guha umurwayi agapfukamunwa cyangwa kumusaba ko yambara agatambaro mu kanwa no mu mazuru mu gihe akoroye cyangwa atetse.
Abakozi bo mu ndege bagomba kwambara uturindantoki tw'impuzandengo igihe bita ku muntu urwaye cyangwa bakora ku mazi yo mu mubiri cyangwa ku bintu bishobora kwandura, kandi wenda bakambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi byiyongeraho mu gihe umurwayi afite umuriro, ikorora rirambye cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Inkweto n'ibindi bintu bikoreshwa rimwe bigomba kujugunywa mu mufuka urimo ibinyabuzima, kandi ibice byanduye bigomba guhanagurwa no kwandurwamo nyuma yaho. Ku bikorwa by'ubwikorezi, harimo amato y'urugendo n'andi mato atwara abagenzi, ingamba zo kurwanya ibyago zirimo gusubika ingendo iyo urwaye, no kwicungira ukwabo no kubwira ikigo nderabuzima kiri mu bwato ako kanya mu gihe umuntu agaragaje umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso ari mu bwato.
Mu buryo bwiza, ubuvuzi bugomba gukorerwa mu nzu y'umuntu wigunze. Ku mashuri n'ibigo byita ku bana, CDC itera inkunga yo gufunga igihe gito kugira ngo hasukurwe cyangwa hakurwemo udukoko turwanya indwara mu gihe umuntu wanduye yaba ari mu ishuri atitaye ku gukwirakwira kw'iyo ndwara mu baturage.
Iyo hari ubwandu bworoheje cyangwa buciriritse mu baturage, ingamba zo kwirinda abantu bashobora gushyira mu bikorwa nko guhagarika ingendo, amakoraniro n'andi materaniro manini nk'imyitozo ngororamubiri cyangwa amasomo ya korali cyangwa amafunguro mu kabari, kongera intera iri hagati y'amameza, gutandukanya igihe cyo kugera no gusohoka, kugabanya abashyitsi batari ngombwa, no gukoresha ahantu hatandukanye mu biro by'ubuzima ku bana bafite ibimenyetso bisa n'iby'ibicurane.
Iyo hari ubwandu bwinshi mu baturage, uretse ingamba zo kwirinda abantu, hashobora gutekerezwa ku guhagarika amashuri. Ku bakozi bashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bakora ibikorwa bisanzwe bya buri munsi, CDC ivuga ko ibyago byo guhungabanya ubuzima byihuse ari bike.
Abashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bagomba kuvugana n'abantu bagaragaweho cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 basabwa gukurikiza amabwiriza nk'ay'abaganga b'ubutabazi bw'ubutabazi, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bukwiye.
Iyo habayeho guhura kwa hafi mu gihe cyo gufatwa, abakozi bagomba gusukura no kuvura imyenda n'imyenda yabo mbere yo kongera kuyikoresha bakoresheje imashini yo gusukura cyangwa isuku y'inzu, kandi bagakurikiza amabwiriza asanzwe yo kubika no gutunganya ibikoresho bya PPE byakoreshejwe no kubikamo no kumesa imyenda.
OSHA ifata abakozi bamwe na bamwe bo mu buvuzi n'abakora mu by'ubuvuzi bw'abapfuye nk'abafite ibyago byinshi cyangwa byinshi byo kwandura.
Mu kazi gashobora guteza ibyago byinshi harimo abakora mu by'ubuvuzi, abashyigikira, abakora mu by'amavuriro n'abakora mu by'ingendo z'ubuvuzi, baba bari mu bantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kurwara COVID-19.
Ibi bihinduka ibyago byinshi byo kwanduzwa n'ibiyobyabwenge iyo abakozi bakoze ibikorwa byo gukora aérosol ku bantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, cyangwa bakorakoranya cyangwa bakagira icyo bakora ku bipimo byabo.
Uburyo bwo gukora aérosol burimo guterwa intanga, guterwa icyomoro, gukoresha bronchoscopie, gukoresha amenyo no kugenzura amenyo, cyangwa gufata ibipimo by'amenyo.
Mu mirimo y'ubupfu ifitanye isano n'ubwandu bwinshi harimo abakozi bakora mu gutegura imibiri y'abantu bari bazi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 igihe bapfaga; iyo bakoze ubwicanyi baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kubonana. Ibindi bikorwa by'ubuhanga bigenzura ibi byiciro by'abashobora guhura n'ubwandu harimo ibyumba by'ubwigunge by'abarwayi bafite COVID-19 bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho, harimo n'igihe habaho ibikorwa byo gukora umwuka utanga umwuka.
Mu bigo bimwe na bimwe by'ubuvuzi n'iby'ubupfu, umwuka uhumeka ufite igipimo cyo hasi ushobora kuba ukwiriye.
Ibipimo bigomba gukoreshwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza yo kwirinda ku rwego rwa 3 rw'umutekano.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) risaba ko abarwayi binjira batandukanywa mu byumba bitandukanye byo gutegerezamo bitewe n'uko bakekwaho COVID-19. Usibye ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi, OSHA isaba ko abakora muri metero 6 z'abarwayi bazwiho kuba barwaye SARS-CoV-2 cyangwa bakekwaho kuyandura, n'abakora ibikorwa byo gukora umwuka.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, ibikoresho byo guhumeka byo mu maso bikoreshwa na NIOSH bikoresha amavuta ya N95 cyangwa birenzeho bigomba gukoreshwa mu rwego rw'igikorwa cy'ubwirinzi bw'ubuhumekero cyuzuye kandi cyanditse kirimo gupima imiterere, amahugurwa n'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi.
Ubundi bwoko bw'imashini zo guhumeka zishobora gutanga uburinzi bwinshi no kunoza uko abakozi bamerewe. OMS ntiyifuza ko umuntu yambara imyenda y'ubwiza, kuko COVID-19 ari indwara y'ubuhumekero aho kwanduzwa n'amazi yo mu mubiri.
OMS itera inkunga ko abakozi bakora isuzuma ry'abinjira mu gihugu bagombye kwambara agapfukamunwa gusa.
Ku bantu bakusanya ibipimo by'ubuhumekero, kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 cyangwa kubajyana nta buryo bwo gukora ibirungo, OMS ibasaba kwambara agapfukamunwa, inkinzo zo guhanagura, cyangwa indangururamajwi, ikanzu n'amaboko.
Iyo hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo gukora aérosol, agapfukamunwa gakoreshwa mu kubaga gasimbuzwa agapfukamunwa ka N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko ibikoresho by'ubwisungane mu kwivuza ku isi yose bidahagije, OMS irasaba kugabanya cyane ibyo bikenerwa binyuze mu gukoresha uburyo bwa telemedicine, inzitizi z'umubiri nko gushyira amadirishya mu buryo bworoshye, kwemerera gusa abashinzwe kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 kwinjira mu cyumba, gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubwisungane mu kwivuza gusa bikenewe mu kazi runaka, gukomeza gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubwisungane mu kwivuza bidasimbuwe mu gihe wita ku barwayi benshi bafite icyorezo kimwe, kugenzura no guhuza uruziga rw'ibikoresho by'ubwisungane mu kwivuza, no guca intege abantu badafite ibimenyetso byo gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
