Guhindura gahunda y'akazi
Nk'uko Robyn yabivuze mbere, itsinda rya C ryateranye ejo ku mugoroba kugira ngo rigire icyo rivuga ku buryo tuzakoresha ibintu n'igihe tuzabikorera mu minsi n'amezi ari imbere.
Muri icyo kiganiro, twasuzumye icyo twatekerezaga ko ari igisubizo gikwiriye ku byo duhanganye na byo n'uburyo bwiza bwo gutuma uyu muryango ukomeza kubaho muri iki gihe.
Mu buryo bw'ingenzi, twifuzaga kugabanya imihangayiko no gushyigikira umurimo wacu mu gihe kirekire.
Niba ushaka guhamagara, nta kibazo.
Ku bakozi bose, abakora imirimo y'ubucuruzi n'abakozi bakora mu buryo bw'amasezerano:
amasaha y'akazi ku munsi, cyangwa amasaha 20 mu cyumweru kugeza igihe tuzabimenyesha.
Ntabwo turatangaza umunsi w'ikiruhuko - niba ushobora gukora amasaha menshi, iyo misiyo ishobora kugukoresha.
Icyakora, muri iki gihe isi ntihinduka, kandi twaba dukeneye kwita ku bo dukunda, kujya guhaha cyangwa kujya kwa muganga, icya mbere ni ukugira ubuzima bwiza.
Ntitujya dukurikirana igihe cyawe.
Niba urwaye, ntukore.
Ibyo ni ibintu bisanzwe, ariko turabivuga.
Nta minsi yo kurwara cyangwa PTO isabwa - babwire umuyobozi wawe gusa kandi ufashe itsinda ryawe gusubiramo kalendari n'ingengabihe kugirango umenye neza ko ibice by'ingenzi by'akazi byuzujwe.
(Niba wanduye COVID-19, turagusaba kumenyesha Bryan muri T&amp;C Ops kugira ngo T&amp;C imufashe kandi imwereke ko ikibazo cyawe cyitabwaho n'ubuyobozi).
Abantu bakora amasaha runaka bazajya bishyurwa umushahara wabo wose.
