b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni enzyme ifatanye n'urusobe rw'inyuma (urw'ingirabuzima fatizo) rw'ingirabuzima fatizo zo mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 ihangana n'ibikorwa bya enzyme ihindura angiotensin (ACE) binyuze mu kugabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II no kongera Ang ((1-7) bigatuma iba umuti uhenze mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora kandi nk'aho umuntu yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'ubwoko bumwe na bumwe bwa koronavirusi.
Ubwoko bwa enzyme ku bantu bukunze kwitwa hACE2.
Ingingo ya 2 ihindura angiotensin ni ingiga irimo metaloenzyme iri ku gice cy'imbere mu mubiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 irimo uruziga rwa peptidase M2 rwa N-terminal na collectrin ya C-terminal ya acide aminate itwara imyanda.
ACE2 ni poroteyine y'urupapuro rw'uruhu rw'ubwoko bwa I, ifite urubuga rw'urupapuro rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uru.
Uruhare rw'umusemburo wa ACE2 rwo hanze y'ingirabuzimafatizo ruratandukanywa n'urw'urundi rugingo rw'umubiri rwitwa sheddase, maze poroteyine ishira mu maraso igakurikiraho igashyirwamo mu maraso, amaherezo igashyirwamo mu maraso.
ACE2 iboneka mu ngingo nyinshi: ACE2 ifatanye n'urwihingiro rw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ubuhumekero z'ubwoko bwa II, intanga z'urwungano rw'urwungano rw'umwijima, ingirabuzimafatizo z'umushinge n'iz'umushinge n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'umusatsi n'iz'umusatsi mu ngingo nyinshi.
Igikorwa cya ACE2 mRNA kandi kiboneka mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa striatum, hypothalamus no mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa brainstem.
Imikorere y'ingenzi ya ACE2 ni ugukora nk'igisubizo cya ACE.
ACE itandukanya ihormone ya angiotensin I n'ihormone ya angiotensin II ituma amaraso atangira kuvamo amaraso.
ACE2 nayo igabanya amino acide carboxyl-terminal phenylalanine ikayivamo angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikayivamo angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora kandi gutandukanya ibindi bintu byinshi birimo [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi itegeka uburyo bwa membrane bw'umuvuduko wa SLC6A19 utwara amino acide kandi yagaragaye ko ifitanye isano n'indwara ya Hartnup.
Nk'indwara y'uruhu, ACE2 ni yo nzira y'ibanze yo kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi zimwe na zimwe, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi ituma SARS ibaho); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi ituma COVID-19 ibaho).
By'umwihariko, guhuza poroteyine ya S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 n'urwego rwa enzymatic rwa ACE2 ku gice cy'imbere mu ngirabuzimafatizo bituma habaho endocytosis no kwimura virusi na enzyme mu bice by'imbere mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Iyi nzira yo kwinjira kandi isaba ko poroteyine ya S ibanza guterwa na serine protease TMPRSS2, ubu bufasha bwayo buri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi nk'umuti ushobora kuvura. Ibi byatumye bamwe batekereza ko kugabanya urugero rwa ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo, bishobora gufasha mu kurwanya ubwandu.
Icyakora, imiryango myinshi y'abahanga n'inzego zishinzwe kugenzura ibintu, zasabye ko hakomeza gukoresha imiti isanzwe ihagarika ACE n'imiti ya ARB.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, bwagaragaje ko "gukoresha imiti igabanya ubukana bw'amaraso (ACE inhibitors) byagabanyije cyane ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'ibihaha ku kigero cya 34% ugereranyije n'abatarayirwaye".
Byongeye kandi, "ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'ibihaha byagabanutse no ku barwayi bahabwa imiti igabanya ubukana bwa ACE, bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara iyi ndwara, cyane cyane abafite indwara yo mu bwonko n'uburwayi bwo ku mutima.
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors na byo byajyaniranaga no kugabanya impfu ziterwa n'umusonga, nubwo ibisubizo byari bike cyane ugereranyije n'ibyagenewe ibyago byose byo kurwara umusonga".
Abantu bakoresha ACE2 (rhACE2) mu kuvura indwara z'ibihaha, kandi bigaragara ko itera imbere mu kuvura indwara z'ibihaha mu maraso no mu guhumeka umwuka mu ngurube zifite indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye ikibazo cy'ibihaha.
Igihe cy'ihererekanya ry'ibinyabuzima bya rhACE2 ku bantu ni amasaha agera kuri 10 kandi igihe cy'igikorwa ni iminota 30 hiyongeraho n'igihe cy'ingaruka (igihe) cy'amasaha 24.
Ubushakashatsi butandukanye bugaragaza ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti uhenze ku bantu badahanganira ibibuza uburyo bwa Renin-angiotensin (RAS inhibitors) cyangwa indwara zituma angiotensin II igenda yiyongera. RhACE2 ivuye mu mubiri yagenzuwe mu igerageza mu buvuzi mu kuvura indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye inkeke.
porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu za mudasobwa zigenewe gufasha mu gukurikirana abantu mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-20, ni ukuvuga uburyo bwo kumenya abantu ("abahuye") bashobora kuba baragiranye isano n'umuntu wanduye.
Ibikoresho byinshi byatangiye cyangwa byatangwa, hamwe n'ubufasha bwa leta mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Imyubakire itandukanye yo kubaka porogaramu zo gukurikirana abakoraho.
Impungenge ku buzima bwite zagiye zivugwa, cyane cyane ku mikorere ishingiye ku gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu bari.
Ibindi bintu bishobora gutuma umuntu atagira ikibazo cyo guhamagara cyane ni ugukoresha telefoni ya Bluetooth kugira ngo amenye aho umuntu aherereye n'izindi telefoni.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ku mugaragaro ko bizashyira hamwe imikorere yo gushyigikira izo porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu zikora za Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa ifatanyije na Alipay yashyizeho porogaramu ituma abaturage bashobora kureba niba barigeze guhura n'abantu barwaye COVID-19.
Ikoreshwa mu mijyi isaga 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapore, hakoreshwa porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
Porogaramu yakozwe n'umuryango w'ikoranabuhanga wo muri ako gace, yasohotse nk'ifunguye kandi izashyikirizwa leta. Macedonia y'Amajyaruguru yatangije porogaramu ya Bluetooth yitwa "StopKorona!", ikoreshwa mu kureba abantu bashobora kwandura no guha abayobozi b'ubuzima ibisubizo byihuse.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itumanaho n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Guhera ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu bari mu ngendo z'iterambere iri mu cyiciro cy'iterambere, kandi ko izaba ishobora gukoreshwa mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'iyo irateganywa muri Irilande no mu Bufaransa ("StopCovid").
Australia na Nouvelle-Zélande byombi birimo gusuzuma porogaramu zishingiye kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether ya Singapuru na BlueTrace protocol. Uburusiya bufite umugambi wo gushyiraho porogaramu yo gufungira abantu mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga ku barwayi basanzwemo COVID-19 baba i Moscou, igamije kubarinda kuva mu ngo zabo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha iby'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yagaragaje ibibazo byinshi bishobora kubaho mu mikorere y'imikorere ishingiye ku porogaramu, harimo n'ibinyoma by'ibinyoma n'ubushobozi buke bushobora kubaho mu gihe gukoresha porogaramu byigariye ku gice gito cy'abaturage.
Mu guhangana n'impungenge ku gukwirakwira kwa porogaramu za "coronavirus" z'ibinyoma cyangwa zangiza, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku bwoko bw'imiryango ishobora kongeramo porogaramu zijyanye na coronavirus muri App Store yayo, ikazigabanya ku miryango "yemewe" gusa cyangwa ifite izina ryiza.
Google na Amazon bashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abashinzwe kubungabunga ubuzima bwite bagaragaje impungenge bafite ku ngaruka z'ibikorwa by'ubugenzuzi bukorwa n'abantu benshi hifashishijwe porogaramu za koronavirusi, by'umwihariko niba ibikorwa remezo by'ubugenzuzi byakozwe mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya koronavirusi bizasenyuka igihe icyo cyorezo kizaba kimaze guhita.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe asaga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura buhabwa imipaka.
Amashyirahamwe yatangaje ibintu umunani ku mishinga ya leta:
kugenzura bigomba kuba "byemewe n'amategeko, ari ngombwa kandi bihuje n'ibisabwa";
igihe cy'ikirenga cy'ibikorwa byo kugenzura no kugenzura, hagomba kuba hari ingingo zivuga ko nta cyo byamara;
gukoresha amakuru bigomba kuba mu rwego rwa COVID-19 gusa;
umutekano w'amakuru n'ubwirinzi bw'amazina bigomba kurindwa kandi bikagaragazwa ko birindwa hashingiwe ku bimenyetso;
kugenzura ikoranabuhanga bigomba kwirinda kongera ivangura no gucibwa intege;
gusangira amakuru n'abantu batatu bigomba gushyirwa mu mategeko;
hakwiye kubaho uburyo bwo kwirinda ihohoterwa n'uburenganzira bw'abaturage bwo kugira icyo bakora ku ihohoterwa;
"kwifatanya mu buryo bufite ireme" kw' "abari n'uruhare" bose, harimo n'abahanga mu by'ubuzima rusange n'amatsinda y'abantu batagira aho babogamira, bizasabwa.
Umugambi uteganyijwe wa Google/Apple ugamije gukemura ikibazo cy'ubugenzuzi buhoraho mu gukuraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana mu bikoresho byabo iyo butakiri ngombwa.
Ibihugu bimwe byakoresheje uburyo bwo gukurikirana aho umuntu ari mu muyoboro aho gukoresha porogaramu, bituma batakenera gukuramo porogaramu kandi ntibashobore gukurikirana.
Muri Isirayeli, uburyo bwo gukurikirana amakuru hakoreshejwe interineti bwemewe.
Ibisubizo bishingiye ku muyoboro bifite amakuru y'aho umuntu ari mu buryo bw'ibanze bifite ibibazo bikomeye bishobora kuvuka mu bijyanye n'ibanga.
Ariko, ntabwo sisitemu zose zifite seriveri nkuru zigomba kubona amakuru yerekeye ahantu umuntu ari; hari uburyo bwinshi bwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite bwakozwe bukoresha seriveri nkuru gusa mu itumanaho (reba igice gikurikira).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hakoreshejwe uburyo butari bushingiye kuri porogaramu mu gukora isuzuma ry'abantu bahuye n'abantu.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, sisitemu yakusanyije amakuru yo gukurikirana avuye mu masoko atandukanye arimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga n'amakuru y'ibikorwa byo gukoresha amakarita, maze ayashyira hamwe kugira ngo atange amakuru binyuze mu butumwa bugufi ku bantu bashobora kwandura.
Uretse gukoresha aya makuru kugira ngo bamenyeshe abantu bashobora guhura na bo, leta yashyize ahagaragara amakuru y'aho umuntu ari, ibyo bikaba byemewe kubera impinduka zikomeye mu mategeko agenga amakuru nyuma y'icyorezo cya MERS muri icyo gihugu.
Aya makuru ashobora kuboneka ku mugaragaro binyuze muri porogaramu nyinshi na website.Ibihugu birimo n'u Budage byatekereje gukoresha uburyo bwigenga kandi burinda ubuzima bwite.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, ibisobanuro ntibyari byarabonetse.
Gukurikirana amakuru y'abantu ku giti cyabo ni igitekerezo cyemewe, gifite inyandiko nyinshi z'ubushakashatsi zisubiza nibura mu 2013.Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'abahanga arenga icumi yakoraga ku bisubizo byujuje ubuziranenge, nk'ikoreshwa rya Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) kugirango bandike aho umukoresha ari hafi ya terefone zigendanwa.
Ariko, PEPP-PT ni igikorwa cyo guhuza ibintu kirimo uburyo bwigenga n'ubw'ibanze, kandi ntabwo ari protocole imwe.Ibigo by'ubucuruzi byigenga birimo Gukurikirana kwegereyeho ku buryo butuma ubuzima bwite bw'abantu budahungabana (DP-PPT/DP-3T), Imibare y'igihe gito yo guhura (TCN, fka Imibare y'ibyabaye mu guhura, CEN), Protokoli n'uburyo bwo gukurikirana amakuru y'abantu ku buryo bw'ibanga (PACT) n'ibindi.
Muri ayo masezerano, amakuru y'umuntu ku giti cye atajya ava ku gikoresho, kandi guhura kose kuba ku gikoresho.
