Ibihugu byinshi byateye imbere nta buriri buhagije mu bitaro ku muntu umwe, ibyo bikaba bigabanya ubushobozi bw'urwego rw'ubuzima bwo guhangana n'ubwiyongere butunguranye bw'umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 bafite ubukana bukomeye ku buryo bisaba ko bajyanwa mu bitaro.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa bwagaragaje ko 5% bari baremerewe kujya mu byumba by'indembe, 2.3% bari bakeneye ubufasha bw'imashini zo guhumeka, naho 1.4% bapfuye.
Mu Bushinwa, hafi 30% by'abantu bari mu bitaro barwaye COVID-19 amaherezo bajya mu bitaro bya ICU.
Imikorere y'umwuka mu buryo bw'imashini irushaho kuba igoranye uko indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye ubwoba (ARDS) igenda yiyongera muri COVID-19 kandi umwuka wa ogisijeni ugenda urushaho kugorana.
Imashini z'ubuhumekero zishobora kugenzura umuvuduko n'ibipimo byinshi bya PEEP ni ngombwa kugira ngo haboneke umwuka wa ogisijeni uhagije, mu gihe hagabanywa ibyago byo gukomereka kw'ibihaha n'impuzi ziterwa n'imashini z'ubuhumekero.
Ibipimo byinshi bya PEEP bishobora kutaboneka ku mashini z'ubuhumekero zishaje.
Ubushakashatsi ku miti ishobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura iyi ndwara bwatangiye muri Mutarama 2020, kandi imiti itandukanye igabanya ubukana bwa virusi iri mu igeragezwa mu buvuzi.
Igikoresho cya Remdesivir gisa n'aho ari cyo kiza ku isonga.
Nubwo imiti mishya ishobora kumara igihe kugeza mu 2021 itangiye gukorwa, imiti myinshi irimo kugeragezwa yamaze kwemererwa gukoresha indi miti cyangwa iri mu igeragezwa rigezweho.
Abantu barwaye indwara ikomeye bashobora kugerageza gukoresha imiti igabanya ubukana bwa virusi.
OMS yasabye ko abitangiye gukora imirimo bagira uruhare mu igerageza ry'ubushobozi n'umutekano w'imiti ishobora gukoreshwa. FDA yatanze uruhushya rw'agateganyo ku plasma ikira nk'uburyo bwo kugerageza mu gihe ubuzima bw'umuntu buri mu kaga gakomeye cyangwa ako kanya.
Ntabwo cyakozwe mu bushakashatsi bw'imiti bukenewe kugira ngo kigaragaze ko gifite umutekano kandi ko gifite ingaruka nziza ku ndwara.
Muri Gashyantare 2020, Ubushinwa bwatangije porogaramu ya telefoni igendanwa yo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
