Abagore batwite bashobora kuba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura COVID-19 mu buryo bukomeye hashingiwe ku makuru y'izindi virusi zisa n'izo, nka SARS na MERS, ariko amakuru ya COVID-19 aracyari make. Mu bantu bamwe na bamwe, COVID-19 ishobora kugira ingaruka ku bihaha bigatera indwara y'ibihaha.
