Abanywa itabi bari bafite ibyago byo kugira ibimenyetso bikomeye bya COVID-19 bikubye inshuro 1.4 kandi bishoboka ko bakenera kwitabwaho cyane cyangwa gupfa inshuro zigera kuri 2.4 ugereranyije n'abatanywa itabi. Hari impungenge z'ingaruka z'igihe kirekire z'iyo ndwara.
Ikigo gishinzwe ibitaro bya Hong Kong cyabonye ko ubushobozi bw'ibihaha bwahise bugabanukaho 20% kugera kuri 30% mu bantu bamwe na bamwe bakize iyo ndwara, kandi ibipimo by'ibihaha byerekanye ko hari ibyangiritse mu ngingo.
Ibyo bishobora no gutuma umuntu agira indwara yo mu mutwe nyuma yo gukira.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, ntibyari bizwi niba ubwandu bw'igihe cyashize butanga ubudahangarwa bwiza kandi bw'igihe kirekire mu bantu bakira iyi ndwara.
Ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara bwigaragaza nk'ubushoboka, hashingiwe ku myitwarire y'izindi koronavirusi, ariko hari abantu bagaragaweho uburwayi bwa COVID-19 nyuma yo gupimwa bagasanga barwaye koronavirusi.
