Ibitabo byemewe na OMS byatangaje ko ibimenyetso byatangiye ku itariki ya 8 Ukuboza 2019.
Hari ibintu byinshi bikunze gukoreshwa mu gupima umubare w'abapfa.
Iyi mibare igenda itandukana bitewe n'akarere n'igihe kandi biganzwa n'umubare w'ibipimo, ubwiza bw'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kwivuza, igihe cyashize icyorezo gitangiye no ku miterere y'abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima muri rusange.
Mu mpera za 2019, OMS yashyizeho kode z'indwara z'ibiza za ICD-10 U07.1 ku bantu bapfuye bazize ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bwemejwe n'ibigo by'ubushakashatsi na U07.2 ku bantu bapfuye bazize COVID-19 yagezweho n'ubwandu bw'indwara cyangwa indwara zitari zarabonetse. Umubare w'abapfuye ugereranyije n'abapfuye ugereranyije n'umubare w'abapfuye bagabanijwe n'umubare w'abapfuye mu gihe runaka.
Dukurikije imibare ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins, imibare y'abamaze gupfa ku isi yose ni 6.9% (153,822/2,240,191) guhera ku ya 17 Mata 2020.
Umubare uratandukanye bitewe n'akarere. Ibindi bipimo birimo igipimo cy'ubwandu (CFR), kigaragaza igipimo cy'abantu bagaragaweho indwara bapfa, n'igipimo cy'ubwandu (IFR), kigaragaza igipimo cy'abantu banduye (bafite indwara n'abatarayigaragaweho) bapfa.
Iyi mibare ntabwo ifitanye isano n'igihe kandi ikurikirana umubare runaka w'abantu kuva ku banduye kugeza ku barembye.
Nubwo abantu bose banduye batagira za 'anticorps', kuba hari za 'anticorps' bishobora gutuma tumenya umubare w'abantu banduye.
Mu gace k'ibanze k'icyorezo mu Butaliyani, Castiglione d'Adda, umudugudu muto utuwe n'abantu 4600, 80 (1.7%) baramaze gupfa.
Muri Gangelt, iyi ndwara yakwirakwijwe n'iminsi mikuru ya Karineva, ikwirakwira no mu rubyiruko, bituma abantu bapfa bake cyane, kandi si abantu bose bapfuye bazize COVID-19 bashobora kuba barashyizwe mu byiciro by'ubudehe.
Byongeye kandi, ubuvuzi bw'Abadage ntibwigeze burengerwa.
Mu Buholandi, abagera kuri 3% bashobora kuba bafite za 'anticorps', nk'uko bigaragazwa n'abatanga amaraso.
