Ingaruka z'icyorezo n'umubare w'abapfa bitewe nacyo bitandukanye ku bagabo n'abagore.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe mu Bushinwa no mu Butaliyani, abagabo ni bo bapfa cyane kurusha abagore.
Abagabo bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara iyo ndwara ni abo mu kigero cy'imyaka 50, kandi itandukaniro riri hagati y'abagabo n'abagore rigabanuka iyo bagejeje imyaka 90.
Mu Bushinwa, abagabo bapfaga ku kigero cya 2.8 ku ijana, abagore bapfa ku kigero cya 1.7 ku ijana.
Impamvu nyayo zituma habaho iryo tandukaniro hagati y'ibitsina ntiziramenyekana, ariko hari impamvu z'ibanze zishobora kuba zishingiye ku miterere y'ibinyabuzima n'imyitwarire.
Itandukaniro ry'ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara rishingiye ku gitsina, kuba abagore n'abagabo batanywa itabi cyane mu gihe bafite indwara ziterwa n'isukari nk'umuvuduko w'amaraso uri hasi y'uw'abagore, bishobora kuba byaratumye abagabo bapfa cyane.
Mu Burayi, 57% by'abanduye bari abagabo naho 72% by'abahitanywe na COVID-19 bari abagabo.
Guhera muri Mata 2020, leta ya Amerika ntabwo ikurikirana amakuru ajyanye n'imibonano mpuzabitsina y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko indwara ziterwa na virusi nka Ebola, HIV, ibicurane na SARS zigira ingaruka zitandukanye ku bagabo n'abagore.
Umubare munini w'abakozi b'ubuzima, cyane cyane abaforomo, ni abagore, kandi bafite amahirwe menshi yo kwandura iyi virusi.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020 ko izina ry'ubuvuzi ry'iyi ndwara rizaba "COVID-19".
Umuyobozi wa OMS Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus yasobanuye ko CO isobanura corona, VI isobanura virusi, D isobanura indwara, naho 19 isobanura igihe icyorezo cyamenyekanye bwa mbere: 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Iri zina ryatoranyijwe mu rwego rwo kwirinda ko hagira aho rivuga ku gace runaka (urugero: Ubushinwa), ubwoko bw'inyamaswa cyangwa itsinda ry'abantu, hakurikijwe amabwiriza mpuzamahanga agenga amazina agamije gukumira gutukwa. Virusi itera COVID-19 yitwa coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
OMS ikoresha kandi "virusi ya COVID-19" na "virusi iteza COVID-19" mu itumanaho rusange.
Iyo ndwara na virusi byombi bikunze kwitwa "coronavirus".
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere cyabereye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, virusi n'indwara byakunze kwitwa "coronavirus" na "Wuhan coronavirus".
Muri Mutarama 2020, OMS yatanze inama yo gukoresha 2019-nCov na 2019-nCoV indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze nk'amazina y'agateganyo ya virusi n'indwara, hakurikijwe amabwiriza yo mu 2015 yo kwirinda gukoresha ahantu mu mazina y'indwara na virusi.
Amazina yemewe ya COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 yatanzwe ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020.
Kubera ubushobozi buke mu buryo bw'ibanze bwo gutanga ibicuruzwa, bamwe mu bakora ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki barimo gucapa ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi nk'udupfunyika two mu mazuru n'ibice by'imashini zitanga umwuka.
Urugero, igihe ibitaro byo mu Butaliyani byasabaga byihutirwa umufuka w'umuvuduko w'umwuka, kandi umucuruzi ntiyashoboraga gutanga mu gihe cyari gikenewe, ikigo cyo muri ako gace cyatangiye gukora imashini z'ubwubatsi zinyuranye maze zicapa za fovu 100 zari zikenewe mu ijoro rimwe.
Nyuma y'aho COVID-19 itangiriye, ibitekerezo by'ubuhendanyi, amakuru atari yo n'amakuru atari yo byatangiye kuvugwa ku nkomoko, urugero, kwirinda, kuvura n'ibindi bintu by'iyi ndwara kandi bikwirakwira ku mbuga za interineti mu buryo bwihuse.
Abantu basa n'aho bashobora gukwirakwiza iyi virusi ku zindi nyamaswa.
Ubushakashatsi ntibwashoboye kubona ibimenyetso by'uko virusi ishobora kwiyongera mu ngurube, amasazi n'inkoko.
Nta miti cyangwa urukingo rwemewe kuvurwa iyo ndwara.
Ubushakashatsi mpuzamahanga ku nkingo n'imiti ya COVID-19 burimo gukorwa n'imiryango ya leta, amatsinda y'abanyeshuri n'abashakashatsi mu by'inganda.
Muri Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangije "Igerageza ry'UBUHAMYA" ryo gusuzuma ingaruka z'imiti ine ya virusi iriho ubu ifite icyizere cyo gukora neza.
Nta rukingo ruhari, ariko ibigo bitandukanye biri gukora cyane ku bakandida b'urukingo.
Ibikorwa byakozwe mbere kuri SARS-CoV birakoreshwa kuko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha receptor ya ACE2 kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'abantu.
Hari uburyo butatu bwo gukingira bugenda bwigwaho.
Mbere na mbere, abashakashatsi bifuza gukora urukingo rw'iyo virusi yose.
Gukoresha virusi nk'iyo, yaba idafite umusaruro cyangwa yapfuye, bigamije gutuma umubiri w'umuntu uhita ubasha guhangana n'ubwandu bushya bwa COVID-19.
Uburyo bwa kabiri, inkingo z'udutsiko duto, bugamije gukora inkingo zituma ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri buhinduka ku duce tumwe na tumwe tw'iyo virusi.
Ku bijyanye na SARS-CoV-2, ubwo bushakashatsi bwibanda kuri poroteyine ya S-spike ifasha virusi kwinjira mu cyuma cyakira za ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni ubwo gukoresha inkingo za nucleic acid (inkingo za DNA cyangwa RNA, uburyo bushya bwo gukora inkingo).
Inkingo z'igerageza zo muri ubwo buryo bwose zigomba kugeragezwa ku mutekano n'ubushobozi. Ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, igeragezwa rya mbere ry'urukingo ryatangiranye n'abakorerabushake bane i Seattle.
Uru rukingo rufite kode y'ibinyabuzima itagira icyo itwaye yakuwe muri virusi itera iyi ndwara. Gushyiraho uburyo bwo kuvura bwa virusi budafite icyo butwaye, byavuzwe ko bishobora guteza ibibazo mu gukora urukingo rwa SARS-COV-2, ariko biravuguruzanya.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, hari ibizamini byo kwa muganga birenga 300 biri gukorwa.
Ibizamini birindwi byari bigamije gusuzuma imiti yemewe ya malariya, harimo n'ibizamini bine byakozwe kuri hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Imiti ikoreshwa mu kurwanya virusi yongeye gushyirwaho igize igice kinini cy'ubushakashatsi bwo mu Bushinwa, aho igerageza ry'icyiciro cya III cya 9 cya Remdesivir mu bihugu byinshi rigomba gutangazwa mu mpera za Mata.
Kuva muri Mata 2020, hari igenzura rikomeye ry'iterambere ry'inkingo n'imiti ya COVID-19 byariho. Imiti myinshi ya virusi iriho iri kugeragezwa mu kuvura COVID-19, harimo remdesivir, chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir na lopinavir/ritonavir ifatanyije na interferon beta.
Hari ibimenyetso by'ibanze byerekana ko remdesivir ifite ubushobozi, guhera muri Werurwe 2020.
Mu barwayi bahabwa imiti ya remdesivir ikoreshwa mu buryo buhuje n'impuhwe, hagaragaye kuzamuka mu rwego rwa kizamini.
Ibizamini byo kwa muganga byo mu cyiciro cya III birakorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ibinini bya Chloroquine, byahoze bikoreshwa mu kuvura malariya, byakorewe ubushakashatsi mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, bibonamo ibisubizo by'ibanze.
Icyakora, hari abantu basaba ko ubwo bushakashatsi bwagombye gusuzumwa n'abandi.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima bwa Koreya n'Ubushinwa bwemeza ko hakoreshwa chloroquine.
Icyakora, Ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi ku ndwara za virusi cyo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, nubwo gitanga inama yo gufata igabano ry'igarama imwe ku munsi, kivuga ko gufata igabano ry'amagarama abiri ari ibintu biteje akaga cyane kandi bishobora kwica.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine ku bushake bw'abaganga bavura abantu barwaye COVID-19. Amabwiriza y'Ubushinwa yo ku ncuro ya 7 arimo interferon, ribavirin cyangwa umifenovir yo gukoresha mu kurwanya COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko dosiye nyinshi za ribavirin zikenewe mu kubuza SARS-CoV-2 mu byumba.
Nitazoxanide yagiriwe inama yo kongera kwifashishwa mu bushakashatsi mu mubiri nyuma yo kugaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ihagarikwa mu rugero rwo hasi. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gutangiza poroteyine ya mbere ya spike ikoreshejwe na serine 2 (TMPRSS2) ni ngombwa kugira ngo SARS-CoV-2 yinjire binyuze mu guhura n'urwungano rwa ACE2.
Ubushakashatsi ku miti ya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine irimo cyangwa idafite azithromycin bufite aho bugarukira cyane byatumye abaganga batemera iyi miti nta bundi bushakashatsi. Oseltamivir ntibubuza SARS-CoV-2 mu mubiri kandi nta ruhare ruzwi igira mu kuvura COVID-19.
Icyorezo cya cytokine gishobora kuba ikibazo mu byiciro bya nyuma bya COVID-19 ikomeye.
Hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo kurwanya ibiza by'ibinyabutabire. Tocilizumab yashyizwe mu mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa nyuma y'uko ubushakashatsi buto bwarangiye.
Iri mu igeragezwa ry'icyiciro cya 2 ritagizwe n'abashakashatsi ku rwego rw'igihugu mu Butaliyani nyuma yo kugaragaza ibisubizo byiza ku bantu barwaye indwara ikomeye.
Iyo iyo miti ifatanyije n'ikizamini cy'amaraso cyitwa ferritin mu maraso kugira ngo hamenyekane ibicurane by'imiti yitwa cytokines, iba igamije kurwanya ibyo bintu, bikaba bivugwa ko ari byo bituma abantu bamwe na bamwe bicwa n'iyo ndwara.
Igikoresho cy'ubuvuzi cyitwa interleukin-6 cyemejwe na FDA hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe nyuma yo kuvura indwara ya sitokine ituma sitokine zidakira za siteroyide zitangwa n'impamvu zitandukanye, ni ukuvuga CAR T cell therapy, mu 2017.
Kugeza ubu, nta bimenyetso bifatika, bigenzurwa bigaragaza ko tocilizumab ari umuti mwiza wo kuvura CRS.
Guhererekanya udukoko twanduye kandi twiganjemo twakozwe n'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya COVID-19 ku bantu babukeneye birimo gukorwaho iperereza nk'uburyo butari urukingo bwo kwinjiza abanduye.
Ubu buryo bwashyizwe mu bikorwa ku ndwara ya SARS ariko ntibugira icyo bugeraho.
Kugabanya virusi ni uburyo bwitezwe bwo gukora, aho uburyo bwo kuvura abarwayi budafite ubushobozi bwo kuvura bushobora gufasha mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2.
